msgid ""
"This page lists all configuration items on your site that have "
"translatable text, like your site name, role names, etc."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta pagina lista totes las configuracions sus vòstre site que "
"contenon de tèxt translatable, coma lo nom del site, los noms de "
