msgid ""
"Click <em>Save settings</em>. You should be returned to the <em>Manage "
"fields</em> page, with your new field in the list."
msgstr ""
"Clicatz sus <em>Enregistrar las configuracions</em>. Deuriatz èsser "
"retornat a la pagina <em>Gestionar los camps</em>, amb vòstre nòu "
"camp dins la lista."

msgid ""
"Whether to force the output to be an absolute link (beginning with "
"http: or https:)"
msgstr ""
"Se cal forçar la sortida a èsser un ligam absolut (commençant per "
"http: o https:)"

msgid ""
"Whether to force this URL to point to a secure location (beginning "
