msgstr ""
"Lo formulari <strong>Reenviar</strong> permet a l'administrator de "
"prévisualizar e de reenviar d'emails e de messatges."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Submissions</strong> page displays a customizable overview "
"of a webform node's submissions."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Submissions</strong> mòstra una vista "
"personalizable de las submissions d'un node de formulari web."

msgid ""
"Only webform administrators are allowed to access this page and create "
"new submissions."
msgstr ""
"Solament los administrators del formulari weban son autorizats a "
"accedir a aquesta pagina e a crear de nòvas sosmetudas."

msgid "The delimiter used when an element has multiple values."
msgstr "Lo delimitador utilizat quand un element a mantun valor."

