"This webform is <a href=\":href\">closed</a>. Only submission "
"administrators are allowed to access this webform and create new "
"submissions."
msgstr ""
"Aqueste formulari web es <a href=\":href\">clausat</a>. Solament los "
"administrators de las submissions pòdon accedir a aqueste formulari "
"web e crear de nòvas submissions."

msgid ""
"This webform is <a href=\":href\">archived</a>. Only submission "
"administrators are allowed to access this webform and create new "
"submissions."
msgstr ""
"Aqueste formulari web es <a href=\":href\">archivat</a>. Sonque los "
"administrators de las sosmissions an lo drech d'accès a aqueste "
"formulari web e de crear de nòvas sosmissions."

