"This screencast provides an overview of how to use webform variants to "
"create A/B tests, audience segmentation, and personalization."
msgstr ""
"Aquel screencast balha una vista d'ensemble sus cossí utilizar las "
"variants de formularis web per crear de tests A/B, de segmentacion "
"d'audiéncia e de personnalizacion."

msgid ""
"Webform module now supports variants, which can be used for A/B tests, "
"segmentation, and personalization"
msgstr ""
"Lo modulus Webform supòrta ara variants, que pòdon èsser utilizats "
"per d’estudis A/B, la segmentacion, e la personalizacion"

