msgstr "Configuracion : Variants"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Variants configuration</strong> page allows administrators "
"to enable/disable variants."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Configuracion de las variants</strong> permet als "
"administrators d'activar/desactivar las variants."

msgid ""
"<strong>Variants</strong> are used for A/B testing, segmentation, and "
"personalization."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Las variants</strong> son utilizadas per los tests A/B, la "
"segmentacion e la personalizacion."

msgid "Plugins: Variants"
msgstr "Plugins: Variantas"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Variants</strong> page allows variations of a webform to "
"be created and managed for A/B testing, segmentation, and "
"personalization."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Variants</strong> permet de crear e gerir de "
"variacions d'un formulari web per de tests A/B, de segmentacion e de "
"personalizacion."

