msgstr "Attributs compartits de pagina de formulari"

msgid "Default shared form theme"
msgstr "Tema per defaut de formulari partatjada"

msgid "Allows webforms to be shared on other websites using an iframe."
msgstr ""
"Permet que los formularis web sián partejats sus d'autres sites "
"utilizant un iframe."

msgid "Code copied to clipboard…"
msgstr "Còde copiat al copach."

msgid ""
"To test anonymous user access to the below embedded webform, please "
"log out or open the below link in a new private or incognito window."
msgstr ""
"Per testar l'accès anonime d'utilizaire al formulari web integrat "
"çai jos, vos cal desconnectar o dobrir lo ligam çai jos dins una "
"fenèstra novèla privada o incògnita."

msgid ""
"Choose how you want to embed the webform and then copy-n-paste the "
"below code snippet directly into the HTML source of any webpage."
msgstr ""
"Trieu cossí vòls integrar lo formulari web e puèi copia e pega lo "
"còde seguent dirèctament dins la sorga HTML de quina pagina web que "
"siá."

msgid ""
"Resizing iframe -- The embedded webform will be responsive and "
"adjusted to fit within the page using an iframe and JavaScript."
msgstr ""
"Redimensionament de l’iframe -- Lo formulari web integrat serà "
"responsiu e ajustat per s’adaptar a la pagina utilizant un iframe e "
"JavaScript."

msgid ""
"Fixed iframe -- The embedded webform will be a fixed size on the page "
"using an iframe with a scrollbar."
msgstr ""
"Iframe fixat -- Lo formulari integrat dins la pagina aurà una talha "
"fixa amb un iframe que compren una barra de desplaçament."

msgid "Resizing iframe code"
msgstr "Redimensionament del còdi iframe"

