msgid "Disable the tracking of user IP address"
msgstr "Desactivar lo seguiment de l’adreça IP de l’utilizaire"

msgid "Disable the tracking of user IP addresses for all webforms"
msgstr ""
"Desactivar lo seguiment dels adreças IP dels utilizaires per totes "
"las formularis web"

msgid "If checked, a user's IP address will not be recorded for all webforms."
msgstr ""
"Se seleccionat, l'adreça IP d'un utilizator serà pas registrada per "
"totes las formularis web."

msgid "Webforms for Everyone"
msgstr "Formularis web per totes"

msgid ""
"This presentation explores how site owners, site builders, and "
"developers can leverage the Webform module for Drupal 8 to build "
"complex and robust forms for their end-users."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta presentacion explora cossí los proprietaris de siti, los "
"constructors de siti e los desvolopaires pòdon utilizar lo modul "
"Webform per Drupal 8 per bastir de formularis complèxes e robustes "
"pels utilizaires finals."

msgid "Broken/missing webform variant plugin."
msgstr "Plugin de varianta de formarièr web perdut/romput."

msgid "<code>:htmldecode</code> decodes HTML entities in returned value."
msgstr ""
"<code>:htmldecode</code> decòda las entitats HTML dins la valor "
"retornada."

msgid "Hide the next button when auto-forwarding"
msgstr "Amaga lo boton seguent quand l'avançament es automatic"

msgid "Default delete button label"
msgstr "Etiqueta del boton de supression per defaut"

msgid ""
"Check if Webform Clientside Validation module is installed when using "
"the Clientside Validation module"
msgstr ""
"Verificatz se lo modul Webform Clientside Validation es installat "
"quand utilizatz lo modul Clientside Validation"

msgid "Webform: Clientside validation"
msgstr "Webform: Validacion client"

msgid "Webform Clientside Validation module installed."
msgstr "Module Webform Clientside Validation installat."

msgid "Webform Clientside Validation module not installed."
msgstr "Lo modulus Webform Clientside Validation es pas installat."

msgid ""
"The Webform Clientside Validation module helps support Webform "
"Clientside Validation integration. <a href=\":href\">Disable Webform "
"Clientside Validation warning</a>"
msgstr ""
"Lo modulus Webform Clientside Validation ajuda a sosténer "
"l'integracion de la validacion costat client de Webform. <a "
"href=\":href\">Desactivar l'avís de validacion costat client de "
"Webform</a>"

msgid "Helps support Webform Clientside Validation integration."
msgstr "Ajuda a sostenir l'integracion de la Validacion Clientside de Webform."

msgid "Show add element button"
msgstr "Afichar lo boton d'ajuda d'element"

msgid "If unchecked, the add button will be removed from each table row."
msgstr "Se desmarcat, lo boton d’ajuda serà removut de cada linha de taula."

msgid "If left blank all webforms will be listed in the select menu."
msgstr ""
"Se laissada vòlida, totes los formularis web seràn listats dins lo "
"menú de seleccion."

msgid ""
"This is displayed after a draft or submission has been saved to the "
"database. The delete button is also included within the submission "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Aquò s'aficha après qu'un esbós o una submissió aja estat "
"enregistrat dins la basa de donadas. Lo boton de supression es tanben "
"inclus dins las informacions de la submissió."

msgid "Open delete confirmation form in a modal dialog."
msgstr ""
"Dobrir lo formulari de confirmacion de supression dins una fenèstra "
"modala."

msgid "<code>:clear</code> removes the token when it is not replaced."
msgstr "<code>:clear</code> elimina lo token quand el es pas remplaçat."

msgid "Navigate between cards when the left or right arrow is pressed"
msgstr ""
"Desplaçatz-vos entre las cartas quand la frecha esquèrra o drecha es "
"premsada"

msgid "Include submission data"
msgstr "Incluir las donadas de sosmetut"

msgid "Display webforms as a top-level item in toolbar"
msgstr ""
"Afichar los formularis web coma un element de nivèl superior dins la "
"barra d'outils"

msgid "Navigate between cards using left or right arrow keys"
msgstr ""
"Navega entre las cartas en utilizant las frechas d'esquèrra o de "
"drecha"

msgid ""
"If checked, users will be able to move between cards using the left or "
"right arrow keys."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, los utilisaires podran se desplaçar entre las "
"cartas en utilisant las teclas de frecha esquerra o drecha."

msgid ""
"Display Webforms as a top-level administration menu item in the "
"toolbar"
msgstr ""
"Afichar los Webforms coma un element de menú d'administracion de "
"nivèl superior dins la barra d'espleches"

msgid ""
"If checked, the Webforms section will be displayed as a top-level "
"administration menu item in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Se aquesta opcion es marcada, la seccion Webforms serà mostrada coma "
"un element de menú d’administracion de nivèl superior dins la "
"barra d’outils."

msgid ""
"Computing complex or multiple values with or without Ajax can be "
"resource intensive and may have performance implications. When "
"possible try limiting or combining computations or consider using "
"custom Twig functions, JavaScript, or PHP."
msgstr ""
"Calcular de valors complexes o multiples amb o sens Ajax pòt èsser "
"intensiu en ressorsas e pòt aver d’implicacions sus la "
"performança. Quand es possible, ensajatz de limitar o combinar los "
"calculs o de considerar d’utilizar de foncions personalizadas en "
"Twig, JavaScript, o PHP."

msgid "Include submission properties"
msgstr "Inclure las proprietats de submissió"

msgid "Submitted properties and values are:"
