msgid "Select the webform that you would like to display in this block."
msgstr ""
"Seleccionatz lo formulari web que volètz afichar dins çò d'aqueste "
"blòc."

msgid "You can also use paragraphs tokens."
msgstr "Pòtz tanben utilizar de tokens de paragrafs."

msgid "Submit %title form"
msgstr "Enviar lo formulari %title"

msgid ""
"If unchecked, the element is never displayed. The element will only be "
"visible within the form builder and hidden from all other displays "
"including submission details, results, and download."
msgstr ""
"Se desmarcat, l’element es jamai mostrada. L’element serà pas "
"visible que dins lo constructor de formularis e serà causit de totes "
"los autres afichatges, comprés los detallhs de submissió, los "
"resultats e lo telecargament."

