msgstr "Webform: jQuery UI Selector de data"

msgid "Form elements attributes"
msgstr "Atributs dels elements del formulari"

msgid "Protect all webforms with Antibot"
msgstr "Protegjatz totes los formularis web amb Antibot"

msgid "Provided by the @plugin_id mail plugin."
msgstr "Fornit pel plugin de corrièr @plugin_id."

msgid ""
"Entered text will be displayed on the handlers administrative page and "
"replace this handler's default description."
msgstr ""
"Lo tèxt entrat serà afichat en la pagina administrativa dels "
"manipulaires e remplaçarà la descripcion per defaut d'aqueste "
"manipulador."

msgid "Entered text will be displayed on the variants administrative page."
msgstr ""
"Lo tèxt entrat serà afichat sus la pagina administrativa de las "
"variants."

msgid "Provides a form element to collect height in feet and inches."
msgstr ""
"Fòrnis un element de formulari per recuèlher l'alçada en pèças e "
"polzadas."

msgid "Allows users to view the Webform module's help page."
msgstr ""
"Permet als utilizaires de visualizar la pagina d'ajuda del mòdule "
"Webform."

msgid "Delete (token) URL"
msgstr "Suprimir l'URL (token)"

msgid ""
"The URL that can used to delete the webform submission. The webform "
"must be configured to allow users to delete a submission using a "
"secure token."
msgstr ""
"L'URL que pòt èsser utilizada per suprimir la sosmission del "
"formulari web. Lo formulari web deu èsser configurat per permetre als "
"utilizaires de suprimir una sosmission en utilizant un token segur."

msgid "Allow deleting a submission using token"
msgstr "Permetre la supression d’una mesa a jorn en utilizant un token"

msgid ""
"If checked users will be able to delete a submission using the "
"webform's URL appended with the submission's (secure) token."
msgstr ""
"Se es cochat, los utilizaires podràn suprimir una sosmission "
"utilizant l’URL del formulari web amb lo token (segur) de la "
"sosmission apondut."

msgid ""
"Only webforms that are open to new submissions can be deleted using "
"the secure token."
msgstr ""
"Solament los formularis web dobèrts a de nòvas sosmetudas pòdon "
"èsser suprimits en utilizant lo token segur."

