msgid "Translations"
msgstr "Traduccions"

msgid "A locally hosted document, such as a PDF file."
msgstr "Un document alojat localament, coma un fichièr PDF."

msgid "A locally hosted image file."
msgstr "Un fichièr d'imatge alojat localament."

msgid "A video hosted on an external site (for example, YouTube or Vimeo)."
msgstr "Un vidèo albergat sus un sit external (per exemple, YouTube o Vimeo)."

msgid "Webform submission operations bulk form"
msgstr "Operacions en massa sus formularis de sosmission de Webform"

msgid "Enable hoverIntent"
msgstr "Activar hoverIntent"

msgid ""
"Provides a workaround for the common problem that users with 'Use the "
"administration pages and help' permission see menu links they don't "
"have access permission for. Deprecated from Drupal 10.3 and above."
msgstr ""
"Propausa una solucion alternativa pel problèma comun que los "
"utilizaires amb la permession «Utilizar las paginas d'administracion "
"e l'ajuda» veián de ligams de menutro qu'an pas lo drech d'accedir. "
"Desalimata dempuèi Drupal 10.3 e versions superioras."

msgid "Admin Toolbar Search (Alt+a)"
msgstr "Rechercha de la barra d'aisinas d'administracion (Alt+a)"

msgid "Enable keyboard shortcut"
msgstr "Activar lo racòrt de claujera"

msgid "Enable keyboard shortcut (Alt + a)"
msgstr "Activar la racòrda clavièr (Alt + a)"

msgid "Enable toggle toolbar keyboard shortcut"
msgstr "Activar lo racourci clau per activar/desactivar la barra d'aisinas"

msgid "hoverIntent behavior"
msgstr "comportament hoverIntent"

msgid "hoverIntent timeout"
msgstr "delai de hoverIntent"

msgid "Hide Toolbar (Alt+p)"
msgstr "Amagar la barra d'aisinas (Alt+p)"

msgid "Toolbar sticky behavior"
msgstr "Comportament fixat de la barra d'aisinas"

msgid "Toolbar hoverIntent behavior"
msgstr "Comportament hoverIntent de la barra d'aisinas"

msgid "hoverIntent timeout (ms)"
msgstr "delai de hoverIntent (ms)"

msgid "Maximum depth of displayed nested menu items."
msgstr "Profondor màger dels elements de menús aninhats afichats."

msgid "<a href=\":hoverintent_src_url\" target=\"_blank\">hoverIntent</a>"
msgstr "<a href=\":hoverintent_src_url\" target=\"_blank\">hoverIntent</a>"

msgid ""
"The features of the <em>Admin Toolbar Links Access Filter</em> module "
"are included in Drupal core since version 10.3 and therefore "
"<strong>it should be uninstalled</strong>.<br>Since the module is no "
"longer needed, it <em>will</em> be removed in future releases of "
"<em>Admin Toolbar</em> when support for versions lower than 10.3 is "
"dropped.<br>\n"
"See issues: <a href=\":issue_url1\">#3463291</a> and <a "
"href=\":issue_url2\">#3487246</a>."
msgstr ""
"Las foncionalitats del module <em>Admin Toolbar Links Access "
"Filter</em> son inclosas dins lo nuclèu de Drupal dempuèi la version "
"10.3 e per consequent <strong>deuriá èsser "
"desinstaladas</strong>.<br>Coma lo module es mai besonh, serà "
"<em>remogat</em> dins las futuròlas versions de <em>Admin "
"Toolbar</em>, quand lo sopòrt per de versions inferioras a 10.3 "
"s’aubrirà.<br>\n"
"Vejatz las questions : <a "
"href=\":issue_url1\">#3463291</a> e <a "
"href=\":issue_url2\">#3487246</a>."

msgid ""
"If set, the search input will be focused when the user presses the "
"keys: \"Alt + a\".<br>Disable this setting if it conflicts with any "
"existing keyboard configuration."
msgstr ""
"Se definat, lo camp de recèrca serà focalizat quand l'utilizaire "
"preme las claus : \"Alt + a\".<br>Desactivatz aquela configuracion se "
"conflicta amb quina configuracion de clavèr existenta."

msgid ""
"The Admin Toolbar module provides a better user experience for the "
"default Drupal Toolbar.<br>It is a drop-down menu that allows quicker "
"access to all the administration pages in a more efficient way, with "
"fewer clicks and less scrolling.<br><br>The following settings mostly "
"provide advanced configuration of the JavaScript behavior of the "
"Toolbar sticky and hoverIntent."
msgstr ""
"Lo module Admin Toolbar proveís una melhora experiéncia d'emplegar "
"per la barra d'otís per defaut de Drupal.<br>Es un menú desplegable "
"que permet un accès mai rapid a totas las paginas d'administracion "
"d'una manièra mai eficaça, amb mens de clics e mens de "
"desgalatge.<br><br>Las configuracions seguentas proveisson mai que mai "
"una configuracion avançada del comportament JavaScript de la barra "
"pegadissa (sticky) e de hoverIntent."

msgid ""
"By default, the Admin Toolbar sticky behavior is <em>enabled</em> so "
"it stays at the top of the browser window when scrolling up or "
"down.<br>Select <em>Disabled</em> to disable Admin Toolbar's sticky "
"behavior so it stays at the top of the page when scrolling up/down and "
"does not follow the browser window."
msgstr ""
"Per defaut, lo comportament <em>sticky</em> de la Barra "
"d'Administracion es <em>activat</em> per que demòra en naut de la "
"fenestra del navegador en desplaçant cap amont o cap "
"avall.<br>Seleccionatz <em>Desactivat</em> per desactivar lo "
"comportament <em>sticky</em> de la Barra d'Administracion per que "
"demòre en naut de la pagina en desplaçant cap amont/avall e que "
"seguís pas la fenestra del navegador."

msgid ""
"If set, the toolbar will be hidden or visible when the user presses "
"the keys: \"Alt + p\".<br>Disable this setting if it conflicts with "
"any existing keyboard configuration."
msgstr ""
"Se es definit, la barra d'otisses se serà esconduda o visible quand "
"l'utilizaire preme las claus: \"Alt + p\".<br>Desactivar aquesta "
"preferéncia se conflictua amb quina que siá configuracion de "
"clavièr existenta."

msgid ""
"Provides a smoother user experience, where only menu items which are "
"paused over are expanded, to avoid accidental activations.<br>Disable "
"@hoverintent_source_link to use module's default basic JavaScript "
"behavior."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona una experiéncia d’utilizaire mai fluida, ont son "
"desvolopats sonque los elements de menú sus los quals se pausa lo "
"curseur, per evitar las activacions accidentalas.<br>Desactivatz "
"@hoverintent_source_link per utilizar lo comportament basic JavaScript "
"per defaut del module."

msgid ""
"Sets the hoverIntent trigger timeout (steps of 250).<br>The higher the "
"value, the longer the menu dropdown stays visible, after the mouse "
"moves out (default: 500ms)."
msgstr ""
"Define lo temps d'espera per activar hoverIntent (passas de "
"250).<br>Quant mai lo valor es naut, mai lo menu desplegable demòra "
"visibla après que la sorsa sortís (per defaut: 500ms)."

msgid "CKEditor Anchor Link"
msgstr "Enllaç ancorat de CKEditor"

msgid "CKEditor Web link"
msgstr "Ligam web de CKEditor"

msgid ""
"This plugin module adds the better link dialog and anchor related "
"features to CKEditor in Drupal 9"
msgstr ""
"Aqueste module de plugin apond lo dialògue de ligam melhorat e las "
"foncionalitats relatives als ancres a CKEditor dins Drupal 9"

msgid "#@anchor_link"
msgstr "#@anchor_link"

msgid "Anchor links (within the same page)"
msgstr "Enlaces d'ancres (dins la meteissa pagina)"

msgid "CKEditor Anchor link"
msgstr "Ligam d'ancora CKEditor"

msgid "Add a note to the backup"
msgstr "Apondre una remarca a la còpia de seguretat"

msgid "was due @time ago"
msgstr "aviá un retard de @time"

msgid "Created the %label Settings Profile."
msgstr "Profile de configuracion %label creat."

msgid "Saved the %label Settings Profile."
msgstr "Perfil de configuracion %label enregistrat."

msgid "Label for the Backup Source."
msgstr "Etiqueta per la sorga de còpia de seguretat."

msgid ""
"%title must contain only letters, numbers, dashes (-) and underscores "
"(_). And Site Tokens."
msgstr ""
"%title deu contenir solament de letras, nombres, tirets (-) e tresses "
"(_). E de Tokens del Site."

msgid "Use <a href=\"http://php.net/date\">PHP Date formatting</a>."
msgstr ""
"Utilizatz <a href=\"http://php.net/date\">lo formatatge de la data en "
"PHP</a>."

msgid "Label for the Backup Destination."
msgstr "Etiqueta per la Destinacion de la Copia de Seguretat."

msgid ""
"The number of backups to retain. Once this number is reached, the "
"oldest backup will be deleted to make room for the most recent backup. "
"Leave blank to keep all backups."
msgstr ""
"Lo nombre de còpias de seguretat a conservar. Una còp s'agísguèt "
"aqueste nombre, la còpia de seguretat la mai anciana serà suprimida "
"per far plaça a la còpia mai recenta. Deissatz en blanc per "
"conservar totes las còpias de seguretat."

msgid ""
"In order to encrypt backup files, please install the Defuse "
"PHP-encryption library via Composer with the following command: "
"<code>composer require defuse/php-encryption</code>. See the <a "
"href=\"@docs\">Defuse PHP Encryption Documentation Page</a> for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Per encriptar los fichièrs de còpia de seguritat, vos cal installar "
"la biblioteca Defuse PHP-encryption amb Composer en utilitzant la "
"comanda seguenta : <code>composer require "
"defuse/php-encryption</code>. Vejatz la <a href=\"@docs\">pagina de "
"documentacion Defuse PHP Encryption</a> per mai d'informacions."

msgid "All backups"
msgstr "Totes las còpias de seguritat"

msgid "Restore completed at @time"
msgstr "Restauracion terminada a @time"

msgid "Schedules Tab"
msgstr "Tabulador de Programacions"

msgid "Download Backup"
msgstr "Telecargar la còpia de seguretat"

msgid "Choose the backup source."
msgstr "S causissètz la sorga de la còpia de seguritat."

msgid "Choose the backup settings profile."
msgstr "Caulhètz lo perfil de las opcions de baraissa."

msgid "Choose the destination."
msgstr "Cal seleccionar la destinacion."

msgid "Choose the schedule backup you want to run."
msgstr "Causissètz la sòsta programada que desirat lançar."

msgid "Backup finished with failure"
msgstr "Copia de seguritat terminada amb error"

msgid "Exception Message: "
msgstr "Messatge d'excepcion:"

msgid ""
"The Backup Destination \"Download\" does not support taking the site "
"offline during backup."
msgstr ""
"La destinacion de sauvatge \"Descarregar\" pausa pas de metre lo site "
"fòra linha pendent la sauvatge."

msgid ""
"Keep CAPTCHA related counters in the <a href=\":statusreport\">status "
"report</a>. Note that this comes with a performance penalty as "
"updating the counters results in clearing the variable cache."
msgstr ""
"Mantenètz los contadors ligats al CAPTCHA dins lo <a "
"href=\":statusreport\">rapòrt d'estatut</a>. Notatz que aquò ven amb "
"una penalitat de performància pr'amor que la metuda a jorn dels "
"contadors entrena lo netejament de la cacha de variabla."

msgid ""
"Note that the CAPTCHA module interacts with page caching (see <a "
"href=\":performancesettings\">performance settings</a>). Because the "
"challenge should be unique for each generated form, the caching of the "
"page it appears on is prevented. Make sure that these forms do not "
"appear on too many pages or you will lose much caching efficiency. For "
"example, if you put a CAPTCHA on the user login block, which typically "
"appears on each page for anonymous visitors, caching will practically "
"be disabled. The comment submission forms are another example. In this "
"case you should set the <em>Location of comment submission form</em> "
"to <em>Display on separate page</em> in the comment settings of the "
"relevant <a href=\":contenttypes\">content types</a> for better "
"caching efficiency."
msgstr ""
"Cal notar que lo mòdule CAPTCHA interagís ambe lo cacha de las "
"paginas (veire <a href=\":performancesettings\">paramètres de "
"performància</a>). Coma lo desafi deu èsser unic per cada fòrmulari "
"generat, lo cacha de la pagina ont apareis es empeschat. Assegura-te "
"que aquelas fòrmularis apareisson pas sus tròp de paginas o perdràs "
"fòrça d’efi Cristianitat del cacha. Per exemple, se metas un "
"CAPTCHA sus lo blòc de connexiom de l’utilizaire, que de costuma "
"apareis sus cada pagina pels visitaires anonimats, lo cacha serà "
"practicament desactivat. Los fòrmularis de sosmetuda de comentaris "
"son un autre exemple. Dins aquò, deuves fixar lo <em>Lòc de "
"sosmetuda del fòrmulari de comentari</em> a <em>Afichar sus pagina "
"separada</em> dins los paramètres de comentari dels <a "
"href=\":contenttypes\">tipes de contengut</a> pertinents per una "
"melhora eficacitat del cacha."

msgid ""
"Users with the <em>Skip CAPTCHA</em> <a href=\":perm\">permission</a> "
"won't be offered a challenge. Be sure to grant this permission to the "
"trusted users (e.g. site administrators). If you want to test a "
"protected form, be sure to do it as a user without the <em>Skip "
"CAPTCHA</em> permission (e.g. as anonymous user)."
msgstr ""
"Los utilizaires amb la <em>Permission <em>Skip CAPTCHA</em></em> <a "
"href=\":perm\">non se los prepausarà un desafiament</a>. "
"Asseguratz-vos d'atribuir aquesta permission als utilizaires de "
"fisança (per exemple, administraires del sit). Se volètz ensajar un "
"fòrmulari protegit, asseguratz-vos de lo far coma un utilizaire sens "
"la permission <em>Skip CAPTCHA</em> (per exemple, coma utilizaire "
"anonim)."

msgid ""
"CAPTCHA session reuse attack detected on @form_id <br/>Posted CAPTCHA "
"token: @posted_captcha_token <br/>Expected captcha token: "
"@expected_captcha_token"
msgstr ""
"Ataca de reutilizacion de sessió CAPTCHA detectada sus @form_id "
"<br/>Token CAPTCHA publicat : @posted_captcha_token <br/>Token CAPTCHA "
"esperat : @expected_captcha_token"

msgid ""
"%form_id post blocked by CAPTCHA module: challenge %challenge (by "
"module %module)."
msgstr ""
"%form_id message enviat blocat pel module CAPTCHA : encastre "
"%challenge (per lo module %module)."

msgid ""
"Configurable error message that the user gets when it enters an "
"incorrect CAPTCHA answer."
msgstr ""
"Messatge d'error configurabla que l'utilizaire recep quand entra una "
"responsa CAPTCHA incorrècta."

msgid ""
"Lower and upper IP addresses should be different. Please correct range "
"%ip_range."
msgstr ""
"Las adreiças IP inferioras e superioras devon èsser diferentas. "
"Corrègiatz lo domeni %ip_range, mercé."

msgid ""
"A CAPTCHA can be added to virtually any Drupal form, through adding an "
"affiliated <em>CAPTCHA Point</em>. Some default <em>CAPTCHA "
"Points</em> are already provided in the <em>CAPTCHA Point</em> "
"section, but arbitrary forms can be easily added and managed."
msgstr ""
"Un CAPTCHA pòt èsser apondut a gaireben qualsevol formulari de "
"Drupal, per l'ajuda d'una <em>punt CAPTCHA</em> afiliada. D'unes "
"<em>punts CAPTCHA</em> de defaut son ja provesides dins la seccion "
"<em>punt CAPTCHA</em>, mas se pòdon tanben apondre e administrar "
"aisidament de formularis arbitraris."

msgid ""
"Enter one IP-address per row in the format XXX.XXX.XXX.XXX. "
"Alternatively you can also define IP-address ranges per row in the "
"format XXX.XXX.XXX.YYY-XXX.XXX.XXX.ZZZ. No spaces allowed. Your "
"current IP address is %ip_address."
msgstr ""
"Metzètz una adreça IP per linha dins lo format XXX.XXX.XXX.XXX. "
"Alternativament, pòtz tanben definir de tranches d’adreças IP per "
"linha dins lo format XXX.XXX.XXX.YYY-XXX.XXX.XXX.ZZZ. Pas d’espaci "
"permetut. vòstra adreça IP actuala es %ip_address."

msgid "Reload Captcha"
msgstr "Recargar Captcha"

msgid "Overlay close"
msgstr "Serrar la superposicion"

msgid "Custom (with tokens)"
msgstr "Personalizat (amb tokens)"

msgid ""
"For token support the <a href=\"@token_url\">token module</a> must be "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Per lo supòrt dels tokens, lo <a href=\"@token_url\">modul token</a> "
"deu èsser installat."

msgid "Plain (mainly for images)"
msgstr "Simple (sopretot per las imatges)"

msgid "Enable closing Colorbox by clicking on the background overlay."
msgstr "Activar la clausura de Colorbox en clicar sus l'envelopa de fons."

msgid ""
"If the Colorbox should be displayed in a fixed position within the "
"visitor's viewport or relative to the document."
msgstr ""
"Se lo Colorbox deu èsser afichat dins una posicion fixa dins la "
"fenestra del visitador o relativa al document."

msgid "Mobile detection"
msgstr "Deteccion mòbil"

msgid "Content image style of first image: @style"
msgstr "Estil d’imatge de contengut de la primièra imatge : @style"

msgid "Node style first"
msgstr "Estil del node primièr"

msgid "Colorbox is already present at @path. No download required."
msgstr "Colorbox es ja present a @path. Cap de telecargament necessari."

msgid ""
"Drush was unable to download the colorbox library from @remote. "
"@exception"
msgstr ""
"Drush a pas pogut telecargar la librariá colorbox dempuèi @remote. "
"@exception"

msgid "Error: unable to unzip colorbox file."
msgstr "Error: impossibla de descomprimir lo fichièr colorbox."

msgid "The colorbox library has been successfully downloaded to @path."
msgstr "La biblioteca colorbox a estat telecargada amb succès a @path."

msgid "Drush was unable to load the colorbox library"
msgstr "Drush a pas pogut cargar la biblioteca colorbox"

msgid ""
"You can find new features in the <a href=\"@url_colorbox_load\" "
"target=\"blank\">Colorbox Load</a> and <a "
"href=\"@url_colorbox_inline\" target=\"blank\">Colorbox Inline</a>"
