msgid "DOMPurify is already present at @path. No download required."
msgstr "DOMPurify es ja present a @path. Cap de telecargament necessari."

msgid ""
"Drush was unable to download the DOMPurify library from @remote. "
"@exception"
msgstr ""
"Drush a pas pogut telecargar la biblioteca DOMPurify dempuèi @remote. "
"@exception"

msgid "Error: unable to unzip DOMPurify file."
msgstr "Error : impossible de descompactar lo fichièr DOMPurify."

msgid "The DOMPurify library has been successfully downloaded to @path."
msgstr "La biblioteca DOMPurify foguèt telecargada amb succès a @path."

msgid "Drush was unable to load the DOMPurify library"
msgstr "Drush a pas pogut cargar la biblioteca DOMPurify"

msgid ""
"The DOMPurify library is not installed. The Colorbox module uses this "
"library to sanitize HTML captions. Without this library, all captions "
"will be treated as plain text. If you intend to have HTML captions in "
"Colorbox content, download the <a href=\"@url\">DOMPurify library</a>, "
"extract it, and copy the dist directory into the /libraries/DOMPurify "
"folder in your Drupal installation directory. Specifically, the system "
"looks for /libraries/DOMPurify/dist/purify.min.js. <br /><br /> To "
"avoid potential security issues, please only install the dist "
"directory, and not any other files from the archive.<br /><br /> If "
"you do not intend to use HTML captions, you can suppress this warning "
"on the <a href=\"@config\">Colorbox configuration page.</a>"
msgstr ""
"La biblioteca DOMPurify es pas installada. Lo modulo Colorbox utiliza "
"aquesta biblioteca per sanitar las legendas HTML. Sens aquesta "
"biblioteca, totas las legendas seràn tractadas coma tèxt simple. Se "
"volètz aver de legendas HTML dins lo contengut Colorbox, telecargatz "
"la <a href=\"@url\">biblioteca DOMPurify</a>, descompressatz-la, e "
"copiatz lo repertòri dist dins lo repèrtòri /libraries/DOMPurify de "
"vòstra installacion Drupal. Especificament, lo sistèma cercarà "
"/libraries/DOMPurify/dist/purify.min.js. <br /><br /> Per evitar "
"d'eventualas problems de seguretat, mercés d'installar sonque lo "
"repertòri dist, e pas d'autres fichièrs de l'archiu.<br /><br /> Se "
"tenètz pas d'emplegar de legendas HTML, podètz suprimir aqueste "
"messatge d'error a la <a href=\"@config\">pagina de configuracion de "
"Colorbox.</a>"

msgid ""
"The DOMPurify library is installed. This library will sanitize HTML in "
"Colorbox captions."
msgstr ""
"La bibliotèca DOMPurify es installada. Aquesta bibliotèca "
"desinfectarà l’HTML dins las legends de Colorbox."

msgid ""
"The <a href=\"@dompurify_link\">DOMPurify</a> library is not "
"installed. This library is necessary if you want to use HTML in "
"Colorbox captions. Without it, all captions will be treated as plain "
"text."
msgstr ""
"La biblioteca <a href=\"@dompurify_link\">DOMPurify</a> es pas "
"instalada. Aquesta biblioteca es necessària se volètz utilizar de "
"tèxte HTML dins las legendas de Colorbox. Sens aquesta, totas las "
"legendas seràn tractadas coma de tèxte pla."

msgid ""
"By default, a warning appears on Drupal's status report if this "
"library is missing. Check this box to suppress the warning."
msgstr ""
"Per defaut, un avertiment apareis dins lo rapòrt d'estat de Drupal se "
"aquesta biblioteca manca. Causissètz aquesta caissa per suprimir "
"l'avertiment."

