msgid ""
"This setting controls how complicated the configuration is. If you do "
"not have a use-case for a more advanced set-up the recommendation is "
"to keep it simple."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta configuracion contròla coma es complicat l'ajustament. Se "
"avètz pas de cas d'utilizacion per una configuracion mai avançada, "
"la recomanacion es de la demorar simpla."

msgid "The configuration ignored in all cases"
msgstr "La configuracion ignorada dins totes los cases"

msgid ""
"One configuration name per line.<br />\n"
"Examples: "
"<ul>\n"
"<li>user.settings</li>\n"
"<li>views.settings</li>\n"
"<li>contact.settings</li>\n"
"<li>webform.webform.* "
"(will ignore all config entities that starts with "
"<em>webform.webform</em>)</li>\n"
"<li>*.contact_message.custom_contact_form.* "
"(will ignore all config entities that starts with "
"<em>.contact_message.custom_contact_form.</em> like fields attached to "
"a custom contact form)</li>\n"
"<li>* (will ignore "
"everything)</li>\n"
"<li>~webform.webform.contact (will force import for "
"this configuration, even if ignored by a "
"wildcard)</li>\n"
"<li>user.mail:register_no_approval_required.body "
"(will ignore the body of the no approval required email setting, but "
"will not ignore other user.mail "
"configuration.)</li>\n"
"<li>language.*|* (will ignore all language "
"collections)</li>\n"
"<li>language.fr|* (will ignore all fr language "
"collection)</li>\n"
"<li>language.fr|field.field.* (will ignore all fr "
"field "
"translations)</li>\n"
"<li>~language.fr|field.field.media.file.field_media_file "
"(will force import for certain field "
"translation)</li>\n"
"<li>language.*|system.site:name (will ignore just "
"the site name but in all translations)</li>\n"
"</ul>"
msgstr ""
"Un nom de configuracion per linha.<br />\n"
"Exemples: "
"<ul>\n"
"<li>user.settings</li>\n"
"<li>views.settings</li>\n"
"<li>contact.settings</li>\n"
"<li>webform.webform.* "
"(s’aplicarà pas a totas las entitats de configuracion que comencen "
"per "
"<em>webform.webform</em>)</li>\n"
"<li>*.contact_message.custom_contact_form.* "
"(s’aplicarà pas a totas las entitats de configuracion que comencen "
"per <em>.contact_message.custom_contact_form.</em> coma los camps "
"apenduts a un formulari de contacte personalizat)</li>\n"
"<li>* "
"(s’aplicarà a tot)</li>\n"
"<li>~webform.webform.contact (forçarà "
"l’importacion d’aquesta configuracion, quitament se es ignorada "
"per un "
"asteròscop)</li>\n"
"<li>user.mail:register_no_approval_required.body "
"(s’aplicarà pas al contengut del messatge de l’emails sens "
"necessitat d’aprovacion, mas s’aplicarà pas a d’autras "
"configuracions dins user.mail.)</li>\n"
"<li>language.*|* (s’aplicarà "
"pas a totas las colleccions de lenga)</li>\n"
"<li>language.fr|* "
"(s’aplicarà pas a tota la colleccion de lenga "
"francesa)</li>\n"
"<li>language.fr|field.field.* (s’aplicarà pas a "
"tota la traduccion dels camps en "
"francés)</li>\n"
"<li>~language.fr|field.field.media.file.field_media_file "
"(forçarà l’importacion d’una traduccion d’un camp en "
"particular)</li>\n"
"<li>language.*|system.site:name (s’aplicarà "
"solament al nom del site dins totas las traduccions)</li>\n"
"</ul>"

