msgid "Chaos Tools Views"
msgstr "Chaos Tools Views"

msgid ""
"This suite is primarily a set of APIs and tools to improve the "
"developer experience. It also contains a module called the Page "
"Manager whose job is to manage pages. In particular it manages panel "
"pages, but as it grows it will be able to manage far more than just "
"Panels."
msgstr ""
"Aquela pròva es principalament un ensems d’APIs e d’otisses per "
"melhorar l’experiéncia del desvelopaire. Conten tanben un modèl "
"nomenat Page Manager que son ròtle es de gerir las paginas. En "
"particular, gere las paginas amb panèls, mas a mesura que creis, "
"podrà gerir fòrça mai que sonque los Panèls."

msgid ""
"Plugins -- tools to make it easy for modules to let other modules "
"implement plugins from .inc files."
msgstr ""
"Plugins -- aisinas per facilitar als modules de daissar a d'autres "
"modules d'implantar de plugins dempuèi de fichièrs .inc."

msgid ""
"Exportables -- tools to make it easier for modules to have objects "
"that live in database or live in code, such as \"default views\"."
msgstr ""
"Exportables -- aisinas per facilitar als modules d’avèir "
"d’objèctes que viason dins la basa de donadas o dins lo còde, coma "
"per exemple las « views per defaut »."

msgid ""
"AJAX responder -- tools to make it easier for the server to handle "
"AJAX requests and tell the client what to do with them."
msgstr ""
"AJAX responder -- aisinas per facilitar al servidor lo tractament de "
"demandas AJAX e indicar al client çò que cal ne far."

msgid "Form tools -- tools to make it easier for forms to deal with AJAX."
msgstr ""
"Outils de formularis -- outils per facilitar lo tractament de l’AJAX "
"dins los formularis."

msgid ""
"Object caching -- tool to make it easier to edit an object across "
"multiple page requests and cache the editing work."
msgstr ""
"Cache d'objècte -- utís per facilitar l'ediccion d'un objècte a "
"travèrs de mantunas requisicions de pagina e per emmagazinar en cache "
"lo trabalh d'ediccion."

msgid ""
"Contexts -- the notion of wrapping objects in a unified wrapper and "
"providing an API to create and accept these contexts as input."
msgstr ""
"Contexts -- la nocion d'encapar d'objèctes dins un encapsulament "
"unificat e de provesir una API per crear e acceptar aqueles contexts "
"coma entraïnas."

msgid ""
"Modal dialog -- tool to make it simple to put a form in a modal "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Dialog modala -- aisina per simplificar l'inseriment d'un formulari "
"dins una dialog modala."

msgid ""
"Dependent -- a simple form widget to make form items appear and "
"disappear based upon the selections in another item."
msgstr ""
"Dependent -- un widget de formulari simple per far aparéisser e "
"desaparéisser los elements del formulari segon las causidas dins un "
"autre element."

msgid ""
"Content -- pluggable content types used as panes in Panels and other "
"modules like Dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Contengut -- tipes de contengut enplugables utilizats coma panèls "
"dins Panels e d'autres modules coma Dashboard."

msgid "Form wizard -- an API to make multi-step forms much easier."
msgstr ""
"Enchantaire de formularis -- una API per simplificar fòrça la "
"creacion de formularis amb divèrses passes."

msgid ""
"CSS tools -- tools to cache and sanitize CSS easily to make user-input "
"CSS safe."
msgstr ""
"Outils CSS -- outils per metre en memòria e sanefiar facilament lo "
"CSS per far que lo CSS inserit pels utilizaires siá segur."

