"l’index de recèrca siá actualizat."

msgid "The vendor directory \"@dir\" is not writable."
msgstr "Lo repertòri del venedor \"@dir\" es pas escrivable."

msgid ""
"The CKEditor 5 \"%cke5_media_plugin_label\" plugin's "
"\"%cke5_allow_view_mode_override_label\" setting should be in sync "
"with the \"%filter_media_plugin_label\" filter's "
"\"%filter_media_allowed_view_modes_label\" setting: when checked, two "
"or more view modes must be allowed by the filter."
msgstr ""
"Lo reglament \"%cke5_allow_view_mode_override_label\" del plugin "
"\"%cke5_media_plugin_label\" de CKEditor 5 deu estar en sincronia amb "
"lo reglament \"%filter_media_allowed_view_modes_label\" del filtre "
"\"%filter_media_plugin_label\" : quand es activat, lo filtre deu "
"autorizar doas o mai de modes de vista."

msgid "Allowed entity types"
msgstr "Tipus d’entitats autorizadas"

msgid ""
"The Drupal application's codebase must be writable in order to use "
"Automatic Updates. This includes Drupal core, modules, themes and the "
"Composer dependencies in the <code>vendor</code> directory. This makes "
"Automatic Updates incompatible with some hosting platforms."
msgstr ""
"La basa de còdi de l'aplicacion Drupal deu èsser en accès "
"d'escritura per utilizar las Mises a Jorn Automatica. Aquò compren lo "
"nuclèu de Drupal, los modules, los tèmas e las dependéncias "
"Composer dins lo repertòri <code>vendor</code>. Aquò fa que las "
"Mises a Jorn Automatica son incompatiblas amb quitas plataformas "
"d'ostalatge."

msgid ""
"Staged changes failed to apply, and the site is in an indeterminate "
"state. It is strongly recommended to restore the code and database "
"from a backup."
msgstr ""
"Los cambiaments en estapa an fracassat a se aplicar, e lo siti es dins "
"un estat indeterminat. Es fortament recomanat de restaurar lo còde e "
"la basa de donadas dempuèi una còpia de securitat."

msgid ""
"Post-apply tasks are running in the same request during which staged "
"changes were applied to the active code base. This can result in "
"unpredictable behavior."
msgstr ""
"Las tasques post-aplicacion s'executan dins la meteissa demanda ont "
"los cambiaments preparats foguèron aplicats a la basa de còdi "
"activa. Aquò pòt resultà en un comportament imprevisible."

msgid ""
"API module providing functionality to stage package installs and "
"updates with Composer."
msgstr ""
"Module API fornissent de foncionalitats per preparar l'installacion e "
"la mesa a jorn de paquets amb Composer."

msgid "There is not enough disk space to create a stage directory."
msgstr "I a pas pro d'espaci sus lo disc per crear un repertòri d'etapa."

msgid ""
"The stage directory has @stage_count instances of @stage_info_file as "
"compared to @active_count in the active directory. This likely "
"indicates that a duplicate extension was installed."
msgstr ""
"Lo repertòri de l'escala a @stage_count instàncias de "
"@stage_info_file comparat a @active_count dins lo repertòri actiu. "
"Aquò indica probablament que s'es installada una extension duplicada."

msgid ""
"The stage directory has @stage_count instances of @stage_info_file. "
"This likely indicates that a duplicate extension was installed."
msgstr ""
"Lo repertòri de l’escenari a @stage_count instàncias de "
"@stage_info_file. Aquò indica probable qu’una extenssion duplicada "
"foguèt installada."

msgid "The stage root directory will not able to be created at \"@dir\"."
msgstr "Lo repertòri racina de l'estadi pas de poder èsser creat a \"@dir\"."

msgid "The stage root directory \"@dir\" is not writable."
msgstr "Lo repertòri racina de l’estadi \"@dir\" es pas escrivable."

msgid ""
"It only allows supported Composer plugins. If you have any, see <a "
"href=\"#package-manager-faq-unsupported-composer-plugin\">What if it "
"says I have unsupported Composer plugins in my codebase?</a>."
msgstr ""
"Solament permet los plugins Composer suportats. Se n'en tenètz, veja "
"<a href=\"#package-manager-faq-unsupported-composer-plugin\">Que faire "
"se m’indica que ai de plugins Composer pas suportats dins mon "
"còde?</a>."

msgid ""
"If <code>cweagans/composer-patches</code> is installed, it must be "
"defined as a dependency of the main project (i.e., it must be listed "
"in the <code>require</code> or <code>require-dev</code> section of "
"<code>composer.json</code>). You can run the following command in your "
"site root to add it as a dependency of the main project:"
msgstr ""
"Se <code>cweagans/composer-patches</code> es installat, deu èsser "
"definit coma una dependéncia del projècte principal (es a dire, deu "
"èsser listat dins la seguida <code>require</code> o "
"<code>require-dev</code> de <code>composer.json</code>). Pòtz "
"lançar la comanda seguent al rengal del vòstre sit per l'ajotar coma "
"dependéncia del projècte principal:"

msgid "Cannot claim the stage because no stage has been created."
msgstr ""
"Impossible de reclamar lo scenari pr'amor qu'aucun scenari a pas estat "
"creat."

msgid ""
"All composer plugins are allowed because "
"<code>config.allow-plugins</code> is configured to <code>true</code>. "
"This is an unacceptable security risk."
msgstr ""
"Totes los plugins composer son autorizats pr'amor que "
"<code>config.allow-plugins</code> es configurat a <code>true</code>. "
"Aquò representa un risc de seguritat inacceptabla."

msgctxt "Validation"
msgid "Extension exists"
msgstr "L'extension existís"

msgid ""
"The breakpoint group typically only needs a single breakpoint with an "
"empty media query in order to do <em>viewport sizing.</em> Multiple "
"breakpoints are used for changing the crop or aspect ratio of images "
"at different viewport sizes, which is often referred to as <em>art "
"direction.</em> A new breakpoint group should be created for each "
"aspect ratio to avoid content shift. Once you select a breakpoint "
"group, you can choose which breakpoints to use for the responsive "
"image style. By default, the option <em>do not use this "
"breakpoint</em> is selected for each breakpoint. See the <a "
"href=\":breakpoint_help\">help page of the Breakpoint module</a> for "
"more information."
msgstr ""
"Lo grop de punts de ruptura necessitat normalament solament un sol "
"punt de ruptura amb una consulta media vidanta per realizar lo "
"<em>dimensionament de la fenèstra d'afichatge.</em> Diveses punts de "
"ruptura son utilizats per cambiar lo recuèlh o lo rapòrt d'aspecte "
"d'imatges a diferents tailladas de fenèstra, çò que s'apèla sovent "
"<em>dirección artistica.</em> Un grop de punts de ruptura novèl "
"deurà èsser creat per cada rapòrt d'aspecte per evitar lo "
"desplaçament del contengut. Un còp que seleccionatz un grop de punts "
"de ruptura, podètz causir quines punts utilizar pel estil d'imatge "
"responsive. Per defecte, l'opcion <em>utilizar pas aqueste punt de "
"ruptura</em> es seleccionada per cada punt de ruptura. Consultatz la "
"<a href=\":breakpoint_help\">pagina d'ajuda del mòdule Breakpoint</a> "
"per mai d'informacions."

msgid ""
"Composer must be configured for secure downloads. This means that <a "
"href=\":disable-tls\">the <code>disable-tls</code> option</a> must be "
"<code>false</code>, and <a href=\":secure-http\">the "
"<code>secure-http</code> option</a> must be <code>true</code> in the "
"<code>config</code> section of your <code>composer.json</code> file. "
"If these options are not set in your <code>composer.json</code>, "
"Composer will behave securely by default. To set these values at the "
"command line, run the following commands:"
msgstr ""
"Composer deu èsser configurat per de telecargaments segurs. Aquò "
"vòl dire que <a href=\":disable-tls\">l’opcion "
"<code>disable-tls</code></a> deu èsser <code>false</code>, e <a "
"href=\":secure-http\">l’opcion <code>secure-http</code></a> deu "
"èsser <code>true</code> dins la seccion <code>config</code> del "
"vòstre fichièr <code>composer.json</code>. Se aquelas opcions son "
"pas definidas dins vòstre <code>composer.json</code>, Composer se "
"comportarà de biais segur per defaut. Per definir aqueles valors a la "
"linha de comanda, lançatz las comandas seguentes :"

msgid "Problem detected in lock file during stage operations."
msgid_plural "Problems detected in lock file during stage operations."
msgstr[0] ""
"Problema detectat dins lo fichièr de blocatge pendent las operacions "
"de mòstra.  \n"
"Pròbles detectats dins lo fichièr de blocatge "
"pendent las operacions de mòstra."

msgid ""
"The stage directory is not protected by PHP-TUF, which is required to "
"use Package Manager securely."
msgstr ""
"Lo repertòri de l'estadi es pas protegut per PHP-TUF, que's necessari "
"per utilizar lo Gestor de Paquets de biais segur."

msgid ""
"There appear to be no pending Composer operations because the active "
"lock file (@active_file) and the staged lock file (@staged_file) are "
"identical."
msgstr ""
"Sembla qu'i a pas d'operacions Composer pendentas pr’amor que lo "
"fichièr de bloqueig activ (@active_file) e lo fichièr de bloqueig en "
"estadi (@staged_file) son idèntics."

msgid "The field %field has been deleted from the %type %source_label."
msgstr "Lo camp %field foguèt suprimat del %type %source_label."

msgid "Stage directory cleaner"
msgstr "Netjador de repertòris de fasa"

msgid ""
"Include unrecognized files and directories in the project root in "
"staging operations"
msgstr ""
"Inclure los fichièrs e repertòris pas reconeguts dins la raca del "
"projecte dins las operacions d'estagiari."

msgid "Rebuild content access permissions"
msgstr "Reconstruïr las permissions d'accès al contengut"

msgid ""
"The @name config object does not contain any translatable values, so "
"it should not specify a language code."
msgstr ""
"L'objècte de configuracion @name conten pas de valors traducibles, "
"alara deuria pas especificar de còde de lenga."

msgid ""
"Path of a file to which Composer Stager process output should be "
"logged"
msgstr ""
"Camin d’un fichièr ont se deu registrar la sortida del procés "
"Composer Stager"

msgid "TUF is not enabled for the <code>@url</code> repository."
msgstr "TUF es pas activat pel repositori <code>@url</code>."

msgid ""
"The Layout Builder Expose All Field Blocks module is a Feature Flag "
"module which exposes all fields on all bundles as field blocks for use "
"in Layout Builder."
msgstr ""
"Lo module Layout Builder Expose All Field Blocks es un module Feature "
"Flag que fa aparéisser totes los camps sus totes los elements coma "
"blòcs de camps per èsser utilizats dins Layout Builder."

msgid ""
"For example, if Layout Builder is enabled on a Node bundle (Content "
"type), and that bundle's display is using field blocks from the User "
"entity (e.g. the Author's name), but Layout Builder is not enabled for "
"the User bundle, then that field block would no longer exist after "
"uninstalling this module."
msgstr ""
"Per exemple, se Layout Builder es activat sus un grop de Nodes (tipe "
"de contengut), e que l'aficha d’aquel grop utilisa de blòcs de "
"camps de l'entitat Utilizaire (per exemple, lo nom de l'autor), mas "
"Layout Builder es pas activat per lo grop Utilizaire, alara aquel "
"blòc de camp desapareisserà se desinstallatz aqueste modulus."

msgid ""
"You can <em>only</em> add workflows on the <a "
"href=\":workflows\">Workflows page</a>, after you have installed a "
"module that leverages the API such as the <a "
"href=\":moderation\">Content Moderation module</a>."
msgstr ""
"Pòdes <em>solament</em> apondre de flux de trabalh a la <a "
"href=\":workflows\">pagina Flux de trabalh</a>, après aver installat "
"un module que utiliza l'API coma lo <a href=\":moderation\">module de "
"Moderacion de Contengut</a>."

msgid ""
"You can <em>only</em> add workflows on the <a "
"href=\":workflows\">Workflows page</a>, after you have installed a "
"module that leverages the API such as the Content Moderation module."
msgstr ""
"Pòdes <em>solament</em> apondre de flux de trabalh sus la <a "
"href=\":workflows\">pagina de Flux de trabalh</a>, après que siás "
"installat un modèl que utiliza l’API coma lo modèl de Moderacion "
"de Contengut."

msgid ""
"A workflow requires at least two states. States can be added when you "
"add or edit a workflow on the <a href=\":workflows\">Workflows "
"page</a>."
msgstr ""
"Un flux de trabalh requer almens doas estats. Los estats pòdon èsser "
"aponduts quand ajustatz o edita un flux de trabalh sus la <a "
"href=\":workflows\">pagina de Fluxes de trabalh</a>."

msgid ""
"A transition defines in which state an item can be save as next. It "
"has one destination state, but can have several states <em>from</em> "
"which the transition can be applied. Transitions can be added when you "
"add or edit a workflow on the <a href=\":workflows\">Workflows "
"page</a>."
msgstr ""
"Una transicion definís dins quin estat un element pòt èsser "
"enregistrat coma seguissent. Ten un estat de destinacion, mas pòt "
"aver mantuns estats <em>de</em> los quals la transicion se pòt "
"aplicar. Las transicions se pòdon dobrir quand afichatz o editez un "
"flus de trabalh a la <a href=\":workflows\">pagina dels flus de "
"trabalh</a>."

msgid ""
"The UploadProgress PHP extension must be enabled to configure the "
"progress indicator. Check the <a href=\":status\">status report</a> "
"for more information."
msgstr ""
"L’extension PHP UploadProgress deu èsser activada per configurar "
"l’indicador de progèss. Contraròtz lo <a href=\":status\">rapòrt "
"d’estat</a> per mai d’informacions."

msgid "Whether or not to enable TLS opportunistically (defaults to true)."
msgstr "Per activar o non TLS de biais oportunista (valon per defaut a vert)."

msgid "Whether or not to enforce TLS (defaults to false)."
msgstr "Que s'impausar o pas TLS (per defaut, es pas activat)."

msgid "Bind to a specific IPv4 or IPv6 address (no default)."
msgstr ""
"Ligar-se a una adreça IPv4 o IPv6 especifica (pas de valor per "
"defaut)."

msgid "Installed %module module."
msgid_plural "Installed %module modules."
msgstr[0] ""
"Modulo %module installat.  \n"
"Moduls %module installats."

msgid "Set property of a config entity"
msgstr "Definir la proprietat d'una entitat de configuracion"

msgid "This value is not a valid extension name."
msgstr "Aquesta valor n'es pas un nom d'extension valid."

msgid "Menu link depth"
msgstr "Profondor del ligam del menú"

msgid "Preprocess callback is not valid: %error."
msgstr "La retorcha de preprocesament es pas valida : %error."

msgid "IdenticalTo"
msgstr "IdenticAmb"

msgctxt "Validation"
msgid "At least one of"
msgstr "Almens un de"

msgctxt "Validation"
msgid "Call a method on a service"
msgstr "Amaga un metòde sus un servici"

msgid "Plays Inline"
msgstr "Jòga en linha"

msgid "Plays Inline: %playsinline"
msgstr "Jòga en linha: %playsinline"

msgid ""
"The core Language module lets you add new languages to your site, "
"provides the <em>Language switcher</em> block, and provides the "
"ability to configure block visibility by language; the block and block "
"visibility settings are only available if you have multiple languages "
"configured. The core Content Translation, Configuration Translation, "
"and Interface Translation modules let you translate content, "
"configuration, and the built-in user interface, respectively. The core "
"Locale module manages automatic downloads of community-provided "
"translations of default configuration and user-interface text if the "
"core Update Status module is installed. See the related topics listed "
"below for specific tasks."
msgstr ""
"Lo module central Lengatge vos permet d’ajustar de novèlas lengas a "
"vòstre siti, provesís lo blòque <em>Comutator de lenga</em>, e "
"balha la capacitat de configurar la visibilitat dels blòques segon la "
"lenga; la configuracion del blòque e de sa visibilitat es disponibla "
"sonque se avètz mantuna lenga configurada. Los modules centrals "
"Traduccion de contengut, Traduccion de configuracion e Traduccion "
"d’interfàcia vos permeton respectivament de tradusir lo contengut, "
"la configuracion, e l’interfàcia integrala d’usuario. Lo module "
"central Locala gerís los telecargaments automatizats de traduccions "
"provesidas per la comunitat per la configuracion per defècte e los "
"tèxtes de l’interfàcia d’usuario se lo module central Estat de "
"telecargament es installat. Consultatz los subjèctes ligats aicí jos "
"per de tasques especificas."

msgid ""
"Wait for the translation system to be updated. Also, if you have the "
"core Update Status module installed and translations are available for "
"your language, wait for translations to be downloaded. You should be "
"returned to the <em>Languages</em> page when this completes."
msgstr ""
"Espèra que lo sistèma de traduccion siá actualizat. tanben, se as "
"installat lo module principal Update Status e que de traduccions son "
"disponiblas per ta lenga, espèra que las traduccions sián "
"telecargadas. Deuriás èsser redirigit a la pagina <em>Languages</em> "
"quand aquò es acabat."

msgid "Ignoring already imported translation for %project."
msgstr "Ignorant la traduccion ja importada per %project."

msgid ""
"Obsolete. All the functionality has been moved to the navigation "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Obsolet. Tota la foncionalitat a estat desplaçada al mòde de "
"navegacion."

msgid ""
"Forms and links inside the content of the layout builder tool are "
"disabled in Edit mode."
msgstr ""
"Los formularis e los ligams dins lo contengut de l'aisina de bastidor "
"de maqueta son desactivats en mòde d'Edicion."

msgid "@state_label (@active_state_label available)"
msgstr "@state_label (@active_state_label disponible)"

msgid "Page Context"
msgstr "Contexte de la pagina"

msgid "Administrative top bar"
msgstr "Bara superiora administrativa"

msgid "This filter has no effect because the %module module controls access."
msgid_plural ""
"This filter has no effect because these modules control access: "
"%modules."
msgstr[0] ""
"Aqueste filtre a pas d'efièch pr'amor que lo %module es lo modòl que "
"contraròtla l'accès.  \n"
"Aqueste filtre a pas d'efièch pr'amor que "
"son aquestes modòls que contraròtlan l'accès : %modules."

msgid "Content status filter"
msgstr "Filtres d'estat del contengut"

msgid "Redundant filters detected"
msgstr "Filtres redondants detectats"

msgid ""
"The %view view uses the %status_filter filter but it has no effect "
"because the following module(s) control access: %modules. Review and "
"consider removing the filter."
msgid_plural ""
"The following views use the %status_filter filter but it has no effect "
"because the following module(s) control access: %modules. Review and "
"consider removing the filter from these views: @views"
msgstr[0] ""
"La vista %view utiliza lo filtre %status_filter mas es sens efècte "
"pr’amor que los moduls seguents contròlan l’acces: %modules. "
"Revisa e considera de suprimir lo filtre.\n"
"\n"
"Las vistas seguentas "
"utilizan lo filtre %status_filter mas es sens efècte pr’amor que "
"los moduls seguents contròlan l’acces: %modules. Revisa e considera "
"de suprimir lo filtre d’aquestas vistas: @views"

msgid "Direct-write is enabled. Skipping sandboxing."
msgstr "L'escritura dirècta es activada. Sautam lo confinament."

msgid ""
"Direct-write is enabled. Changes have been made to the running code "
"base."
msgstr ""
"L'escritura directa es activada. De cambiaments an estat fach dins la "
"basa de còde en execucion."

msgid ""
"Direct-write mode is enabled, which means that changes will be made "
"without sandboxing them first. This can be risky and is not "
"recommended for production environments. For safety, your site will be "
"put into maintenance mode while dependencies are updated."
msgstr ""
"Lo mòde d'escritura directa es activat, çò que vòl dire que las "
"modificacions seràn realizadas sens las previsualizar primièr. Aquò "
"pòt èsser riscat e es pas recomandat per d'entorns de produccion. "
"Per seguritat, vòstre siti serà plaçat en mòde de mantenença "
"pendent la mesa a jorn de las dependéncias."

msgid "The sandbox directory is a subdirectory of the active directory."
msgstr "Lo dorsièr sandbox es un susdorsièr del dorsièr actiu."

msgid "The pg_trgm PostgreSQL extension is present."
msgstr "L'extension pg_trgm de PostgreSQL es present."

msgid "%profile_name (%profile%version)"
msgstr "%profile_name (%profile%version)"

msgid ""
"Drupal is unable to generate highly randomized numbers, which means "
"certain security features like password reset URLs are not as secure "
"as they should be. Instead, only a slow, less-secure fallback "
"generator is available. The most likely cause is that open_basedir "
"restrictions are in effect and /dev/urandom is not on the allowed "
"list. See the <a href=\":drupal-php\">system requirements</a> page for "
"more information. %exception_message"
msgstr ""
"Drupal es pas capable de generar de nombres fòrça aleatòrisats, "
"çò que vòu dire que de foncionalitats de seguretat utilizadas per "
"exemples per los URLs de reinitializacion de senhalas son pas tan "
"seguras coma devrián èsser. Al contrari, un generador lent e mens "
"segur es disponibil coma sol solucien de repli. Lo motiu mai probable "
"es que las restriccions open_basedir son en vigor e que /dev/urandom "
"es pas dins la lista autorizada. Consultatz la pagina <a "
"href=\":drupal-php\">requisits del sistèma</a> per mai "
"d’informacions. %exception_message"

msgid ""
"Update notifications are not enabled. It is <strong>highly "
"recommended</strong> that you install the Update Status module from "
"the <a href=\":module\">module administration page</a> in order to "
"stay up-to-date on new releases. For more information, <a "
"href=\":update\">Update status handbook page</a>."
msgstr ""
"Las notificacions de mesa a jorn son pas activadas. Es "
"<strong>fortament recomandat</strong> d'installar lo mòdule Update "
"Status dempuèi la <a href=\":module\">pagina d'administracion dels "
"mòduls</a> per demorar informat de las novèlas versions. Per mai "
"d'informacion, <a href=\":update\">pagina del manual de l'estat de "
"mesa a jorn</a>."

msgid ""
"If you have the core Update Status module installed, in the "
"<em>Manage</em> administrative menu, navigate to <em>Reports</em> &gt; "
"<em>Available updates</em> to see a report of the updates that are "
"available for your site software. If <em>Last checked</em> is far in "
"the past, click <em>Check manually</em> to update the report. Scan the "
"report; if the core software or any modules or themes have security "
"updates available, you should update them as soon as possible."
msgstr ""
"Se tenètz lo mòdule essencial Update Status installat, dins lo menú "
"administratiu <em>Manage</em>, anatz a <em>Reports</em> &gt; "
"<em>Available updates</em> per véser un rapòrt de las actualizacions "
"disponiblas per lo logicial de vòstre site. Se <em>Last checked</em> "
"es luènh dins lo passat, clicatz sus <em>Check manually</em> per "
"metre a jorn lo rapòrt. Escanejatz lo rapòrt ; se lo logicial "
"essencial o qualques mòduls o tematicas an de recambis de seguretat "
"disponiblas, cal que los actualizetz lo pus lèu possible."

msgid ""
"Regularly review available updates and update as required to maintain "
"a secure and current site. Always run the <a "
"href=\":update-php\">update script</a> each time a module is updated. "
"Install the <a href=\":update-status\">Update Status module</a> to see "
"a report of available releases for Drupal Core and contributed modules "
"and themes."
msgstr ""
"Revisatz regularament las mesas a jorn disponiblas e actualizatz atal "
"que necessari per mantenir un sitèl segur e actualizat. Executatz "
"totjorn l’<a href=\":update-php\">script de mesa a jorn</a> cada "
"còp qu’un modulus es actualizat. Installatz l’<a "
"href=\":update-status\">modulus Estat de Mesa a Jorn</a> per véser un "
"rapòrt de las versiones disponiblas per lo Nuclèu de Drupal e los "
"moduls e tèmas contribuïts."

msgid "Update Status settings"
msgstr "Modificar los paramèstres d’estatut"

msgid ""
"The Update Status module periodically checks for new versions of your "
"site's software (including contributed modules and themes), and alerts "
"administrators to available updates. The Update Status system is also "
"used by some other modules to manage updates and downloads; for "
"example, the Interface Translation module uses the Update Status to "
"download translations from the localization server. Note that whenever "
"the Update Status system is used, anonymous usage statistics are sent "
"to Drupal.org. If desired, you may uninstall the Update Status module "
"from the <a href=\":modules\">Extend page</a>; if you do so, "
"functionality that depends on the Update Status system will not work. "
"For more information, see the <a href=\":update\">online documentation "
"for the Update Status module</a>."
msgstr ""
"Lo module Update Status verifica periodicament se i a cap de nòvas "
"versions del softwar del vòstre sit (incluent los modules e temes "
"contribuïts), e alèrta los administrators quand i a d'actualizacions "
"disponibles. Lo sistèma Update Status es tanben utilizat per quauques "
"autres modules per gerir las actualizacions e los telecargaments; per "
"exemple, lo module Interface Translation utiliza Update Status per "
"telecargar las traduccions dempuèi lo servidor de localizacion. "
"Notatz que cada còp que lo sistèma Update Status es utilizat, "
"d’estatisticas d’utilizacion anonimament son mandadas a "
"Drupal.org. Se voletz, poètz desinstal·lar lo module Update Status "
"dempuèi la <a href=\":modules\">pagina Estendre</a>; se o fasètz, "
"las foncionalitats que dependon del sistèma Update Status que mai, "
"foncionaran pas. Per mai d’informacions, veiatz la <a "
"href=\":update\">documentacion en linha del module Update Status</a>."

msgid ""
"The <a href=\":update-report\">Available updates report</a> displays "
"core, contributed modules, and themes for which there are new releases "
"available for download. On the report page, you can also check "
"manually for updates. You can configure the frequency of update "
"checks, which are performed during cron runs, and whether "
"notifications are sent on the <a href=\":update-settings\">Update "
"Status settings page</a>."
msgstr ""
"Lo <a href=\":update-report\">rapòrt d'actualizacions disponiblas</a> "
"mòstra los centres, los modules contribuïts, e los tèmas pels quals "
"i a de nòvas versions disponiblas per telecargar. Dins la pagina del "
"rapòrt, podètz tanben verificar manualament las actualizacions. "
"Podètz configurar la frequència de las verificacions "
"d'actualizacions, que son realizadas pendent las execucions de cron, e "
"se las notificacions son mandatadas a la <a "
"href=\":update-settings\">pagina de configuracion de l'Estatut "
"d'Actualizacions</a>."

msgid ""
"The core User module allows users to register, log in, and log out, "
"and administrators to manage user roles and permissions. Depending on "
"which modules you have installed on your site, the related topics "
"below will help you with tasks related to managing user accounts and "
"visitors."
msgstr ""
"Lo mòdule central Utilizaire permet als utilizaires de se registrar, "
"se connectar e se desconectar, e als administrators de gerir los "
"ròtles e las autorizacions dels utilizaires. En foncion dels mòduls "
"que tenètz installats sus vòstre site, los tèmas ligats a seguire "
"vos ajudaràn dins las tasques que concernisson la gestion dels "
"comptes utilizaires e dels visitaires."

