"The layout for %label will be reverted to its default state. All "
"layout modifications and inline blocks wil be reset."
msgstr ""
"La maqueta per %label serà revertida a son estat defòrt. Totas las "
"modificacions de maqueta e los blòcs en linha seràn reinitializats."

