msgid ""
"The topic of the resource. Typically, the subject will be represented "
"using keywords, key phrases, or classification codes. Recommended best "
"practice is to use a controlled vocabulary. To describe the spatial or "
"temporal topic of the resource, use the Coverage element."
msgstr ""
"Lo subjècte de la ressorsa. Generalament, lo subjècte serà "
"representat en utilitzant de mots-claus, de frasas clausas, o de "
"còdis de classificacion. La melhora practica recomandada es "
"d’utilizar un vocabulari controlat. Per descriure lo subjècte "
"espacial o temporal de la ressorsa, utilisatz l’element Coverage."

msgid ""
"An account of the resource. Description may include but is not limited "
"to: an abstract, a table of contents, a graphical representation, or a "
"free-text account of the resource."
msgstr ""
"Un compte rendut de la ressorsa. La descripcion pòt incluir, mas sens "
"s’i limitar, un abstracte, una taula de contenguts, una "
"representacion grafica, o un compte rendut en tèxt liure de la "
"ressorsa."

msgid ""
"An entity responsible for making the resource available. Examples of a "
"Publisher include a person, an organization, or a service. Typically, "
"the name of a Publisher should be used to indicate the entity."
msgstr ""
"Una entitat responsables de render la ressorsa disponibla. "
"D’exemples d’un Editor comprenon una persona, una organizacion, o "
"un servici. Normalament, lo nom de l’Editor deu èsser utilizat per "
"indicar l’entitat."

msgid ""
"An entity responsible for making contributions to the resource. "
"Examples of a Contributor include a person, an organization, or a "
"service. Typically, the name of a Contributor should be used to "
"indicate the entity."
msgstr ""
"Una entitat responsabla de far de contribucions al ròtle. D'exemples "
"d'un Contribuidor comprenon una persona, una organizacion, o un "
"servici. Normalament, lo nom d'un Contribuidor deu èsser utilizat per "
"indicar l'entitat."

msgid ""
"A point or period of time associated with an event in the lifecycle of "
"the resource. Date may be used to express temporal information at any "
"level of granularity.  Recommended best practice is to use an encoding "
"scheme, such as the W3CDTF profile of ISO 8601 [W3CDTF]."
msgstr ""
"Un punt o una periode de temps associat a un eveniment dins lo cicle "
"de vida de la ressorsa. La data pòt èsser utilizada per exprimir "
"d’informacions temporalas a quina que siá nivèu de granularitat. "
"La practica recòrdala recomanada es d’utilizar un esquema "
"d’encodatge, tal coma lo perfil W3CDTF de l’ISO 8601 [W3CDTF]."

msgid ""
"The file format, physical medium, or dimensions of the resource. "
"Examples of dimensions include size and duration. Recommended best "
"practice is to use a controlled vocabulary such as the list of "
"Internet Media Types [MIME]."
msgstr ""
"Lo format del fichièr, lo mèdia fisic, o las dimensios del ressors. "
"D'exemples de dimensios inclutzon la talha e la durada. La millor "
"practica recomanada es d’utilizar un vocabulàri controlat coma la "
"lista dels Tipes de Mèdia Internet [MIME]."

msgid ""
"An unambiguous reference to the resource within a given context. "
"Recommended best practice is to identify the resource by means of a "
"string conforming to a formal identification system."
msgstr ""
"Una referéncia non ambigua al recors dins un contèxt donat. La bona "
"practica recomandada es d'identificar lo recors per mejan d'una cadena "
"conforma a un sistèma formal d'identificacion."

msgid ""
"A related resource from which the described resource is derived. The "
"described resource may be derived from the related resource in whole "
"or in part. Recommended best practice is to identify the related "
"resource by means of a string conforming to a formal identification "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Una ressorsa relacionada de la qual la ressorsa descricha es derivada. "
"La ressorsa descricha pòt èsser derivada de la ressorsa relacionada "
"en tot o en partida. La practica recomandada mai bona es d'identificar "
"la ressorsa relacionada metent en òbra una cadena conforma a un "
"sistèma formal d'identificacion."

msgid ""
"A related resource. Recommended best practice is to identify the "
"related resource by means of a string conforming to a formal "
"identification system."
msgstr ""
"Un recors relacionat. La melhora practica recomandada es "
"d’identificar lo recors relacionat per un string conform a un "
"sistèma d’identificacion formal."

msgid ""
"The spatial or temporal topic of the resource, the spatial "
"applicability of the resource, or the jurisdiction under which the "
"resource is relevant. Spatial topic and spatial applicability may be a "
"named place or a location specified by its geographic coordinates. "
"Temporal topic may be a named period, date, or date range. A "
"jurisdiction may be a named administrative entity or a geographic "
"place to which the resource applies. Recommended best practice is to "
"use a controlled vocabulary such as the Thesaurus of Geographic Names "
"[TGN]. Where appropriate, named places or time periods can be used in "
"preference to numeric identifiers such as sets of coordinates or date "
"ranges."
msgstr ""
"Lo subjècte espacial o temporal de la ressorsa, l'aplicabilitat "
"espaciala de la ressorsa, o la jurisdiccion jos la quala la ressorsa "
"es pertinent. Lo subjècte espacial e l'aplicabilitat espaciala pòdon "
"èsser un endrech nomenat o una locacion especificada per sas "
"còrdonadas geograficas. Lo subjècte temporal pòt èsser una epòca "
"nomenada, una data, o una durada dins lo temps. Una jurisdiccion pòt "
"èsser una entitat administrativa nomenada o un endrech geografic al "
"que la ressorsa s'aplica. La bona practica recomandada es d'utilizar "
"un vocabulari controlat coma lo Thesaurus of Geographic Names [TGN]. "
"Ont es adaptat, los endreches o periòdes de temps nomenats pòdon "
"èsser utilizats en preferéncia als identifiants numerics coma de "
"conjunt de còrdonadas o de duradas dins lo temps."

msgid ""
"Information about rights held in and over the resource. Typically, "
"rights information includes a statement about various property rights "
"associated with the resource, including intellectual property rights."
msgstr ""
"Informacions sus los dreits tenuts dins e sus la ressorsa. "
"Generalament, las informacions sus los dreits includisson una "
"declaracion a prepaus dels diferents dreits de proprietat associats a "
"la ressorsa, inclusent los dreits de proprietat intlectuala."

msgid ""
"A description that concisely summarizes the content of the page, as "
"appropriate for presentation within a Tweet. Do not re-use the title "
"text as the description, or use this field to describe the general "
"services provided by the website. The string will be truncated, by "
"Twitter, at the word to 200 characters."
msgstr ""
"Una descripcion que resume de manièra concisa lo contengut de la "
"pagina, coma es adaptat per èsser presentat dins un Tweet. Daissatz "
"pas reusar lo títol coma descripcion, ni d'utilizar aqueste camp per "
"descriure los servicis generaus provesits pel sit web. La cadena serà "
"truncada per Twitter a la paraula 200 caractèrs."

