msgstr ""
"Un ensems de meta etiquetas especialament per controlar de "
"foncionalitats avançadas amb Facebook."

msgid "Open Graph: Video Secure URL"
msgstr "Open Graph : URL Segura del Vidèo"

msgid ""
"The height of the above video(s). Note: if both the unsecured and "
"secured videos are provided, they should both be the same size."
msgstr ""
"L'alçada del(s) vidèo(s) ci-dessus. Remarca : se los vidèos sens "
"seguretat e securizats son fornits, devon aver la meteissa grandor."

msgid "Video Secure URL"
msgstr "URL segura del vidèo"

