msgstr "Etiqueta personalizada %label creada."

msgid "Updated %label Custom tag."
msgstr "Etiqueta personalitzada %label actualizada."

msgid "Edit Custom tag @label"
msgstr "Editar etiqueta personalizaa @label"

msgid ""
"These custom tags are designed to use the custom purpose on the "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Aquestes balisas personalizadas son concebudas per utilizar l'objècte "
"personalizat sus lo site web."

msgid "The entities routes metatags must be added by fields."
msgstr ""
"Las metatags de las rotas d'entitats devon èsser apondudas pels "
"camps."

msgid "Trimming options"
msgstr "Opcions de talhadura"

msgid ""
"A list of characters to trim at the end of all metatags. Provide a "
"single string without any separators, e.g. \"|,.\" (instead of \"| , "
".\"). Note that spaces, tabs, new lines, carriage returns and vertical "
"tabs (\" \\n"
"\\r\\t\\v\") will be trimmed automatically and do not "
"need to be listed in this field. The trimming is applied at the very "
"end after the tag is trimmed for length, and after the trimming option "
"was executed."
msgstr ""
"Una lista de caractèrs per talhar al final de totes los metatags. "
"Fornissètz una cadena unica sens cap de separadors, per exemple "
"\"|,.\" (en luòc de \"| , .\"). Remarcatz que los espacis, las "
"tabulacions, las linhas novèlas, los retorns de carrièra e las "
"tabulacions verticalas (\" \\n"
"\\r\\t\\v\") seràn talhadas "
"automaticament e devon pas èsser indicadas dins aqueste camp. La "
"talhada s'aplica al final après que lo tag siá talhat per longor, e "
"après que l’opcion de talhada siá estada executada."

msgid "Configuration instance"
msgstr "Instància de configuracion"

msgid ""
"Meta tag configuration, stored as either a serialized array or a "
"JSON-encoded string."
msgstr ""
"Configuracion de la balisa meta, estocada coma una taula serializada o "
"una cadena codificada en JSON."

msgid "Expected an array but got null or other type for group: @group_name"
msgstr ""
"Esperava una taula mas obtenguèt null o un autre tipe per lo grop : "
"@group_name"

msgid "Optional suffix to add"
msgstr "Sufís opcional a ajustar"

msgid "Element of the HTML tag. e.g. meta, link, etc."
msgstr "Element de la balisa HTML. Ex.: meta, link, etc."

msgid ""
"The name of the html value attribute. e.g. content, href, charset, "
"etc."
msgstr ""
"Lo nom de l'atribut de valor html. per exemple content, href, charset, "
"etc."

msgid ""
"Enter a unique identifier for this custom tag. This identifier can "
"contain lowercase letters, numbers and underscores. This is only used "
"internally, it is not used in the actual HTML output."
msgstr ""
"Metetz un identificant unic per aquesta etiqueta personalizabla. "
"Aqueste identifiant pòt conténer de letras minusculas, de nombres e "
"de basetgs. Es utilizat solament en intern, es pas utilizat dins la "
"sortida HTML efectiva."

msgid ""
"Select the Value attribute of the Custom tag. This determines which "
"HTML attribute will contain the user-provided content."
msgstr ""
"Seleccionatz l'atribut Value de l'etiqueta Custom. Aquò determina "
"quin atribut HTML contindrà lo contengut proporcionat per "
"l'utilizador."

msgid ""
"Define the HTML attributes for this custom meta tag. The first "
"attribute serves as the primary identifier and is required. Additional "
"attributes are optional and provide fixed values for all instances of "
"this tag."
msgstr ""
"Definissètz los atributs HTML per aquesta etiqueta meta personalizaa. "
"Lo primièr atribut servís d'identificador principal e es necessari. "
"D'autres atributs son opcionals e forniscan de valors fixes per totas "
"las instàncias d'aquesta etiqueta."

msgid "Primary attribute (Required)"
msgstr "Atribut primièr (Necessari)"

msgid "Additional attribute @num"
msgstr "Atribut adicional @num"

msgid "This attribute identifies the meta tag and is required."
msgstr "Aquesta atribut identifica la meta balisa e es necessari."

msgid "This attribute provides a fixed value for all instances of this tag."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta atribut provesís una valor fix per totas las instàncias "
"d'aqueste etiqueta."

msgid "Common values: name, property, rel, http-equiv, itemprop."
msgstr "Valors comunas: name, property, rel, http-equiv, itemprop."

msgid "Additional attribute name (e.g., type, sizes)."
msgstr "Nom d'attribut adicional (per exemple, type, talhas)."

msgid ""
"For new tags, defaults to the machine name. For existing tags, this "
"identifies the specific meta tag."
msgstr ""
"Per las nòvas etiquetas, utiliza per defaut lo nom de la maquina. Per "
"las etiquetas existentas, aquò identifica l’etiqueta meta "
"especifica."

msgid "Fixed value for this attribute."
msgstr "Valor fixada per aqueste atribut."

msgid ""
"\n"
"        <h4>Common Examples:</h4>\n"
"        <ul>\n"
"          "
"<li><strong>Basic meta tag:</strong><br>\n"
"            Primary "
"attribute: name = \"description\"<br>\n"
"            Result: &lt;meta "
"name=\"description\" content=\"[user-input]\" /&gt;</li>\n"
"          "
"<li><strong>Open Graph tag:</strong><br>\n"
"            Primary "
"attribute: property = \"og:title\"<br>\n"
"            Result: &lt;meta "
"property=\"og:title\" content=\"[user-input]\" /&gt;</li>\n"
"          "
"<li><strong>Twitter Card:</strong><br>\n"
"            Primary "
"attribute: name = \"twitter:card\"<br>\n"
"            Result: &lt;meta "
"name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"[user-input]\" /&gt;</li>\n"
"          "
"<li><strong>Link with type:</strong><br>\n"
"            Primary "
"attribute: rel = \"icon\"<br>\n"
"            Additional attribute: type "
"= \"image/svg+xml\"<br>\n"
"            Result: &lt;link rel=\"icon\" "
"type=\"image/svg+xml\" href=\"[user-input]\" /&gt;</li>\n"
"        "
"</ul>\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"<h4>Exemples comuns :</h4>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"  <li><strong>Meta etiqueta basica "
":</strong><br>\n"
"    Atribut principal : name = \"description\"<br>\n"
" "
"   Resultat : &lt;meta name=\"description\" content=\"[user-input]\" "
"/&gt;</li>\n"
"  <li><strong>Etiqueta Open Graph :</strong><br>\n"
"    "
"Atribut principal : property = \"og:title\"<br>\n"
"    Resultat : "
"&lt;meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"[user-input]\" /&gt;</li>\n"
"  "
"<li><strong>Carta Twitter :</strong><br>\n"
"    Atribut principal : "
"name = \"twitter:card\"<br>\n"
"    Resultat : &lt;meta "
"name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"[user-input]\" /&gt;</li>\n"
"  "
"<li><strong>Enlac amb tipe :</strong><br>\n"
"    Atribut principal : "
"rel = \"icon\"<br>\n"
"    Atribut suplementari : type = "
"\"image/svg+xml\"<br>\n"
"    Resultat : &lt;link rel=\"icon\" "
"type=\"image/svg+xml\" href=\"[user-input]\" /&gt;</li>\n"
"</ul>"

