msgid ""
"Uncheck this if you intend to only regenerate the sitemaps manually or "
"via drush."
msgstr ""
"Descocheu aquò se pensatz tornar regenerar los sitemaps manualament o "
"per drush solament."

msgid "Default sitemap generator"
msgstr "Generador de mapa de siti per defecte"

msgid "Generates a standard conform hreflang sitemap of your content."
msgstr ""
"Genera una mapa de sitio hreflang estandard conforma per vòstre "
"contengut."

msgid "Generating XML sitemaps"
msgstr "Generar de cartes XML del site"

msgid "Progress of sitemap regeneration"
msgstr "Progrés de la regeneracion de la mapa del siti"

msgid "Sitemaps"
msgstr "Plan de siti"

msgid "Simple XML Sitemap PHP extensions"
msgstr "Extensions PHP per de mapas XML simplics"

msgid ""
"In order to be able to generate sitemaps, the Simple XML Sitemap "
"module requires the <em>xmlwriter</em> PHP extension to be enabled."
msgstr ""
"Per èsser capable de generar sitemaps, lo modul Simple XML Sitemap "
"demanda que l’extension PHP <em>xmlwriter</em> siá activada."

msgid "Include a stylesheet in the sitemaps for humans"
msgstr "Inclure una tala de estilos dins los sitemaps destinats als umans"

msgid "Simple XML Sitemap (Views)"
msgstr "Mapa de siti XML simpla (Vistas)"

msgid ""
"Provides integration of the Simple XML Sitemap module with the Views "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Provesís l'integracion del modòl Simple XML Sitemap amb lo modòl "
"Views."

msgid ""
"No view displays are set to be indexed yet. <a href=\"@url\">Edit a "
"view.</a>"
msgstr ""
"Cap de vista d'afichatge es pas encara configurat per èstre indexat. "
"<a href=\"@url\">Modificar un afichatge.</a>"

msgid "The priority this display will have in the eyes of search engine bots."
msgstr ""
"La prioritat que aquesta presentacion aurà als uèlhs dels robots "
"dels motors de recèrca."

msgid "Maximum display variations"
msgstr "Variacions màgeras d'afichatge"

msgid ""
"The maximum number of link variations to be indexed for this display. "
"If left blank, each argument will create link variations for this "
"display. Use with caution, as a large number of argument values​can "
"significantly increase the number of sitemap links."
msgstr ""
"Lo nombre maximal de variacions de ligams a indexar per aquela "
"visualizacion. Se demorat vidèis, cada argument crearà de variacions "
"de ligams per aquela visualizacion. Utilizatz amb precaucion, pr'amor "
"qu'un grand nombre de valors d’argument pòt augmentar "
"significantament lo nombre de ligams dins la carta del siti."

msgid "Resume generation"
msgstr "Generacion de currículum vitae"

msgid "Add styling and sorting to sitemaps"
msgstr "Ajustatz l’estil e lo tri alas mapas de siti"

msgid ""
"If checked, sitemaps will be displayed as tables with sortable entries "
"and thus become much friendlier towards human visitors. Search engines "
"will not care."
msgstr ""
"Se marcada, las cartes de site se mostraràn jos forma de taulas amb "
"d’entradas triablas, çò que las farà plan mai amistosas pels "
"visitaires umans. Los motors de recèrca s’en preocuparàn pas."

msgid ""
"If checked, entity links are generated exclusively for languages the "
"entity has been translated to as long as the language is not excluded "
"below.<br>Otherwise entity links are generated for every language "
"installed on the site apart from languages excluded below.<br>Bear in "
"mind that non-entity paths like homepage will always be generated for "
"every non-excluded language."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, los ligams d'entitat son generats exclusivament per "
"las lengas que l'entitat a estadas traduchas tant que la lenga es pas "
"exclusa çai jos.<br>D'un autre biais, los ligams d'entitat son "
"generats per cada lenga installada sus lo siti a l'excepcion de las "
"lengas exclusas çai jos.<br>Cal remembrar que los camin non-entitat "
"coma la pagina d'aculh generats totjorn per cada lenga non-exclusa."

msgid ""
"On some hosting providers it is impossible to pass parameters to cron "
"to tell Drupal which URL to bootstrap with. In this case the base URL "
"of sitemap links can be overridden here.<br>Example: <em>@url</em>"
msgstr ""
"Es impossible amb qualques provesidors d'ostalatge de passar de "
"parametres au cron per indicar a Drupal quina URL utilizar per lo "
"bootstrap. Dins aquel cas, la URL de basa dels ligams de sitemap pòt "
"èsser substituïda ici.<br>Exemple : <em>@url</em>"

msgid ""
"The maximum duration <strong>in seconds</strong> the generation task "
"can run during a single cron run or during one batch process "
"iteration.<br>The higher the number, the quicker the generation "
"process, but higher the risk of PHP timeout errors."
msgstr ""
"La durada màger <strong>en segondas</strong> que la tasca de "
"generacion pòt durar pendent una sola execucion de cron o pendent una "
"iteracion d'un procès en massa.<br>Mai lo nombre es naut, mai lo "
"procès de generacion es rapid, mas mai es alçat lo risc d'errors de "
"temps d'espera de PHP."

msgid ""
"Administer Simple XML Sitemap settings, alter inclusion settings of "
"content and generate sitemaps on demand."
msgstr ""
"Administrar las configuracions de Simple XML Sitemap, modificar las "
"configuracions d'inclusion del contengut e generar de planhs de sit en "
"demanda."

msgid "Regenerate all sitemaps after hitting <em>Save</em>"
msgstr ""
"Regenerar totes los plans de site après aver clicat sus "
"<em>Enregistrar</em>"

msgid "Otherwise the sitemaps will be regenerated during a future cron run."
msgstr ""
"D'autra manièra, los sitemaps seràn regenerats pendent una execucion "
"futura del cron."

msgid ""
"The priority this <em>@bundle</em> entity will have in the eyes of "
"search engine bots."
msgstr ""
"La prioritat que aquesta entitat <em>@bundle</em> aurà als uèlhs "
"dels robots dels motors de recèrca."

msgid ""
"The frequency with which this <em>@bundle</em> entity changes. Search "
"engine bots may take this as an indication of how often to index it."
msgstr ""
"La frequéncia amb que aquesta entitat <em>@bundle</em> cambia. Los "
"bots dels motors de cèrca pòdon prene aquò coma una indicacion de "
"la regularitat amb que la indexar."

msgid ""
"Determines if images referenced by this <em>@bundle</em> entity should "
"be included in the sitemap."
msgstr ""
"Determina se las imatges referenciadas per aquela entitat "
"<em>@bundle</em> devon èsser inclosas dins la mapa del siti."

msgid "Simple XML Sitemap (Search engines)"
msgstr "Simple XML Sitemap (Moteurs de recèrca)"

msgid "Search engine ID"
msgstr "ID del fòrtz de recèrca"

msgid "Last submitted"
msgstr "Darrièr submés"

msgid "Sitemap search engine submission settings"
msgstr "Paramètres d'envois a las aisinas de recèrca pel plan del sit"

msgid "Sitemap submission enabled"
msgstr "Envoi de mapa dels sitis activat"

msgid "Sitemap submission frequency"
msgstr "Frequéncia de submissió del plan del site"

msgid "Sitemap search engine submission"
msgstr "Sometuda del plan del sit pels motors de recèrca"

msgid ""
"The maximum number of links one sitemap can hold. If more links are "
"generated than set here, a sitemap index will be created and the links "
"split into several sub-sitemaps.<br>50 000 links is the maximum Google "
"will parse per sitemap, but choosing a lower value may be needed to "
"avoid PHP memory errors on huge sites.<br>If left blank, all links "
"will be shown on a single sitemap."
msgstr ""
"Lo nombre maxim de ligams que pòt contenir un mapa de sit. Se mai de "
"ligams son generats que lo nombre fixat aicí, un index de mapa de sit "
"serà creat e los ligams seràn dividits dins divèrses sub-mapas de "
"sit.<br>50 000 ligams es lo maxim que Google analisarà per cada mapa "
"de sit, mas causir un valor mai baish pòt èsser necessari per evitar "
"d’errors de memoritatz PHP sus de sites fòrça grands.<br>Se "
"laissatz aqueste camp void, totes los ligams se mostraràn dins un sol "
"mapa de sit."

msgid "Configure, add content to and generate XML sitemaps."
msgstr "Configure, dobèrta contengut e genera planhs XML."

msgid "Disable language hreflang"
msgstr "Desactivar l’atribut hreflang de la lenga"

msgid "Remove hreflang markup in HTML"
msgstr "Suprimir la balisa hreflang dins HTML"

msgid ""
"Google recommends displaying hreflang definitions either in the HTML "
"markup or in the sitemap, but not in both places.<br>If checked, "
"hreflang definitions created by the language module will be removed "
"from the markup reducing its size."
msgstr ""
"Google recomanda de mostrar las definicions hreflang dins lo marcage "
"HTML o dins la mapa del situs, mas pas dins los dos endreches.<br> Se "
"la caseta es marcada, las definicions hreflang creatas pel modulus de "
"lenga seràn enlevadas del marcage per redusir son talhièr."

msgid "published on @time"
msgstr "publicat lo @time"

msgid "published on @time, regenerating"
msgstr "publicat lo @time, en regeneracion"

msgid ""
"The number of entities to process in each queue item.<br>Increasing "
"this number will use more memory but will result in less queries "
"improving generation speed."
msgstr ""
"Lo nombre d'entitats a tractar dins cada element de la "
"coa.<br>Augmentar aqueste nombre utilizarà mai de memòria mas "
"menarà a mens de consultas, melhorant la velocitat de generacion."

msgid "@indexed out of @total total queue items have been processed."
msgstr "@indexed de @total elements de la coa totala an estat tractats."

msgid ""
"All variants belonging to the built-in \"Default hreflang\" sitemap "
"type have been converted to entities. Custom sitemap types added via "
"plugins will have to be recreated manually. See "
"simple_sitemap.type.default_hreflang.yml. The sitemaps need to be "
"regenerated now."
msgstr ""
"Totas las variants que pertòcan al tipe de sitemap incorporat "
"\"Default hreflang\" foguèt convertidas en entitats. Los tipes de "
"sitemap personalizats aponduts per plugins devon èsser recriats "
"manualament. Vesiatz simple_sitemap.type.default_hreflang.yml. Cal ara "
"regenerar los sitemaps."

msgid "Sitemap types"
msgstr "Tipos de plan de site"

msgid "Sitemap generator"
msgstr "Generador de mapa del siti"

msgid "URL generators"
msgstr "Generadors d'URL"

msgid "Simple XML sitemap type"
msgstr "Tip de mapa de site XML simple"

msgid "Add sitemap type"
msgstr "Apondre un tipe de mapa del site"

msgid ""
"Choose which sitemaps are to be submitted to which search "
"engines.<br>Sitemaps can be configured <a href=\"@url\">here</a>."
msgstr ""
"Causissètz quines sitemaps devon èsser mandatats a quines motors de "
"recèrca.<br>Los sitemaps pòdon èsser configurats <a "
"href=\"@url\">aicí</a>."

msgid "No sitemaps have been defined yet. <a href=\"@url\">Add a new one</a>."
msgstr ""
"Aucun plan de site definýt encara. <a href=\"@url\">Apondre un de "
"nòu</a>."

msgid "Sitemap type"
msgstr "Type de mapa del siti"

msgid ""
"No sitemap types have been defined yet. <a href=\"@url\">Add a new "
"one</a>."
msgstr ""
"Cap de tipe de mapa del site es definit encara. <a "
"href=\"@url\">Apondre un nòu</a>."

msgid "sitemap"
msgstr "plan del sito"

msgid "sitemap type"
msgstr "típus de plan de site"

msgid "sitemap types"
msgstr "tipus de plan de website"

msgid ""
"At least one sitemap needs to be defined for a bundle to be "
"indexable.<br>Sitemaps can be configured <a href=\"@url\">here</a>."
msgstr ""
"Almens una mapa del site deu èsser definida per qu'un grop siá "
"indexable.<br>Las mapas del site pòdon èsser configuradas <a "
"href=\"@url\">aquí</a>."

msgid "Sitemap type %label has been updated."
msgstr "Lo tipe de mapa del site %label a estat actualizat."

msgid "Sitemap type %label has been created."
msgstr "Lo tipe de plan del site %label a estat creat."

msgid ""
"@indexed out of @total queue items have been processed.<br>Each "
"sitemap is published after all of its items have been processed."
msgstr ""
"@indexed dels @total elements de la coda an estat tractats.<br>Cada "
"plan de site ven publicat après que totes sas entitats sián estat "
"tractadas."

msgid "Sitemap index generator"
msgstr "Generador d'index de mapa del siti"

msgid ""
"In order to use the Simple XML Sitemap Views module, the Views URL "
"generator must be <a href=\"@url\">added</a> to a sitemap type."
msgstr ""
"Per utilizar lo module Simple XML Sitemap Views, lo generador d'URL de "
"Views deu èsser <a href=\"@url\">aquitat</a> a un tipe de plan de "
"sit."

msgid ""
"Please configure at least one <a href=\"@sitemaps_url\">sitemap</a> to "
"be of a <a href=\"@types_url\">type</a> that implements the views URL "
"generator."
msgstr ""
"Siás plan de configurar almens un <a "
"href=\"@sitemaps_url\">sitemap</a> d'un <a "
"href=\"@types_url\">type</a> que implementa lo generador d'URL per las "
"vistas."

msgid "Included in sitemaps: "
msgstr "Inclús dins los sitemaps :"

msgid "Excluded from all sitemaps"
msgstr "Exclús de totes los plans de site"

msgid "No sitemaps have been selected for submission."
msgstr "Aucun plan de site a pas estat seleccionat per l'enviament."

msgid "Index this display in sitemap <em>@variant_label</em>"
msgstr ""
"Indexar aquesta presentacion dins la mapa del site "
"<em>@variant_label</em>"

msgid "Default sitemap"
msgstr "Mapa del site per defaut"

msgid ""
"This sitemap will be available under <em>/sitemap.xml</em> in addition "
"to its default path <em>/variant-name/sitemap.xml</em>.<br>Sitemaps "
"can be configured <a href=\"@url\">here</a>."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta mapa de site serà disponibla jos <em>/sitemap.xml</em> en mai "
"de son camin defaut <em>/variant-name/sitemap.xml</em>.<br>Los mapas "
"de site pòdon èsser configurats <a href=\"@url\">aquí</a>."

msgid ""
"Prevent per-sitemap duplicate links.<br>Unchecking this may help "
"avoiding PHP memory errors on huge sites."
msgstr ""
"Prevenir los ligams duple per plan del sit.<br>Descochar aquò pòt "
"ajudar a evitar d'errors de memòria PHP sus de grans sitis."

msgid ""
"The sitemap ID will be part of the URL and can only contain lowercase "
"letters, numbers, dashes and underscores."
msgstr ""
"L'ID de la mapa del site farà partida de l'URL e pòt solament "
"contenir de letras minusculas, de nombres, de tires e de tirants baix."

msgid ""
"The sitemap's type defines its looks and content. Sitemaps types can "
"be configured <a href=\"@url\">here</a>."
msgstr ""
"Lo tipe de la mapa del sit definís son aspècte e son contengut. Los "
"tipes de mapes del sit pòdon èsser configurats <a "
"href=\"@url\">aicí</a>."

msgid "Sitemap %label has been updated."
msgstr "La mapa del siti %label a estat mesa a jorn."

msgid "Sitemap %label has been created."
msgstr "Lo plan de siti %label a estat creat."

msgid ""
"Sitemaps of this type will be built according to the sitemap generator "
"plugin chosen here."
msgstr ""
"Los sitemaps d'aquel tipe seràn creats segon lo plugin generador de "
"sitemap causit aquí."

msgid ""
"Sitemaps of this type will be populated with URLs generated by these "
"URL generator plugins."
msgstr ""
"Los planhs de siti d’aqueste tipe seràn emplenats amb d’URL "
"generats per aquestes extensions generatriças d’URL."

msgid ""
"Processing items from the queue.<br>Each sitemap gets published after "
"all of its items have been processed."
msgstr ""
"Trament d'elements de la cua.<br>Cada mapa del siti es publicat après "
"que totes sos elements sián estat tractats."

msgid "Indexed bundles"
msgstr "Paquets indexats"

msgid "No supported entity types available."
msgstr "Cap de tipe d'entitat sostengut disponible."

msgid "%bundle_label <span class=\"description\">(sitemaps: %sitemaps)</span>"
msgstr ""
"%bundle_label <span class=\"description\">(plans de site : "
"%sitemaps)</span>"

msgid "Configure %label entity type"
msgstr "Configura lo tipe d'entitat %label"

msgid "IndexNow notification enabled"
msgstr "Notificacion IndexNow activada"

msgid "IndexNow notification disabled"
msgstr "Notificacion IndexNow desactivada"

msgid "IndexNow"
msgstr "IndexNow"

msgid "Simple XML Sitemap IndexNow"
msgstr "Indicador simple XML de sitemap IndexNow"

msgid "Verification key in Drupal State"
msgstr "Clau de verificacion dins l'Estat de Drupal"

msgid "Verification key not available"
msgstr "Clau de verificacion pas disponibla"

msgid ""
"In order to generate a verification key for the IndexNow service and "
"choose which sitemaps are to be submitted to search engines, visit <a "
"href=\"@url\">this</a> configuration page."
msgstr ""
"Per generar una clau de verificacion per lo servici IndexNow e causir "
"quines sitemaps devon èsser mandat als motors de recèrca, visita <a "
"href=\"@url\">aquesta</a> pagina de configuracion."

msgid ""
"Submits sitemaps to search engines and notifies IndexNow compatible "
"engines about changes to entities."
msgstr ""
"Envia de sitemaps als motors de recèrca e notifica als motors "
"compatibles amb IndexNow las modificacions dels entitats."

msgid "Index entity on save"
msgstr "Indexar l'entitat a l'enregistrament"

msgid ""
"Allows optionally sending a change notice to IndexNow compatible "
"search engines on entity form save."
msgstr ""
"Permet opcionalament d'enviar un avís de cambiaments als motors de "
"recèrca compatibles amb IndexNow lors de la salvagarda del formulari "
"d'entitat."

msgid "IndexNow URL"
msgstr "IndexNow URL"

msgid "IndexNow bundle settings"
msgstr "Paramètres del paquet IndexNow"

msgid "IndexNow submission enabled"
msgstr "Sufracament IndexNow activat"

msgid "Selected engine for IndexNow submissions"
msgstr "Moteur seleccionat per las sosmissions IndexNow"

msgid "IndexNow on entity save"
msgstr "IndexNow a l'enregistrament de l'entitat"

msgid "No search engines supporting sitemap submission have been found."
msgstr ""
"Cap de motor de recèrca que sostenga la submissió de plan de sits a "
"agut estat trobat."

msgid "Sitemap submission is disabled."
msgstr "La mòstra del plan del site es desactivada."

msgid ""
"The last IndexNow submission was <em>@entity</em> to @engine_label on "
"@time"
msgstr ""
"La darrera sosmession IndexNow èra <em>@entity</em> a @engine_label "
"lo @time"

msgid "IndexNow settings can be configured <a href=\"@url\">here</a>."
msgstr ""
"Las configuracions d'IndexNow pòdon èsser definidas <a "
"href=\"@url\">aquí</a>."

msgid "No search engines supporting IndexNow have been found."
msgstr "Cap de motors de recèrca que sostenguen IndexNow an estat trobats."

msgid "IndexNow submission is disabled."
msgstr "La mesa a disposicion IndexNow es desactivada."

msgid "Notify IndexNow search engines of changes <em>by default</em>"
msgstr ""
"Notificar als moteurs de recèrca IndexNow dels cambiaments <em>de "
"biais predetermi</em>"

msgid "Notify IndexNow search engines of changes <em>now</em>"
msgstr "Notifiatz als motors de recèrca IndexNow las cambiaments <em>ara</em>"

msgid ""
"Send change notice to IndexNow compatible search engines right after "
"submitting entity forms of this type.<br/>Changes include creating, "
"deleting and updating of an entity. This setting can be overridden on "
"the entity form."
msgstr ""
"Mandar un avís de cambiaments als motors de recèrca compatibles amb "
"IndexNow tan lèu coma se mòstra un formulari d'entitat d'aquest "
"tipe.<br/>Los cambiaments inclúsan la creacion, la supression e la "
"mesa a jorn d'una entitat. Aquesta configuracion pòt èsser "
"modificada sul formulari de l'entitat."

msgid ""
"Send change notice to IndexNow compatible search engines right after "
"submitting this form."
msgstr ""
"Enviar un avis de modificacion als motors de recèrca compatibles amb "
"IndexNow just après aver presentat aquest formulari."

msgid "Sitemap submission settings"
msgstr "Paramètres d’enviament de plan de site"

msgid "Submit sitemaps to search engines"
msgstr "Enviar de plans de site als motors de recèrca"

msgid "IndexNow settings"
msgstr "Configuracions d'IndexNow"

msgid "Submit changes to IndexNow capable engines"
msgstr "Enviar los cambiaments als motors capables d'IndexNow"

msgid "Preferred IndexNow engine"
msgstr "Moteur IndexNow preferit"

msgid ""
"All IndexNow requests will be sent to the engine selected here. Only "
"one engine needs to be notified, as it will notify other IndexNow "
"compatible engines for you.<br/>For the sake of equality of "
"opportunity, <strong>consider leaving this at "
"<em>Random</em></strong>, so a random engine can be picked on each "
"submission."
msgstr ""
"Totes las solicitudes IndexNow seràn mandadas al motor causit aquí. "
"Solament un motor deu èsser notificat, pr'amor qu'el notificarà los "
"autres motors compatibles amb IndexNow per vosautres.<br/>Per rason "
"d’igualtat d’opportunitats, <strong>consideratz de laissar aquò a "
"<em>Alator</em></strong>, per que un motor alator pòsca èsser causit "
"a cada emissió."

msgid "Index on every entity save operation"
msgstr "Indexar a cada operacion de salvagarda d’entitat"

msgid ""
"If checked, all entity save operations for <a "
"href=\"@inclusion_url\">included entities</a> will trigger "
"notification of IndexNow search engines.<br/>If unchecked, this will "
"only be possible by adding/altering/deleting an entity through a "
"form.<br/>This should be unchecked if there are mass operations "
"performed on entities that are irrelevant to indexing."
msgstr ""
"Se es cofat, totas las operacions de salvagarda d’entitats per <a "
"href=\"@inclusion_url\">entitats inclosas</a> desencadenaràn la "
"notificacion als motors de recèrca IndexNow.<br/>Se es descofat, "
"aquò serà possible sonque en apondent/modificant/supprimissent una "
"entitat a travèrs d’un formulari.<br/>Cal de desconfar aquò se i a "
"d’operacions de massa realizadas sus d’entitats que son pas "
"pertocsas a l’indexacion."

msgid ""
"The IndexNow verification key is saved in <em>Drupal state</em>. "
"Consider defining it in <em>settings.php</em> like so:<br/>@code"
msgstr ""
"La clau de verificacion IndexNow es salvada dins <em>l’estat de "
"Drupal</em>. Consideratz de la definir dins <em>settings.php</em> atal "
":<br/>@code"

msgid ""
"An IndexNow verification key needs to be generated and optionally "
"added to <em>settings.php</em> in order for IndexNow engines to get "
"notified about changes. This warning only applies to the production "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"Una clau de verificacion per IndexNow deu èsser generada e, "
"opcionalament, gendada dins <em>settings.php</em> per que los motors "
"IndexNow sián notificats dels cambiaments. Aquesta adverténcia "
"s'aplica solament a l'environament de produccion."

msgid ""
"Simple XML Sitemap settings will be added only to entity forms of "
"entity types enabled here. Settings for specific entity bundles (e.g. "
"<em>page</em>) can be adjusted here or on the bundle pages."
msgstr ""
"Las configuracions de Simple XML Sitemap se'n integraràn solament "
"dins los formularis d'entitats dels types d'entitats activats aquí. "
"Las configuracions per de paquets d'entitats especifics (per exemple "
"<em>page</em>) se pòdon ajustar aquí o sus las paginas dels paquets."

msgid "Simple XML Sitemap settings"
msgstr "Configuracions simplas per XML Sitemap"

msgid ""
"A sitemap index which lists all other sitemaps is now available and "
"can be enabled."
msgstr ""
"Un index de plan del site que recapa totes los autres plans del site "
"es ara disponibles e pòt èsser activat."

msgid "IndexNow notification"
msgstr "Notificacion IndexNow"

msgid "IndexNow notification checkbox"
msgstr "Caissa de verificacion per la notificacion IndexNow"

msgid "Remove verification key from state"
msgstr "Suprimir la clau de verificacion de l'estat"

msgid "Generate verification key"
msgstr "Generar una clau de verificacion"

msgid "The IndexNow verification key is saved in <em>settings.php</em>: @key"
msgstr ""
"La clau de verificacion IndexNow es enregistrada dins "
"<em>settings.php</em> : @key"

msgid ""
"The IndexNow verification key is defined in <em>Drupal state</em>: "
"@key"
msgstr ""
"La clau de verificacion IndexNow es definida dins <em>l’estat de "
"Drupal</em> : @key"

msgid ""
"The IndexNow verification key is saved in <em>settings.php</em> and "
"can be safely removed from <em>Drupal state</em>."
msgstr ""
"La clau de verificació IndexNow es salva dins <em>settings.php</em> e "
