msgstr ""
"Apondre de camins interns personalizats de Drupal a de mapas del site "
"especifics."

msgid ""
"Specify drupal internal (relative) paths, one per line. Do not forget "
"to prepend the paths with a '/'.<br>Optionally link priority <em>(0.0 "
"- 1.0)</em> can be added by appending it after a space.<br> Optionally "
"link change frequency <em>(always / hourly / daily / weekly / monthly "
"/ yearly / never)</em> can be added by appending it after a space."
msgstr ""
"Especificatz los camins interns (relatius) de drupal, un per linha. "
"Oblidetz pas de prepausar los camins amb un '/'.<br>Opcionalament, la "
"prioritat del ligam <em>(0.0 - 1.0)</em> pòt èsser aponduda en la "
"seguissant après un espaci.<br> Opcionalament, la frequéncia de "
"cambiament del ligam <em>(sempre / cada ora / cada jorn / cada setmana "
"/ cada mes / cada an / jamai)</em> pòt èsser aponduda en la "
"seguissent après un espaci."

msgid ""
"<strong>Examples:</strong><br><em>/ 1.0 daily</em> -> home page with "
"the highest priority and daily change frequency<br><em>/contact</em> "
"-> contact page with the default priority and no change frequency "
"information"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Exemples :</strong><br><em>/ 1.0 quarzenal</em> -> pagina "
"d'aculhida amb la prioritat mai nauta e frequéncia de cambiament "
"diària<br><em>/contact</em> -> pagina de contacte amb la prioritat "
"per defaut e sens information de frequéncia de cambiament"

msgid ""
"<strong>@sitemap, line @line</strong>: The path <em>@path</em> does "
"not exist."
msgstr ""
"<strong>@sitemap, linha @line</strong> : Lo camin <em>@path</em> "
"existís pas."

msgid ""
"<strong>@sitemap, line @line</strong>: The path <em>@path</em> needs "
"to start with a '/'."
msgstr ""
"<strong>@sitemap, linha @line</strong> : Lo camin <em>@path</em> deu "
"començar amb un '/'."

msgid ""
"<strong>@sitemap, line @line</strong>: The priority setting "
"<em>@priority</em> for path <em>@path</em> is incorrect. Set the "
"priority from 0.0 to 1.0."
msgstr ""
"<strong>@sitemap, linha @line</strong> : Lo paramètre de prioritat "
"<em>@priority</em> per lo camin <em>@path</em> es incorrècte. "
"Definissètz la prioritat entre 0.0 e 1.0."

msgid ""
"<strong>@sitemap, line @line</strong>: The changefreq setting "
"<em>@changefreq</em> for path <em>@path</em> is incorrect. The "
"following are the correct values: <em>@changefreq_options</em>."
msgstr ""
"<strong>@sitemap, linha @line</strong> : La configuracion changefreq "
"<em>@changefreq</em> per lo cami <em>@path</em> es incorrècta. Los "
"valors justes son los seguents : <em>@changefreq_options</em>."

msgid "There are no languages other than the default language available."
msgstr "Non i a pas d'autras lengas disponiblas que la lenga deu defòlt."

msgid "The sitemaps need to be regenerated."
msgstr "Las cartas del siti devon èsser regeneradas."

