"Submission settings can be configured <a "
"href=\"@url\">here</a>.<br/>The ping protocol is <strong>being "
"deprecated</strong>, use IndexNow if applicable."
msgstr ""
"Las configuracions de matinada de donadas se pòdon configurar <a "
"href=\"@url\">aicí</a>.<br/>Lo protocòl ping es <strong>en cors de "
"desaparicion</strong>, causissètz IndexNow se es apropriat."

