msgid ""
"Generates standard-compliant hreflang XML sitemaps to enhance your "
"site's SEO, notifies search engines of website changes via IndexNow "
"and sitemap ping protocols, and provides a framework for developing "
"other sitemap types."
msgstr ""
"Genera plans de site XML hreflang conformes als estandards per "
"melhorar lo SEO del vòstre siti, notifica los motors de recèrca dels "
"cambiaments del siti via IndexNow e los protòcles de ping de plan de "
"site, e provesís un encastre per desenvelopar d'autres tipes de plans "
"de site."

