"pòt èsser utilizat per prepausar una cadena constanta a una entrada. "
"Exemples : $, #, -."

msgid ""
"Text or code that is placed directly after the input. This can be used "
"to add a unit to an input. Examples: lb, kg, %."
msgstr ""
"Test o còdi que siá plaçat dirèctament après l’entrada. Aquò "
"pòt èsser utilizat per apondre una unitat a una entrada. Exemples : "
"lb, kg, %."

msgid ""
"Unable to render elements, please view the below message(s) and the "
"error log."
msgstr ""
"Unable to render elements, please view the below message(s) and the "
"error log.\n"
"\n"
"Impossible de renderizar los elements, mercés de "
"vesitar lo(s) messatge(s) jos aquò e lo registre d'errors."

msgid "Unsaved warning is enabled for all forms."
msgstr "L’avís de susvelh non sauvat es activat per totas las formularis."

msgid ""
"If checked, users will be displayed a warning message when they "
"navigate away from a form with unsaved changes."
msgstr ""
"Se es cofat, se mòstrara als utilizaires un messatge d'avisi quand "
"navegaràn fòra d'un formulari amb de modificacions pas "
"enregistradas."

msgid ""
"Expand/collapse all (details) link is automatically added to all "
"forms."
msgstr ""
"Lo ligam expandir/contractar tot (detalhs) es apondut automaticament a "
"totas las fòrmas."

msgid "The HTTP method with which the form will be submitted."
msgstr "Lo metòde HTTP amb lo qual lo formulari serà mandat."

msgid "POST (Custom)"
msgstr "ENVIARE (Personalizat)"

msgid "GET (Custom)"
msgstr "OBTÉN (Personalizat)"

msgid ""
"Code Mirror is used to provide a text editor for YAML, HTML, CSS, and "
"JavaScript configuration settings and messages."
msgstr ""
"Code Mirror es utilizat per provesir un editor de tèxt per las "
"configuracions e los messatges en YAML, HTML, CSS e JavaScript."

msgid ""
"Input masks are used to ensure predefined and custom formats for text "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"Las mascas d'entrada son utilizadas per assegurar de formats "
"prèstablits e personalizats pels camps de tèxte."

msgid ""
"Rating plugin for jQuery. Fast, progressive enhancement, touch "
"support, customizable (just swap out the images, or change some CSS), "
"unobtrusive JavaScript (using HTML5 data-* attributes), RTL support. "
"The Rating plugin supports as many stars as you'd like, and also any "
"step size."
msgstr ""
"Plugin de valoracion per jQuery. Rapide, aprimorament progressive, "
"supòrt tàctil, personalizable (basta cambiar las imatges, o "
"modificar un pauc de CSS), JavaScript discret (utilizant los atributs "
"HTML5 data-*), supòrt RTL. Lo plugin de valoracion supòrta tanplan "
"mantunas estelas coma volètz, ainsi que qualsevol talha de pas."

msgid ""
"Select2 gives you a customizable select box with support for searching "
"and tagging."
msgstr ""
"Select2 vos dona una caixa de seleccion personalizable amb supòrt per "
"la recerca e l’etiquetatge."

msgid ""
"Signature Pad is a JavaScript library for drawing smooth signatures. "
"It is HTML5 canvas based and uses variable width Bézier curve "
"interpolation. It works in all modern desktop and mobile browsers and "
"doesn't depend on any external libraries."
msgstr ""
"Signature Pad es una biblioteca JavaScript per desenhar de firmitas "
"lisas. Es basada sus HTML5 canvas e utiliza una interpelacion de "
"curvas Bézier amb una largor variabla. Fonciona dins totes los "
"navigadors mejans de tauleta e d’ordenador d’auèi e depend pas "
"d’aucuna biblioteca externa."

msgid "Signature Pad is used to provide a signature element."
msgstr "Pad de Signatura es utilizat per provesir un element de signatura."

msgid ""
"A lightweight, customizable javascript timepicker plugin for jQuery, "
"inspired by Google Calendar."
msgstr ""
"Un plugin javascript de seleccionador d’ora leugièr e "
"personalizable per jQuery, inspirat pel Calendari de Google."

msgid "Timepicker is used to provide a polyfill for HTML 5 time elements."
msgstr ""
"Timepicker es utilizat per provesir un polyfill pels elements de temps "
"d'HTML 5."

msgid ""
"Word or character counting, with server-side validation, is available "
"for text fields and text areas."
msgstr ""
"Comptatge de mots o de caractèrs, amb validacion del costat del "
"servidor, es disponibla per los camps de tèxt e las zònas de tèxt."

msgid "For multiple options, use commas to separate multiple defaults."
msgstr ""
"Per mai d'opcions, utilizar de virgulas per separar mai d'un valor per "
"defaut."

msgid "Other field prefix"
msgstr "Autra prefíx de camp"

msgid "Other field suffix"
msgstr "Sufís de camp exterior"

msgid ""
"Select where the final files should be stored. Private file storage "
"has more overhead than public files, but allows restricted access to "
"files within this element."
msgstr ""
"Seleccionatz ont las fichièrs finals devon èsser estocats. "
"L'emmagazinatge de fichièrs privats a mai de còsts que las fichièrs "
"publicas, mas permet un accés restrench a los fichièrs a l'interior "
"d'aqueste element."

msgid "Confirmation page URL alias"
msgstr "Alias d’URL de la página de confirmacion"

msgid "Default confirmation back label"
msgstr "Etiqueta de retòrna de confirmacion per defaut"

msgid "Confirmation back link CSS classes"
msgstr "Classes CSS del ligam de tornar del confirmar"

msgid "Wizard start attributes"
msgstr "Atributs de començament de l'ausir"

msgid "Wizard next page button label"
msgstr "Etiqueta del boton per la pagina seguenta de l'assistent"

msgid "Confirmation back link"
msgstr "Ligam de retorn de confirmacion"

msgid ""
"A list of classes that will be provided in \"Button CSS classes\" "
"dropdown. Enter one or more classes on each line. These styles should "
"be available in your theme's CSS file."
msgstr ""
"Una lista de classas que serà provesida dins lo menut desplegable "
"«Button CSS classes». Metètz una o mai classas per linha. Aquelas "
"estils devon èsser disponibles dins lo fichièr CSS del vòstre "
"tèma."

msgid ""
"A list of classes that will be provided in the \"Confirmation CSS "
"classes\" dropdown. Enter one or more classes on each line. These "
"styles should be available in your theme's CSS file."
msgstr ""
"Una lista de classas que se fornisson dins lo menú desplegable "
"«Confirmation CSS classes». S’escriu una classa o mai dins cada "
"linha. Aquel estil deu èsser disponibil dins lo fichièr CSS de "
"vòstre tèma."

msgid ""
"A list of classes that will be provided in the \"Confirmation back "
"link CSS classes\" dropdown. Enter one or more classes on each line. "
"These styles should be available in your theme's CSS file."
msgstr ""
"Una lista de classas que s'aprovisionaràn dins lo menu desplegable "
"\"Confirmation back link CSS classes\". Metètz una o mantunas classas "
"per linha. Aquelas estiladas devon estar disponiblas dins lo fichièr "
"CSS del vòstre tèma."

msgid "Webform test third party settings"
msgstr "Paramètres de terças partidas per lo teste de Webform"

msgid "Webform confidential message"
msgstr "Messatge confidencial de Webform"

msgid "Webform handlers"
msgstr "Mantenedors de formularis web"

msgid "Webform field storage settings"
msgstr "Paramètres d’emmagazinament dels champs Webform"

msgid "Webform autocomplete display format settings"
msgstr ""
"Paramètres del format d'afichatge d'autocompletament del formulari "
"web"

msgid "Display the referenced webform with default submission data."
msgstr ""
"Afichar lo formulari web referenciat amb las donadas de sosmission per "
"defaut."

msgid "webforms"
msgstr "formularis web"

msgid "This command will export webform submissions to a file."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta comanda exportarà las sosmetudas del formulari web dins un "
"fichièr."

msgid "'@title' (@entity_type:@entity_id) does not reference a webform."
msgstr "'@title' (@entity_type:@entity_id) refús pas una webform."

msgid ""
"'@title' (@entity_type:@entity_id) does not have a '@webform_id' "
"webform associated with it."
msgstr ""
"'@title' (@entity_type:@entity_id) a pas de formulari web "
"'@webform_id' associat."

msgid ""
"If you run into any issues with a webform, you can also attach the "
"below configuration (without any personal information) to a new ticket "
"in the Webform module's <a href=\":href\">issue queue</a>."
msgstr ""
"Se trobatz quauquas dificultats amb un formulari web, podètz tanben "
"ajustar la configuracion çai jos (sens cap d'informacion personala) a "
"un bilhet novèl dins la <a href=\":href\">caissa de problèmas</a> "
"del mòdeul Formulari web."

msgid "A flag that indicate the status of the webform submission."
msgstr "Una bandièra que indica l'estat de la sosmetuda del formulari web."

msgid "Administrative notes about the webform submission."
msgstr "Notas administrativas sul mandat del formulari web."

msgid "The serial number of the webform submission entity."
msgstr "Lo numèro de seria de l'entitat de submissió del formulari web."

msgid "Here is your webform's configuration:"
msgstr "Vaicí la configuracion de vòstre formulari web :"

msgid ""
"Provides examples of all webform elements and functionality which can "
"used for demonstrating and testing advanced functionality or used as "
"cut-n-paste code snippets for creating new webforms."
msgstr ""
"Provides examples of all webform elements and functionality which can "
"used for demonstrating and testing advanced functionality or used as "
"cut-n-paste code snippets for creating new webforms.\n"
"\n"
"Proporciona "
"d'exemples de totes los elements e foncionalitats de formularis web "
"que pòdon èsser utilizats per demostar e provar de foncionalitats "
"avançadas o coma còdis copiat-colat pel dessenh de nòus formularis "
"web."

msgid "View webform submissions for any node"
msgstr ""
"Visualizar las sosmissions dels formularis web per quina siá de las "
"vòstras nòdas"

msgid "View webform submissions for own node"
msgstr "Vesi las sosmetudas de formularis web per lo pròpri vejaire"

msgid "Edit webform submissions for any node"
msgstr ""
"Modificar las sosmetudas dels formularis web per quin qu'òm vògue de "
"nòdle"

msgid "Edit webform submissions for own node"
msgstr "Modificar las sosmissions del formulari web per pròpri node"

msgid "Delete webform submissions for any node"
msgstr ""
"Suprimir las sosmissions de formularis web per quina que siá de las "
"entradas"

msgid "Delete webform submissions for own node"
msgstr "Suprimir las submisses dels formularis web per son pròpri nœud"

msgid "Webform Templates"
msgstr "Modèls de Formularis Web"

msgid "The webform element %title has been deleted."
msgstr "L'element de formulari web %title a estat suprimat."

msgid "Webform element %type test has been reset."
msgstr "L'element %type del formulari web foguèt restablit."

msgid "Webform element %type test has been updated."
msgstr "L'element de Webform %type a estat actualizat."

msgid ""
"This is used as a descriptive label when displaying this webform "
"element."
msgstr ""
"Aquò es utilizat coma una plaça descriptiva quand se Aficha aqueste "
"element de formulari web."

msgid "The default value of the webform element."
msgstr "Lo valor per defaut de l'element de formulari web."

msgid ""
"If set, this message will be used when a required webform element is "
"empty, instead of the default \"Field x is required.\" message."
msgstr ""
"Se configurat, aqueste messatge serà utilizat quand un element de "
"formulari web requerit es vidèc, al liure del messatge per defaut "
"«Lo camp x es necessari.»"

msgid "<a href=\":href\">Delete all submissions</a> to this webform."
msgstr ""
"<a href=\":href\">Suprimir totas las fòrmas mandadas</a> d'aqueste "
"formulari web."

msgid ""
"<a href=\":href\">Enable the Webform UI module</a> and safely delete "
"this element."
msgstr ""
"<a href=\":href\">Activatz lo modulus Webform UI</a> e suprimez "
"aqueste element amb seguretat."

msgid ""
"The %key element can not be removed because the %title webform has <a "
"href=\":href\">results</a>."
msgstr ""
"L'element %key pòt pas èsser suprimat pr'amor que lo formulari web "
"%title a <a href=\":href\">de risultats</a>."

msgid ""
"The %title (@type) is a webform element that can not have any child "
"elements."
msgstr ""
"Lo %title (@type) es un element de formulari web que pòt pas anar amb "
"d’elements enfant."

msgid "Webform %label created."
msgstr "Formulari web %label creat."

msgid "Webform %label elements saved."
msgstr "Elements %label del formulari web enregistrats."

msgid "Webform @label created."
msgstr "Webform @label creat."

msgid "There are currently no handlers setup for this webform."
msgstr ""
"Actualament, i a pas cap de manèra configurada per aqueste fòrmulari "
"web."

msgid "Webform %label handler saved."
msgstr "Gestionari Webform %label enregistrat."

msgid "Webform @label handler saved."
msgstr "Manipulador de Webform @label enregistrat."

msgid ""
"If checked, this webform will be available as a template to all users "
"who can create new webforms."
msgstr ""
"Se marcadís, aqueste formulari web serà disponible coma un modèl "
"per totes los utilizaires que pòdon crear de nòus formularis web."

msgid ""
"If checked, all warnings and log messages about 'This webform is "
"currently not saving any submitted data.' will be suppressed."
msgstr ""
"Se marcats, totas las avisas e los messatges de registre concernents a "
"« Aqueste formulari web actualament no sauva pas ges de donadas "
"metudas » seràn supausats."

msgid ""
"Optionally specify an alternative URL by which the webform "
"confirmation page can be accessed."
msgstr ""
"Opcionalament, especificatz una URL alternativa per la quala la pagina "
"de confirmacion del formulari web pòt èsser accessada."

msgid "A message to be displayed if the webform breaks."
msgstr "Un messatge que cal mostrar se lo formulari web es planhat."

msgid ""
"If checked, users will be displayed a warning message when they "
"navigate away from a webform with unsaved changes."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, los utilizaires veiràn un messatge d'avís quand "
"se desviaràn d'un formulari web amb de cambiaments pas salvats."

msgid ""
"If checked, an expand/collapse all (details) link will be added to "
"this webform when there are two or more details elements available on "
"the webform."
msgstr ""
"Se seleccionat, un ligam d'espandiment/retraccament de tot (detalhs) "
"serà plaçat dins aqueste formulari web quand i a dos o mai "
"d'elements de detalhs disponibles dins lo formulari web."

msgid ""
"The value of the next submission number. This is usually 1 when you "
"start and will go up with each webform submission."
msgstr ""
"La valor del proxime nombre de submissió. Normalament es 1 quand "
"comencetz e dintrará en aument amb cada submissió del formulari web."

msgid "The username of the webform author/owner."
msgstr "Lo nom d'utilizaire de l'autor/propriètaire del formulari web."

msgid ""
"Please make sure this webform's action URL or path is setup to handle "
"the webform's submission."
msgstr ""
"Siás segur que l'URL o lo camin de l'accion d'aqueste formulari web "
"es configurat per gerir la sovenida del formulari web."

msgid "The URL or path to which the webform will be submitted."
msgstr "L'URL o lo camin al qual lo formulari web serà mandat."

msgid ""
"This webform is currently not saving any submitted data. Please enable "
"the <a href=\":settings_href\">saving of results</a> or add a <a "
"href=\":handlers_href\">submission handler</a> to the webform."
msgstr ""
"Aqueste formulari web actualament non guarda cap donada submitida. "
"Mercés d'activar la <a href=\":settings_href\">sauvegarda dels "
"resultats</a> o d'añadir un <a href=\":handlers_href\">gestionari de "
"soumisions</a> al formulari web."

msgid ""
"The below webform has been prepopulated with custom/random test data. "
"When submitted, this information <strong>will still be saved</strong> "
"and/or <strong>sent to designated recipients</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Lo formulari web josmenionat es estat preemplenat amb de donadas de "
"test personalizadas/aleatòrias. Quand serà mandat, aquela "
"informacion <strong>sauvegardada uèi encara</strong> e/o "
"<strong>mandada als destinataris designats</strong>."

msgid "Submissions to %webform for %user"
msgstr "Envèis a %webform per %user"

msgid ""
"There are no third party settings available. Please install a "
"contributed module that integrates with the Webform module."
msgstr ""
"Non i a pas de paramètres de tresena partida disponiblas. Mercés "
"d'installar un mòdule contribuït que s'integra amb lo mòdule "
"Webform."

msgid "Webform info"
msgstr "Informacion Webform"

msgid ""
"No export file ready for download. The file may have already been "
"downloaded by your browser. Visit the <a href=\":href\">download "
"export webform</a> to create a new export."
msgstr ""
"Cap de fichièr d'esportacion preparat per èsser telecargat. Lo "
"fichièr pòt ja aver estat telecargat pel vòstre navegador. Visitatz "
"lo <a href=\":href\">formulari web d'esportacion per telecargar</a> "
"per crear una nòva esportacion."

msgid "Testing %title webform"
msgstr "Testar lo formulari web %title"

msgid "The UUID of the webform submission entity."
msgstr "L'UUID de l'entitat de submissió del formulari web."

msgid "The URI the user submitted the webform."
msgstr "L'URI que l'òrdre a mandat pel formulari web."

msgid ""
"The time that the webform submission was first saved as draft or "
"submitted."
msgstr ""
"Lo moment que la remesa del formulari web foguèt primièr "
"enregistrada coma esbòç o remesa."

msgid ""
"The time that the webform submission was submitted as complete (not "
"draft)."
msgstr ""
"Lo moment ont la sotmesida del formulari web foguèt enviada coma "
"terminada (pas coma borrador)."

msgid ""
"The time that the webform submission was last saved (complete or "
"draft)."
msgstr ""
"Lo temps que la sotmission del formulari web foguèt enfin "
"enregistrada (completa o en bruch)."

msgid "Disable client-side validation for all webforms"
msgstr ""
"Desactivar la validacion del costat client per totes los formularis "
"web"

msgid ""
"If checked, the <a href=\":href\">novalidate</a> attribute, which "
"disables client-side validation, will be added to all webforms."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, l'<a href=\":href\">atribut novalidate</a>, que "
"desactivarà la validacion del costat client, serà apondut a totes "
"las formularis web."

msgid ""
"Determines the default placement of the description for all webform "
"elements."
msgstr ""
"Determina lo plaçament per defaut de la descripcion per totes los "
"elements del formulari web."

msgid ""
"Public files upload destination is dangerous for webforms that are "
"available to anonymous and/or untrusted users."
msgstr ""
"Lo destinatari de l’enviament de fichièrs publics es perilhós per "
"de formularis web accessibles als usatgièrs anònims e/o pas de "
"fisança."

msgid "Webform submissions cleared."
msgstr "Sosmetudas de formulari web estonadas."

msgid "Webform submissions purged."
msgstr "Sometiments dels formularis web suprimits."

msgid "Webform selection"
msgstr "Seleccion de formulari web"

msgid ""
"Flag to control whether this webform should be open or closed to new "
"submissions."
msgstr ""
"Indicador per controlar se aqueste formulari web deu èsser dobèrt o "
"claus per las nòvas submissiouns."

msgid "A webform containing default submission values."
msgstr "Un formulari web contenent de valors per defecte per la mesa jos."

msgid "Webform PHP mailer"
msgstr "Envialador PHP de Webform"

msgid ""
"A +/- value describes a dynamic value that is that many years earlier "
"or later than the current year at the time the webform is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Una valor +/- descriu una valor dinamica que es aquela fòrça "
"d’annadas abans o après l’annada correnta al moment ont se "
"mòstra lo formulari web."

msgid ""
"Randomizes the order of the options when they are displayed in the "
"webform."
msgstr ""
"Desòrdna l’òrdre de las opcions quand son afichadas dins lo "
"formulari web."

msgid ""
"If checked, all existing submission values will be visible to the "
"webform's users."
msgstr ""
"Se marcadas, totes los valors de sosmissions existents seràn visibles "
"per los utilizaires del formulari en linha."

msgid "The default value of the composite webform element as YAML."
msgstr "Lo valor per defaut de l'element webform compost en format YAML."

msgid ""
"Randomizes the order of the questions when they are displayed in the "
"webform."
msgstr ""
"Mescla l'òrdre de las questions quand son mòstradas dins lo "
"formulari web."

msgid "A basic contact webform template."
msgstr "Un modèl simpla de formulari web de contacte."

msgid "An employee evaluation webform template."
msgstr "Un modèl de fòrmulari web per l'avaluacion dels emplegats."

msgid "An issue webform template."
msgstr "Un modèl de fòrmulari web de problèma."

msgid "A job application webform template."
msgstr "Un modèl de fòrmulari web per la candidatura a un emplec."

msgid "A job seeker profile webform template."
msgstr "Un modèl de formulari web per un perfil de cercaire d'emplec."

msgid "A subscribe to mailing list webform template."
msgstr ""
"Un modèl de formulario web per s’abonar a una lista de "
"distribucion."

msgid "A user profile webform template."
msgstr "Un modèl de formulàri web per un perfil d'utilizaire."

msgid "Submission serial number"
msgstr "Numerotacion de la submisson"

msgid "Deleted @form: Submission #@id."
msgstr "Suplegat @form : Submission #@id èra suprimida."

msgid ""
"Please note: That the below custom element attributes will also be "
"applied to the @name fieldset wrapper. (<a href=\":href\">Issue "
"#2836374</a>)"
msgstr ""
"Vòli notar: Que los atributs personalizats dels elements aital "
"s'aplicaran tanben al contengut del camp @name dins lo balisatge "
"fieldset. (<a href=\":href\">Issue #2836374</a>)"

msgid ""
"Examples of elements with <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/RobinHerbots/jquery.inputmask\">input "
"masks</a>."
msgstr ""
"Exemples d’elements amb de <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/RobinHerbots/jquery.inputmask\">mascas "
"d’entrada</a>."

msgid "Example: Elements: Condition Logic"
msgstr "Exemple : Elements : Logica de Condicion"

msgid "Examples of elements using conditional logic."
msgstr "Exemples d’elements utilizant una logica condicionala."

msgid "The node that the webform was submitted from."
msgstr "Lo nòde dempuèi ont lo formulari web foguèt mandat."

msgid "Installing the Webform module"
msgstr "Installacion dau mòdule Webform"

msgid ""
"Below are elements that are available but do not have a Webform "
"Element integration plugin."
msgstr ""
"Abaix son los elements que son disponiblas mas que an pas un plugin "
"d'integracion d'Element de Formulari Web."

msgid ""
"Examples of multiple column webform layout using <a "
"href=\"https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/\">Flexbox</a>."
msgstr ""
"Exemples de mòstras de formularis web amb divèrsas colomnas "
"utilizant <a "
"href=\"https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/\">Flexbox</a>."

msgid "Example of a multiple step 'wizard' webform."
msgstr "Exemple d’un formulari web « engenhaire » amb pas multipli."

msgid ""
"[webform_submission:values:first_name] "
"[webform_submission:values:last_name]"
msgstr ""
"[webform_submission:values:first_name] "
"[webform_submission:values:last_name]"

msgid "Select available element types"
msgstr "Seleccionatz los sòns de tipe d'element disponiblas"

msgid "Global Assets (CSS/JavaScript)"
msgstr "Recors Globaus (CSS/JavaScript)"

msgid "Amount of submissions to process"
msgstr "Quantitat de sosmissions a processar"

msgid "Webform submission bulk form"
msgstr "Formulàri massiu d'enviament Webform"

msgid ""
"Provides a Webform content type which allows webforms to be integrated "
"into a website as nodes."
msgstr ""
"Propausa un tipe de contengut Webform que permet d’integrar de "
"formularis web dins un siti coma de nòdes."

msgid "Provides a user interface for building and maintaining webforms."
msgstr ""
"Prepausa una interfaccia d'utilizaire per bastir e mantenir de "
"formularis web."

msgid "The element may still be empty unless it is required."
msgstr "L'element pòda encara èsser void a mens que siá necessari."

msgid "Items format"
msgstr "Format dels elements"

msgid "Draft and completed"
msgstr "Borrador e acabat"

msgid "Add a form element that lets you run operations on multiple webform."
msgstr ""
"Apondre un element de formulari que vos permet de realizar "
"d'operacions sus divèrses webforms."

msgid "Space ()"
msgstr "Espaci ()"

msgid ""
"Add a form element that lets you run operations on multiple "
"submissions."
msgstr ""
"Apondre un element de formulari que vos permet d’executar "
"d’operacions sus mantunas sosmissions."

msgid "Enter custom CSS to be attached to all webforms."
msgstr "Entratz lo CSS personalizat que s'ajuntarà a totes las formòlas web."

msgid "Provides an element that wraps child elements in a container."
msgstr ""
"Provides an element that wraps child elements in a container.  "
"\n"
"Dispausa d'un element que envelopa los elements enfants dins un "
"contenidor."

msgid "Provides a form element for an HTML 'hidden' input element."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona un element de formulari per un element d'entrada HTML « "
"hidden »."

msgid ""
"Provides a display-only form element with an optional title and "
"description."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona un element de fòrmulari nominal amb un títol e una "
"descripcion opcionals."

msgid "Provides a form element for entering a telephone number."
msgstr "Ofrís un element de formulari per inserir un numèro de telefòn."

msgid "Provides a text format form element."
msgstr "Prepausa un element de tòca de formatatge de tèxte."

msgid "Provides a form element for storage of internal information."
msgstr ""
"Forneis un element de formulari pel senhalament d’informacions "
"internas."

msgid "Composite element options"
msgstr "Opcions de l'element compausit"

msgid ""
"Provides a form element to collect contact information (name, address, "
"phone, email)."
msgstr ""
"Forneís un element de fòrmulari per recaptar d'informacions de "
"contacte (nom, adreça, telefon, corrièr electronic)."

msgid ""
"Provides a flex(ible) box container used to layout elements in "
"multiple columns."
msgstr ""
"Provesís un contenidor de caissa flex(ibla) utilizat per tal de metre "
"en pagina d'elements en mantuns colomnas."

msgid "Provides a form element for uploading and saving an image file."
msgstr ""
"Met a disposicion un element de formulari per telecargar e salvar un "
"fichièr d'imatge."

msgid "Likert questions and answers options"
msgstr "Questions de tipe Likert e opcions de responsa"

msgid ""
"The 'File' element is unavailable because no stream wrappers are "
"available"
msgstr ""
"L'element « Fichièr » es pas disponible perque i a pas de cobritz "
"de flux disponiblas"

msgid "Provides a form element for time selection."
msgstr "Proporciona un element de formulari per la seleccion del temps."

msgid "Provides a form element for uploading and saving a video file."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona un element de formulari per telecargar e guardar un "
"fichièr video."

msgid "Disable system tray"
msgstr "Desactivar lo bac del sistèma"

msgid "Display elements in table columns"
msgstr "Afichar d'elementes dins las colomnas de taula"

msgid ""
"If checked, the <a href=\":href\">autocomplete</a> attribute will be "
"set to off, which disables autocompletion for all form elements."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, l'<a href=\":href\">atribut autocomplete</a> serà "
"desactivat, çò que desactiva l'autocomplecion per totas las entitats "
"de formulari."

msgid "Disable off-canvas system tray"
msgstr "Desactivar la barra del sistèma despausada"

msgid ""
"Check this option if the user should be allowed to enter multiple "
"entity references using tags."
msgstr ""
"Cochatz aquesta opcion se l’utilizaire deu poder intrar divèrsas "
"referéncias d’entitats en utilizant de balises."

msgid "Provides a form element to display a link."
msgstr "Proporciona un element de fòrmulari per afichar un ligam."

msgid "Wrapper type"
msgstr "Tipo d'encapusulament"

msgid "Webform Demo: Application/Evaluation System"
msgstr "Demonstracion Webform: Sistèma d'aplicacion/evaluacion"

msgid ""
"If set, this message will be used when an element's allowed number of "
"values is exceeded, instead of the default \"@message\" message."
msgstr ""
"Se es configurat, aqueste messatge serà utilizat quand lo nombre "
"permés de valors per un element es superat, al luòc del messatge per "
"defaut \"@message\"."

msgid ""
"If the close date/time is left blank, this webform will never be "
"closed."
msgstr ""
"Se la data/ora de clausura es laissada en blanc, aquel formulari web "
"serà jamai clausurat."

msgid "Page title to be shown upon successful submission."
msgstr ""
"Títol de la pagina que se mostrarà un còp la sotmission realizada "
"amb succès."

msgid ""
"A jQuery plugin for entering and validating international telephone "
"numbers. It adds a flag dropdown to any input, detects the user's "
"country, displays a relevant placeholder and provides "
"formatting/validation methods."
msgstr ""
"Un plugin jQuery per ingresar e validar numèros de telefòne "
"internacionals. Apond una lista desplegable amb de bandièras a tot "
"camp de trach, detecta lo país de l’utilizaire, aficha un espaci "
"reservat pertinent e provesís de metòdes de formatatge/validacion."

msgid ""
"Select 'Webform from URL' to display this block, when the current "
"request's path contains the selected webform."
msgstr ""
"Seleccionatz « Webform dempuèi l’URL » per afichar aqueste blòc, "
"quand lo camin de la requèsta actuala conten lo webform seleccionat."

msgid ""
"Select 'Webform submission from URL' to display this block, when the "
"current request's path contains a webform submission that was created "
"from the selected webform."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu 'Enviament de formulari web depint URL' per mostrar "
"aqueste blòc, quand lo camin de la demanda actuala conten una "
"sotmission de formulari web que foguèt creada a partir del formulari "
"web seleccionat."

msgid ""
"Select 'Node from URL' to display this block, when the current "
"request's path contains a node that references the selected webform "
"using a dedicated webform field or node."
msgstr ""
"Seleccionatz «Node dempuèi l’URL» per afichar aquesta bòsca "
"quand lo camin de la demanda actuala conten un node que fa referéncia "
"al formulari web seleccionat en utilitzant un camp o un node dedicat "
"al formulari web."

msgid "Provides an element to render advanced HTML markup and processed text."
msgstr ""
"Provesís un element per renderizar de balisatge HTML avançat e de "
"tèxt prepausat."

msgid "Tree delimiter"
msgstr "Delimitador d'arbres"

msgid ""
"Provides a form element to select a single or multiple terms displayed "
"as hierarchical tree or as breadcrumbs using a select menu."
msgstr ""
"Provesís un element de formulari per seleccionar un o mai de termes "
"illustrats coma un arbre jerarquic o coma de migalhas de pan en "
"utilizant un menut de seleccion."

msgid "Demo: Application Evaluation"
msgstr "Demo: Avaloracion de l'aplicacion"

msgid "Limit term depth"
msgstr "Profondor maxima del tèrme"

msgid "Default submission logging"
msgstr "Registre per defaut de las submissions"

msgid "Form previous submissions notification"
msgstr "Notifia de las submissions precedentas del formulari"

msgid "Email to address options"
msgstr "Adreça de corrièl a opciòns"

msgid "Email from address options"
msgstr "Opcions d'adreça de correu electronic"

msgid "Return path email"
msgstr "Camino de retorn del corrier electronic"

msgid ""
"To uninstall Webform node, delete all content that has the Webform "
"content type."
msgstr ""
"Per desinstal·lacion del node Webform, suprime tot lo contengut qu'a "
"lo tipe de contengut Webform."

msgid ""
"There is data for this element in the database. This setting can no "
"longer be changed."
msgstr ""
"I a de donadas per aqueste element dins la basa de donadas. Aquesta "
"configuracion pòt pas mai èsser modificada."

msgid ""
"If the open date/time is left blank, this form will immediately be "
"opened."
msgstr ""
"Se la data/ora d'èrba es laissada vacenta, aquest formulari serà "
"dubèrt immediatament."

msgid ""
"A message to be displayed notifying the user that the webform is going "
"to be opening to submissions. The opening message will only be "
"displayed when a webform is scheduled to be opened."
msgstr ""
"Un messatge a afichar per notificar a l'utilizaire que lo formulari "
"web va èsser dobèrt per las submetudas. Lo messatge d'obertura serà "
"afichat sonque quand un formulari web es programat per èsser dobèrt."

msgid ""
"A message to be displayed notifying the user that the webform is "
"closed. The closed message will be displayed when a webform's status "
"is closed or a submission limit is reached."
msgstr ""
"Un messatge que se mostrarà per avisar l’utilizaire que lo "
"formulari web es clausurat. Lo messatge de clausura se mostrarà quand "
"l’estat d’un formulari web es clausurat o quand se rescontra una "
"limita de submissió."

msgid ""
"If checked, the submit button will be disabled immediately after it is "
"clicked."
msgstr ""
"Se es chausit, lo boton d'envoia serà desactivat immediatament après "
"èsser estat clicat."

msgid "Allow your users to save and finish the webform later"
msgstr ""
"Permetez a vòstres utilizaires de sauvar e acabar lo formulari web "
"mai tard"

msgid "Authenticated and anonymous users"
msgstr "Utilizaire autenticats e anònims"

msgid ""
"Please make sure to enable the <a href=\":href\">automatic purging of "
"draft submissions</a>, to ensure that your database is not filled with "
"abandoned anonymous submissions in draft."
msgstr ""
"Siatz segur d'activar lo <a href=\":href\">purge automatic dels envois "
"en esbós</a>, per assegurar que vòstra basa de donadas siá pas "
"emplenada amb d'envois anonims abandonats en esbós."

msgid "Submission behaviors"
msgstr "Comportaments de sosmetuda"

msgid ""
"If checked, drafts and submissions created by an anonymous user will "
"be reassigned to their user account when they login."
msgstr ""
"Se checkat, los esboças e las submissiás creadas per un utilizator "
"anonim seràn reassociadas a son compte d’utilizator quand se "
"connectarà."

msgid "Log submission events"
msgstr "Registrar los eveniments de submissió"

msgid "International Telephone Input is used by the Telephone element."
msgstr ""
"L'Entrada Telefònica Internacionala es utilizada per l'element "
"Telefòn."

msgid ""
"A simple jQuery plugin that transforms a select element into a more "
"user friendly graphical interface."
msgstr ""
"Un plugin jQuery simple que transforma un element select dins una "
"interfàcia grafica mai amistosa per l’utilizaire."

msgid "The username of the user that submitted the webform."
msgstr ""
"Lo nom d’utilizaire de l’utilizaire qu’a sosmés lo formulari "
"web."

msgid ""
"If checked, all submission events will be logged to dedicated "
"submission log available to all webforms and submissions."
msgstr ""
"Se es cofat, totes los eveniments d'enviament seràn enregistrats dins "
"un registre d'enviaments dedicat accessible a totes las formòlas e "
"sosmissions."

msgid "Default reply-to email"
msgstr "Adreça de respòsta per defècte"

msgid "Default return path (email)"
msgstr "Camins de retorn per defaut (correus electronic)"

msgid "Set submission source entity: @source_entity"
msgstr "Definir l’entitat d’origina de la mòstra: @source_entity"

msgid ""
"Use this field's %entity_type entity as the webform submission's "
"source entity."
msgstr ""
"Utilizatz l'entitat %entity_type d'aquest camp coma entitat sorga de "
"la submissió del formulari web."

msgid ""
"If unchecked, the current page's entity will be used as the webform "
"submission's source entity. For example, if this webform was displayed "
"on a node's page, the current node would be used as the webform "
"submission's source entity."
msgstr ""
"Se foguèt pas cochent, l'entitat de la pagina corrent serà utilizada "
"coma entitat d'origina de la submissió del formulari web. Per "
"exemple, se aqueste formulari web foguèt afichat sus la pagina d'un "
"nòud, lo nòud corrent serà utilizat coma entitat d'origina de la "
"submissió del formulari web."

msgid "Open value"
msgstr "Valor dubèrt"

msgid "Close value"
msgstr "Valor serrada"

msgid "Default submission data (YAML)"
msgstr "Dadas d’enviament per defaut (YAML)"

msgid "The @title close date cannot be before the open date"
msgstr ""
"La data de tancament de @title pòt pas èsser abans de la data "
"d'ertura"

msgid "Initial country"
msgstr "País inicial"

msgid "Image select"
msgstr "Seleccion d'imatge"

msgid "Provides a form element for selecting images."
msgstr "Provesís un element de formulari per seleccionar d’imatges."

msgid "'@subject' sent to '@to_mail' from '@from_name' [@from_mail]'."
msgstr "'@subject' mandat a '@to_mail' dempuèi '@from_name' [@from_mail]'."

msgid "Other (Used when 'other' value is entered)"
msgstr "Autre (Utilizat quand la valor « autre » es entrada)"

msgid "Empty (Used when no option is selected)"
msgstr "Vòide (Utilizat quand cap d'efièch es causit)"

msgid "Webform Demo: Event Registration System"
msgstr "Demostracion Webform: Sistèma d'Inscripcion a l'Eveniment"

msgid "Webform scheduled email commands"
msgstr "Comandaments d'e-mails programmats de Webform"

msgid "Allows webform emails to be scheduled."
msgstr ""
"Permet de programar l’enviament de corrèus electrònics per "
"formularis web."

msgid "Handler @id is not a scheduled email handler."
msgstr "Lo gestor @id es pas un gestor de corrièrs electronic programat."

msgid "Webform Scheduled Email Handler"
msgstr "Manipulador de corrièrs planificats per Webform"

msgid "scheduled"
msgstr "escaladat"

msgid "Scheduled email @action for @handler handler."
msgstr "Correu electronic programat @action per lo gestor @handler."

msgid "queued to be sent."
msgstr "en filèra per èsser mandada."

msgid "Scheduled email status (@total)"
msgstr "Estat dels emails programats (@total)"

msgid ""
"It is strongly recommended that <a href=\":href\">submission "
"logging</a> is enable to track scheduled emails."
msgstr ""
"Es fòrtament recomandat d'activar lo <a href=\":href\">registrament "
"de las submisssions</a> per seguir los corrièrs planificats."

msgid "Send email on"
msgstr "Mandar un corrièl sus"

msgid "Check schedule emails after submissions have been processed."
msgstr ""
"Comprova los e-mails programats après que las submissions sián "
"estadas tractadas."

msgid "Multiple handlers can be used to schedule multiple emails."
msgstr ""
"Diverse manejaires pòdon èsser utilisats per programar mantun "
"corrièr electronic."

msgid "Deleting this handler will unschedule all scheduled emails."
msgstr ""
"Eliminar aqueste gestor desencadenarà la desprogramacion de tots los "
"corrièrs planificats."

msgid ""
"Scheduled emails are automatically sent starting at midnight using <a "
"href=\":href\">cron</a>, which is executed at predefined interval."
msgstr ""
"Los correus electronic programmats son mandat automàticament a partir "
"de la miègjornada en utilizant <a href=\":href\">cron</a>, que "
"s'executa a d'intervales predeterminats."

msgid ""
"%submission: Email <b>not sent</b> for %handler handler because a "
"<em>To</em>, <em>CC</em>, or <em>BCC</em> email was not provided."
msgstr ""
"%submission: Correu electronic <b>pas mandat</b> per lo gestor "
"%handler pr'amor qu'un adreiça <em>Al</em>, <em>CC</em>, o "
"<em>BCC</em> èra pas fornida."

msgid ""
"%submission: Email <b>not scheduled</b> for %handler handler because "
"%send is not a valid date/token."
msgstr ""
"%submission: Correu electronic <b>non planificat</b> per lo gestor "
"%handler perque %send es pas una data/token valid."

msgid ""
"%submission: Email <b>@action</b> by %handler handler to be sent on "
"%date."
msgstr ""
"%submission: Correu electronic <b>@action</b> per lo gestor %handler "
"que serà enviat lo %date."

msgid "%submission: Email <b>unscheduled</b> for %handler handler."
msgstr ""
"%submission: Correu electronic <b>pas planificat</b> per lo gestor "
"%handler."

msgid "Unschedule:"
msgstr "Desprogramar:"

msgid "Show all webforms"
msgstr "Mostrar totes los formularis web"

msgid "Select how multiple values are displayed."
msgstr "Seleccionatz cossí se mòstran los valors multiples."

msgid "Contact Documentation"
msgstr "Contactar la Documentacion"

msgid "Webform Cookbook"
msgstr "Libre de Reçèptas per Webform"

msgid "Signature related-projects"
msgstr "Signatura prepausits ligats"

msgid "Form builder comparison"
msgstr "Comparason de constructors de formularis"

msgid ""
"Webform is much heavier; it has a great deal of functionality enabled "
"right within the one module, and that's on top of supplying all the "
"normal field elements (because it doesn't just use the Field API)"
msgstr ""
"Webform es plan mai pesuc; ten una granda quantitat de foncionalitats "
"activadas just dins lo meteis modulus, e aquò es a mai de provesir "
"totes los elements de camps normaus (perque utiliza pas solament "
"l’API de camps)."

msgid ""
"Please post comments and feedback to this <a href=\":href\">Google "
"Sheet</a>."
msgstr ""
"Mercés de publicar los comentaris e los retours aquí <a "
"href=\":href\">Google Sheet</a>."

msgid ""
"The <a href=\":homepage_href\">@title</a> library is <a "
"href=\":external_href\">externally hosted libraries</a> and loaded via "
"a Content Delivery Network (CDN)."
msgstr ""
"La biblioteca <a href=\":homepage_href\">@title</a> es una <a "
"href=\":external_href\">biblioteca alensada dempuèi una font "
"externa</a> e es carregada a través d'una ret de difusion de "
"contengut (CDN)."

msgid ""
"A jQuery plugin that makes long, unwieldy select boxes much more "
"user-friendly."
msgstr ""
"Un plugin jQuery que fa que las caissas de seleccion longas e "
"malaisidas sián plan mai ergonomicas per l’utilizaire."

msgid "Leave blank to use %email as the '@title' email."
msgstr "Daissatz en blanc per utilizar %email coma l'adreça e-mail '@title'."

msgid "File upload limit"
msgstr "Limita de tamanh per l'enviament de fichièrs"

msgid "Excluded submission handlers"
msgstr "Manegadors de submission excludits"

msgid "Purging settings"
msgstr "Esfregant las configuracions"

msgid ""
"If checked, source entity can be populated using query string "
"parameters. For example, appending "
"?source_entity_type=node&source_entity_id=1 to a webform's URL would "
"set a submission's 'Submitted to' value to 'node:1'."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, l'entitat de sorga pòt èsser emplenada en "
"utilizant de paramètres dins la cadena de consulta. Per exemple, "
"apondre ?source_entity_type=node&source_entity_id=1 a l'URL d'un "
"formulari web fixariá la valor « Submetut a » d'una sosmission a « "
"node:1 »."

msgid ""
"Third party settings allow contrib and custom modules to define "
"webform specific customization settings."
msgstr ""
"Las configuracions de tèrça partida permeton als modules contribuits "
"e personalizats de definir de configuracions personalizadas "
"especificas al webform."

msgid "Required by @type element."
msgid_plural "Required by @type elements."
msgstr[0] ""
"Requerit pel element @type.  \n"
"Requerits pels elements @type."

msgid "Duplicate '@label' options"
msgstr "Opcions duplicadas '@label'"

msgid "%name: this element cannot hold more than @count value."
msgid_plural "%name: this element cannot hold more than @count values."
msgstr[0] ""
"%name: aqueste element pòt pas conténer mai que @count valor.  "
"\n"
"%name: aqueste element pòt pas conténer mai que @count valors."

msgid ""
"Third party settings allow contrib and custom modules to define global "
"settings that are applied to all webforms and submissions."
msgstr ""
"Las configuracions de terças partidas permeton als modules contribuit "
"e personalizats de definir de configuracions globalas que son "
"aplicadas a totes las formòlas web e sosmissions."

msgid "File upload settings"
msgstr "Paramètres de carga de fichièrs"

msgid ""
"Uncheck the below optional external libraries that you do not want to "
"be used by any webforms."
msgstr ""
"Descochetz las bibliotècas externals opcionals çai jos que volètz "
"pas qu'ajòsson dins cap de formularis web."

msgid ""
"The default sender address for emailed webform results; often the "
"email address of the maintainer of your forms."
msgstr ""
"L'adreça expedidora per defaut pels resultats de formularis web "
"enviats per correu electronic; sovent l'adreça de correu electronic "
"del mantenedor de vòstres formularis."

msgid "Select available submission handlers"
msgstr "Seleccionatz los gestionaris d'envidaments disponibles"

msgid "Wizard previous"
msgstr "Maga anterièr"

msgid "wizard previous"
msgstr "assistent precedent"

msgid "Wizard next"
msgstr "Seguissent de l’assistent"

msgid "wizard next"
msgstr "aide seguenta"

msgid "Computed settings"
msgstr "Configuracions calculadas"

msgid ""
"This computed element's value will only be available as a token or "
"exported value."
msgstr ""
"Lo valor d’aqueste element calculat serà disponibla sonque coma un "
"token o un valor exportat."

msgid "Computed value/markup"
msgstr "Valor calculada/marquatge"

msgid ""
"The value will be stored in the database. As a result, it will only be "
"recalculated when the submission is updated. This option is required "
"when accessing the computed element through Views."
msgstr ""
"Lo valor serà emmagazinat dins la basa de donadas. Per consequéncia, "
"serà recalculat sonque quand la submissió serà mesa a jorn. Aquesta "
"opcion es necessària quand se accedís a l'element calculat a "
"travèrs de las Vistas."

msgid ""
"Provides an item to display computed webform submission values using "
"tokens."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona un element per afichar los valors computats d'una "
"submissió de formulari web en utilizant de tokens."

msgid ""
"Provides an item to display computed webform submission values using "
"Twig."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona un element per afichar los valors calculats d’una "
"sosmetuda de formulari web en utilizant Twig."

msgid ""
"Prevent SPAM webform submissions from being submitted without "
"JavaScript enabled using the <a href=\":href_antibot\">antibot</a> "
"method."
msgstr ""
"Empesissètz que los formularis web SPAM sián mandat sens que "
"JavaScript siá activat en utilizant la meteissa metòda <a "
"href=\":href_antibot\">antibot</a>."

msgid "Default empty option required label"
msgstr "Etiqueta requerida de l’opcion vièlh per defaut"

msgid "Default empty option optional label"
msgstr "Etiqueta opcional per l'opcion vidanta per defaut"

msgid "Form prepopulate source entity required"
msgstr "Entitat de font per emplenar lo formulari prealablement es requerida"

msgid "Form prepopulate source entity type"
msgstr "Tipe d'entitat de sorga per preplegar lo formulari"

msgid "Submission user columns"
msgstr "Colomnas d’utilizaire de sosmission"

msgid "Always include private and restricted access elements."
msgstr "Incorporatz totjorn d'éléments amb accès privat e restrench."

msgid ""
"Below columns are displayed to users who can view previous submissions "
"and/or pending drafts."
msgstr ""
"Las colomnas jositas son mostradas als utilizaires que pòdon veire "
"las mòstras precedentas e/o los mòstras en esper."

msgid "Select settings"
msgstr "Seleccionar los parameters"

msgid "Default empty option optional"
msgstr "Opcíon voida per defaut opcionau"

msgid "The default recipient address for emailed webform results."
msgstr ""
"L'adreça de destinatari per defècte pels resultats del formulari web "
"mandats per corrier electronic."

msgid ""
"Webform and source entity are automatically detected based on the "
"current page request. You can use the below settings to hardcode the "
"submission limit block's webform and source entity."
msgstr ""
"Lo formulari web e l'entitat sorga son detectats automaticament en "
"foncion de la recèrca de pagina actuala. Podètz utilizar las "
"configuracions seguissentas per codificar en dur lo formulari web e "
"l'entitat sorga del blòc de limita de submissió."

msgid "An %label id is required."
msgstr "Es necessari un id %label."

msgid "A valid %label is required."
msgstr "Es necessari un %label valid."

msgid "Date year range reverse"
msgstr "Rang d'anadas de data inversat"

msgid "If checked date year range will be listed from max to min."
msgstr ""
"Se la casèla es cochada, lo rang d'ans de las datas s'aficharà del "
"màger al mens."

msgid "Time picker input - Use jQuery time picker with custom time format"
msgstr ""
"Entrada de selector d'ora - Utilizatz lo selector d'ora jQuery amb un "
"fòrmato d'ora personalizat"

msgid ""
"If character counter is enabled, maxlength will automatically be set "
"to the count maximum."
msgstr ""
"Se lo comptador de caractèrs es activat, maxlength serà fixat "
"automaticament al maximum del compte."

msgid ""
"@name cannot be longer than %max @type but is currently %length @type "
"long."
msgstr ""
"@name pòt pas èsser mai long de %max @type mas es actualament de "
"%length @type de long."

msgid "If checked, access controls for included element will be ignored."
msgstr ""
"Se es marcac, los contròls d'accèss per l'element inclus seràn "
"ignorats."

msgid ""
"This webform contains private and/or restricted access elements, which "
"will only be included if the user submitting the form has access to "
"these elements."
msgstr ""
"Aquel formulari web conten d'elements privats e/o d'accès restrench, "
"que seràn incluts sonque se l'utilizaire que sòmte lo formulari a "
"accès a aqueles elements."

msgid "Webform handler response tokens."
msgstr "Tokens de responsa per manejaires de formularis web."

msgid "Empty element message/placeholder"
msgstr "Messatge/espaci reservat per element void"

msgid "Tidy HTML markup"
msgstr "Marcatge HTML net"

msgid "Provides a webform element example."
msgstr "Propausa un exemple d'element de formulari sul www."

msgid "Webform Element Example"
msgstr "Exemple d'element Webform"

msgid "Provides an example that shows how to create a Webform element."
msgstr "Proporciona un exemple que mòstra cossí crear un element Webform."

msgid "Provides an example of a webform submission posted to a remote server."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona un exemple d’una sosmission de formulari web enviada a "
"un servidor remote."

msgid ""
"There are no nodes with webform entity references. Please create add a "
"Webform field to content type."
msgstr ""
"Non i a pas de nòdes amb de referéncias d’entitat de formulari "
"web. Mercés d’afegir un camp de Formulari web al tipe de contegnut."

msgid "There are no webform node references."
msgstr "I a pas de referéncias de nòdes webform."

msgid "Provides starter templates that can be used to create new webforms."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona modèls de debuta que se pòdon utilizar per crear de "
"nòus formularis web."

msgid "Advanced HTML markup rendered using a text format."
msgstr "Marcatge HTML avançat rendut en utilizant un format de tèxt."

msgid ""
"Requires understanding <a href=\":href\">how to build tables using "
"render arrays</a>."
msgstr ""
"Requèr <a href=\":href\">de comandar coma bastir de taulas en "
"utilizant d’èrbas de presentacion</a>."

msgid "Secure value (changeable via server-side code and tokens)."
msgstr "Valor segura (modifiable via lo còde del seridor e los tokens)."

msgid "Allows value to be computed using [tokens]."
msgstr "Permet de calcular la valor en utilizant de [tokens]."

msgid "Basic HTML markup."
msgstr "Marcage HTML basica."

msgid ""
"If checked, dismissible promotion messages that appear when the "
"Webform module is updated will be disabled."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, los messages de promocion que se pòdon sonar e que "
"apareisson quand lo mòde Webform es actualizat seran desactivats."

msgid ""
"Note: Promotions are only visible to users who can <em>administer "
"modules</em>."
msgstr ""
"Nota: Las promociús son visibles son per los utilizaires que pòdon "
"<em>administrar los modules</em>."

msgid ""
"If checked, &lt;p&gt; tags, which can add top and bottom margins, will "
"be removed from all single line HTML markup."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, las balises &lt;p&gt;, que pòdon apondre de marges "
"en naut e en bas, seràn tornadas a quitar de tot lo marcage HTML "
"d'una sola linha."

msgid ""
"The admin title will always be displayed when managing elements and "
"viewing & downloading submissions."
msgstr ""
"Lo títol d’administracion serà totjorn afichat quand se gestionan "
"los elements e quand se veián e telecargan los manuscriches."

msgid ""
"If an element's title is hidden, the element's admin title will be "
"displayed when viewing a submission."
msgstr ""
"Se lo títol d'un element es amagada, lo títol d'administracion de "
"l'element s'aficharà pendent la revision d'una submissió."

msgid "Details (opened)"
msgstr "Detalhs (dobèrt)"

msgid "Details (closed)"
msgstr "Detals (cerrat)"

msgid "This is a @label value."
msgstr "Aquò es una valor @label."

msgid "Computed Elements"
msgstr "Elements computats"

msgid "These are the terms of service."
msgstr "Són çò que son las condicions del servici."

msgid ""
"In order to create a link to your terms, wrap the words where you want "
"your link to be in curly brackets."
msgstr ""
"Per crear un ligam cap a vòstres tèrmes, envelopatz las paraulas ont "
"vòstre ligam deu èsser dins de clausulas corbas."

msgid "Terms of service settings"
msgstr "Configuracions dels tèrmes de servici"

msgid "Provides a terms of service element."
msgstr "Proporciona un element de condicions de servici."

msgid "@form webform remote @type post (@state) to @url failed. @message"
msgstr "@form webform remote @type post (@state) a fallit cap a @url. @message"

msgid "Handler instance ID"
msgstr "Identificant de l’exemplari del gestor"

msgid "Webform example composite"
msgstr "Exemple compausit de webformulàri"

msgid "Schedule email"
msgstr "Programar un corrièr electronic"

msgid "Trigger/Value"
msgstr "Declenchant/Vaor"

msgid "Webform settings @label has been saved."
msgstr "Las configuracions del Webform @label son estadas enregistradas."

msgid ""
"Form is being posted using a custom method. Confirmation page must be "
"handled by the <a href=\":href\">custom form action</a>."
msgstr ""
"Lo formulari es enviat amb una metòda personalizaa. La pagina de "
"confirmacion deu èsser gestionada per la <a href=\":href\">accion de "
"formulari personalizaa</a>."

msgid ""
"Saving of submissions is disabled, submission settings, submission "
"limits, purging and the saving of drafts is disabled. Submissions must "
"be sent via an email or handled using a <a href=\":href\">custom "
"webform handler</a>."
msgstr ""
"L'enregistrament de las sosmetudas es desactivat, las configuracions "
"de sosmetuda, los limits de sosmetuda, lo purge e l'enregistrament "
"dels mòsses es desactivat. Las sosmetudas devon èsser mandadas per "
"mejanç d'un corrièl o dobridas amb un <a href=\":href\">manipulador "
"de formulari web personalizat</a>."

msgid "Required message"
msgstr "Messatge requerit"

msgid ""
"Specifies the legal number intervals. Leave blank to support any "
"number interval. Decimals are supported."
msgstr ""
"Especifica los intervals legals de nombres. Daissatz liure per "
"sosténer quicòm interval de nombres. Los decimals son sostenguts."

msgid ""
"You can set sub-element properties using a double underscore between "
"the sub-element's key and sub-element's property "
"(subelement__property). For example, you can add custom attributes or "
"states (conditional logic) to the title sub-element using "
"'title__attributes' and 'title__states'."
msgstr ""
"Pots configurar las proprietats dels sos-elements en utilizant un "
"doble sònh entre la claus del sos-element e la proprietat del "
"sos-element (soselement__proprietat). Per exemple, pots apondre "
"d’atributs personalizats o d’estats (logica condiciona) al "
"sos-element títol en utilizant 'title__attributes' e 'title__states'."

msgid ""
"Elements that collect multiple option values include multi-select, "
"checkboxes, and toggles."
msgstr ""
"Elements que recolan mantun valor d'eleccion comprenon seleccion "
"multiple, caissas de verificar e commutators."

msgid "Limit settings"
msgstr "Paramètres de limita"

msgid ""
"Descriptions, which are only applicable to radios and checkboxes, can "
"be delimited using ' -- '."
msgstr ""
"Las causas, que son aplicablas sonque a las balas de seleccion e als "
"quadres de verificacion, pòdon èsser delimitadas amb ' -- '."

msgid "<strong>@title @version</strong> (Installed)"
msgstr "<strong>@title @version</strong> (Instalhat)"

msgid ""
"<span class=\"color-warning\"><strong>@title @version</strong> "
"(CDN).</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"color-warning\"><strong>@title @version</strong> "
"(CDN).</span>"

msgid "<strong>@title @version</strong> (CDN)."
msgstr "<strong>@title @version</strong> (CDN)."

msgid "<a href=\":href\">Disable CDN warning</a>"
msgstr "<a href=\":href\">Desactivar l'avís CDN</a>"

msgid ""
"@total libraries (@installed installed; @excluded excluded; @missing "
"CDN)"
msgstr ""
"@total bibliotècas (@installed installadas; @excluded excluas; "
"@missing CDN)"

msgid "Drupal Association"
msgstr "Associacion Drupal"

msgid ""
"The below requirements are checked by the <a href=\":href\">Status "
"report</a>."
msgstr ""
"Las obligacions jos indiquadas son verificadas pel <a "
"href=\":href\">Rapòrt d'estat</a>."

msgid ""
"If unchecked, all warnings about Webform SPAM protection will be "
"disabled."
msgstr ""
"Se deseleccionat, totas las averténcias concernent la proteccion "
"contra lo SPAM de Webform seràn desactivadas."

msgid "Check that all entered values for this element are unique."
msgstr ""
"Verificatz que totes los valors inserits per aqueste element sián "
"unics."

msgid ""
"Check that entered values for this element is unique for the current "
"source entity."
msgstr ""
"Verifica que los valors entrebessits per aqueste element sián unics "
"per l'entitat d'origina actuala."

msgid "Time step"
msgstr "Pas de temps"

