msgid "Contact URL"
msgstr "Adreça URL de contacte"

msgid "Webforms: Submissions log"
msgstr "Formulàris web: Registre de sosmetudas"

msgid "Default wizard confirmation label"
msgstr "Etiqueta de confirmacion per l’assistent per defaut"

msgid "Default more title"
msgstr "Títol mai defaut"

msgid "Default section title tag"
msgstr "Títol de la seccion per defaut"

msgid "Wizard confirmation label"
msgstr "Etiqueta de confirmacion del magicien"

msgid "Track wizard progress in the URL"
msgstr "Seguís lo progès del camin en l'URL"

msgid "Schedule emails for all existing submissions"
msgstr "Programar de emails per totas las submisscions existentas"

msgid "Webforms: Templates"
msgstr "Formularis web: Modèls"

msgid "Emailing & handling submissions"
msgstr "Correspondença electronica & gestion de las sosmissions"

msgid "Collecting webform submissions"
msgstr "Recòlta de las submisses de formularis web"

msgid "Understanding a webform submission"
msgstr "Compréner una submissió de formulari web"

msgid "Attaching webforms to nodes"
msgstr "Ajustar de formularis web als nòds"

msgid "Placing webforms as blocks"
msgstr "Plaçant los formularis web coma blòcs"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Templates</strong> page lists reusable templates that can "
"be duplicated and customized to create new webforms."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Modèls</strong> enumèra de modèls reutilizables "
"que se pòdon copiar e personalizar per crear de nòus formularis web."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Forms configuration</strong> page allows administrators to "
"manage form settings, behaviors, labels, messages and CSS classes."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de <strong>Configuracion dels formularis</strong> permet als "
"administrators de gerir las configuracions, los comportaments, las "
"etiquetas, los messatges e las classas CSS dels formularis."

msgid "Configuration: Elements"
msgstr "Configuracion : Elements"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Elements configuration</strong> page allows administrators "
"to enable/disable element types and manage element specific settings, "
"properties, behaviors and formatting."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de <strong>Configuracion dels elements</strong> permet als "
"administrators d’activar/desactivar los tipes d’elements e de "
"gerir las configuracions especificas dels elements, las proprietats, "
"los comportaments e lo formatatge."

msgid "Configuration: Options"
msgstr "Configuracion : Opcions"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Options configuration</strong> page lists reusable "
"predefined options/values available for select menus, radio buttons, "
"checkboxes and Likert elements."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Configuracion d'opcions</strong> lista las "
"opcions/valors predefinits reutilizables disponibles per los menús de "
"seleccion, los botons radio, las caissas de verifica e los elements "
"Likert."

msgid "Configuration: Submissions"
msgstr "Configuracion : Submissions"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Submissions configuration</strong> page allows "
"administrators to manage submissions settings, behaviors and messages."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de <strong>Configuracion de las sosmissions</strong> permet "
"als administrators de gerir los paramètres, comportaments e messatges "
"de las sosmissions."

msgid "Configuration: Handlers"
msgstr "Configuracion : Gestors"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Handlers configuration</strong> page allows administrators "
"to enable/disable handlers and configure default email settings and "
"messages."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Configuracion dels manejaires</strong> permet als "
"administrators d'activar/desactivar los manejaires e de configurar las "
"configuracions d'email per defaut e los messatges."

msgid ""
"<strong>Handlers</strong> are used to route submitted data to external "
"applications and send notifications & confirmations."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Gestors</strong> son utilizats per enrutar las donadas "
"submetudas cap a d'aplicacions esternas e mandar de notificacions e de "
"confirmacions."

msgid "Configuration: Exporters"
msgstr "Configuracion : Exportators"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Exporters configuration</strong> page allows "
"administrators to enable/disable exporters and configure default "
"export settings."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Configuracion dels exportadors</strong> permet als "
"administrators d’activar/desactivar los exportadors e de configurar "
"las configuracions d’esportacion predefinidas."

msgid ""
"<strong>Exporters</strong> are used to export results into a "
"downloadable format that can be used by MS Excel, Google Sheets and "
"other spreadsheet applications."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Exportaires</strong> son utilizats per exportar de resulta en "
"un fòrmant telecargable que pòt èsser utilizat per MS Excel, Google "
"Sheets e d’autras aplicacions de taula de calcul."

msgid "Configuration: Libraries"
msgstr "Configuracion : Librariás"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Libraries configuration</strong> page allows "
"administrators to enable/disable libraries and define global custom "
"CSS/JavaScript used by all webforms."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de <strong>Configuracion de las bibliotècas</strong> permet "
"als administrators d'activar/desactivar las bibliotècas e de definir "
"un CSS/JavaScript personalizat global utilizat per totas las "
"formularis web."

msgid "Configuration: Libraries: Help"
msgstr "Configuracion : Bibliotecas : Ajuda"

msgid "Configuration: Advanced"
msgstr "Configuracion : Avançada"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Advanced configuration</strong> page allows an "
"administrator to enable/disable UI behaviors, manage requirements and "
"define data used for testing webforms."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Configuracion avançada</strong> permet a un "
"administrador d'activar/desactivar los comportaments de l'UI, de gerir "
"los requisits e de definir las donadas utilizadas per testar las "
"formularis web."

msgid "Configuration: Translate"
msgstr "Configuracion: Traduire"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Translate configuration</strong> page allows webform "
"messages and labels to be translated into multiple languages."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Configuracion de traduccion</strong> permet de "
"traduire los messatges e las etiquetas dels formularis web en mantuns "
"lengatges."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Element plugins</strong> overview page lists all available "
"webform element plugins."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de resum <strong>del plugins d'elements</strong> recampa "
"totes los plugins d'elements de formulari web disponiblas."

msgid ""
"<strong>Webform Element</strong> plugins are used to enhance existing "
"render/form elements. Webform element plugins provide default "
"properties, data normalization, custom validation, element "
"configuration form and customizable display formats."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Elements de Webform</strong> los plugins son utilizats per "
"melhorar los elements de rendut/formulari ja existents. Los plugins "
"d'elements de Webform fornisson de proprietats per defaut, la "
"normalizacion de donadas, la validacion personalizabla, lo formulari "
"de configuracion de l'element e de formats d'afichatge "
"personalizables."

msgid "Plugins: Emails/Handlers"
msgstr "Plugins : Emails/Handlers"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Handler plugins</strong> overview page lists all available "
"webform handler plugins."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de presentacion dels <strong>plugins de gestor</strong> "
"enumèra totes los plugins de gestor de formularis web disponibles."

msgid "Plugins: Exporters"
msgstr "Plugins : Exportators"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Exporter plugins</strong> overview page lists all "
"available results exporter plugins."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de presentacion dels <strong>plugins d'exportacion</strong> "
"balha una lista de totes los plugins d'exportacion de resultats "
"disponiblas."

msgid ""
"The (View) <strong>Source</strong> page allows developers to edit a "
"webform's render array using YAML markup."
msgstr ""
"La pagina (View) <strong>Source</strong> permet als desvolopaires "
"d'editar un tableau de renderizat d'un formulari web en utilizant la "
"notacion YAML."

msgid ""
"Developers can use the (View) <strong>Source</strong> page to alter a "
"webform's labels quickly, cut-n-paste multiple elements, reorder "
"elements, as well as  add custom properties and markup to elements."
msgstr ""
"Los desvolopaires pòdon utilizar la pagina (Vista) "
"<strong>Source</strong> per modificar lèu las etiquetas d'un "
"formulari web, tallar e pegar mantuns elements, reordenar los "
"elements, atal coma apondre de proprietats personalizadas e de "
"balisatge als elements."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Test</strong> form allows a webform to be tested using a "
"customizable test dataset."
msgstr ""
"Lo formulari <strong>de test</strong> permet de testar un formulari "
"web en utiliza una basa de donadas de test personalizable."

msgid ""
"The <strong>API</strong> form allows developers to test a webform's "
"API."
msgstr ""
"Lo formulari <strong>API</strong> permet als desvelopaires de testar "
"l’API d’un formulari web."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Translate</strong> page allows a webform's configuration "
"and elements to be translated into multiple languages."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Translate</strong> permet de tradusir la "
"configuracion e los elements d'un formulari web dins mantunas lengas."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Elements</strong>  page allows users to add, update, "
"duplicate and delete elements and wizard pages."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Elements</strong> permet als utilizaires d'ajouter, "
"de metre a jorn, de duplegar e de suprimir d'elements e de paginas de "
"magicien."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Emails/Handlers</strong> page allows additional actions "
"and behaviors to be processed when a webform or submission is created, "
"updated, or deleted."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Emails/Handlers</strong> permet d’executar "
"d’accions e de comportaments addicionalas quand un formulari web o "
"una submissió es creada, mesa a jorn, o suprimida."

msgid "Settings: General"
msgstr "Ajustaments: Generals"

msgid ""
"The <strong>General</strong> settings page allows a webform's "
"administrative information, paths, behaviors and third-party settings "
"to be customized."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de configuracions <strong>Generala</strong> permet de "
"personalizar l'informacion administrativa, los camins, los "
"comportaments e las configuracions de tercèrs d'un formulari web."

msgid "Settings: Form"
msgstr "Configuracions : Formulari"

msgid "Settings: Submissions"
msgstr "Configuracions: Submissions"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Submissions</strong> settings page allows a submission's "
"labels, behaviors, limits and draft settings to be customized."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de configuracions de las <strong>Sendas</strong> permet de "
"personalizar las etiquetas, los comportaments, los limits e las "
"configuracions de borrador d’una senda."

msgid "Settings: Confirmation"
msgstr "Configuracions : Confirmacion"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Confirmation</strong> settings page allows the submission "
"confirmation type, message and URL to be customized."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de configuracion de <strong>Confirmacion</strong> permet de "
"personalizar lo tipe de confirmacion de mandat, lo messatge e l’URL."

msgid "Settings: Assets"
msgstr "Configuracions : Actius"

msgid ""
"The <strong>CSS/JS</strong> settings page allows site builders to "
"attach custom CSS and JavaScript to a webform."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de configuracion <strong>CSS/JS</strong> permet als "
"constructors de sitis d'apondre un CSS e JavaScript personalizats a un "
"formulari web."

msgid "Settings: Access"
msgstr "Paramètres : Accés"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Submissions</strong> page lists all incoming submissions "
"for all webforms."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Envèis</strong> recensa totes los envèis recebut "
"per totes los formularis web."

msgid "Submissions: Log"
msgstr "Envios : Registre"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Submissions log</strong> page tracks all submission events "
"for all webforms that have submission logging enabled. Submission "
"logging can be enabled globally or on a per webform basis."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Registre de las submissiòns</strong> suivís totes "
"los eveniments de submissiò per totas las fòrmas web que an lo "
"registre de submissiò activat. Lo registre de submissiò pòt èsser "
"activat globalament o per cada fòrma web."

msgid "Results: Submissions"
msgstr "Resultats : Sòmis"

msgid "Results: Log"
msgstr "Resultats : Registre"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Results Log</strong> lists all webform submission events "
"for the current webform."
msgstr ""
"Lo <strong>Registre de Resultats</strong> enumèra totes los "
"eveniments de submissió de formularis web pel formulari web actual."

msgid "Results: Download"
msgstr "Resultats : Telecargar"

msgid "Submission: View"
msgstr "Submissió: Veire"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Data (YAML)</strong> page displays a submission's raw data "
"as YAML."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Donadas (YAML)</strong> mòstra las donadas brutas "
"d'una submissió en format YAML."

msgid "Submission: Log"
msgstr "Sòmision : Registre"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Log</strong> page shows all events and transactions for a "
"submission."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Registre</strong> mòstra totes los eveniments e "
"transaccions per una submissió."

msgid "Submission: Edit"
msgstr "Sòmision : Modificar"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Edit</strong> form allows the administrator to update a "
"submission."
msgstr ""
"Lo formulari <strong>Edit</strong> permet a l’administrador de metre "
"a jorn una submissió."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Edit all</strong> form allows administrator to update all "
"values for submission create from a multi-step form."
msgstr ""
"Lo <strong>Edit all</strong> formulari permet a l’administrador de "
"metre a jorn totes los valors per una submissió creada a partir "
"d’un formulari de mantuns passatges."

msgid "Submission: Resend"
msgstr "Enviament: Tornar a mandar"

msgid "Submission: Notes"
msgstr "Sometuda : Remarcas"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Notes</strong> form allows administrator to flag and "
"annotate a submission."
msgstr ""
"Lo formulari <strong>Notas</strong> permet a l’administrator de "
"marcar e d’anotar una sosmetuda."

msgid "Devel: Export"
msgstr "Devel: Exportar"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Schema</strong> page displays an overview of a webform's "
"elements and specified data types, which can be used to map webform "
"submissions to an external API."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Esquema</strong> mòstra una vista d'ensemble dels "
"elements d'un fòrmulari web e dels types de donadas especificats, que "
"pòdon èsser utilizats per mapar las submissiòlas del fòrmulari web "
"cap a una API externa."

msgid ""
"A <strong>Webform Node</strong> allows webforms to be fully integrated "
"into a website as nodes."
msgstr ""
"Un <strong>node de webform</strong> permet d’integrar completament "
"los webforms dins un sit web coma de nodes."

msgid "Webform Node: References"
msgstr "Node de fòrmulari web : Referéncias"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Reference</strong> pages displays an overview of a "
"webform's references and allows you to quickly create new references "
"(a.k.a Webform nodes)."
msgstr ""
"Las paginas <strong>Referéncia</strong> mòstran una vista d'ensemble "
"de las referéncias d'un formulari web e vos permeton de crear "
"rapidament de nòvas referéncias ( tanben apeladas de nòuds de "
"formulari web)."

msgid "Webform Node: Results: Submissions"
msgstr "Node Webformaire : Resultats : Sometudas"

msgid "Submissions can be reviewed, updated, flagged and annotated."
msgstr ""
"Las submissiás pòdon èsser revisadas, actualizadas, marcadas e "
"anotadas."

msgid "Webform Node: Results: Log"
msgstr "Node Webformulari: Resultats: Registre"

msgid "Webform Node: Results: Download"
msgstr "Node Webform: Resultats: Telecargar"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Download</strong> page allows a webform node's submissions "
"to be exported into a customizable CSV (Comma Separated Values) file "
"and other common data formats."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Telecargar</strong> permet d’exportar las "
"soumisions d’un nòde webform dins un fichièr CSV (valors separats "
"per de virgula) personalizable e dins d’autres formats de donadas "
"corrents."

msgid ""
"A <strong>Webform Block</strong> allows a webform to be placed "
"anywhere on a website."
msgstr ""
"Un <strong>blòc de formulari web</strong> permet de plaçar un "
"formulari web a qualques endreches sus un site web."

msgid "Message: Webform UI Disabled"
msgstr "Messatge : Interfàcia Webform desactivada"

msgid ""
"Please enable the <strong>Webform UI</strong> module if you would like "
"to add easily add and manage elements using a drag-n-drop user "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"Per favor, activa lo <strong>module Webform UI</strong> se vòls "
"apondre e administrar elements facilament en utilizant una interfàcia "
"d’utente amb arrapar e pesar."

msgid "Star/flag the status of this submission"
msgstr "Estelar/bandiar l’estatut d’aquesta submissió"

msgid ""
"Inline (reloads the current page and replaces the webform with the "
"confirmation message)"
msgstr ""
"En linha (recarrega la pagina actuala e remplaça lo formulari web amb "
"lo messatge de confirmacion)"

msgid ""
"Modal (reloads the current page/form and displays the confirmation "
"message in a modal dialog)"
msgstr ""
"Modal (recarrega la pagina/lo formulari corrent e aficha lo messatge "
"de confirmacion dins una fenèstra modala)"

msgid ""
"If checked, users will not be allowed to navigate back to the form "
"using the browser's back button."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, los utilizaires podran pas tornar navigar cap al "
"formulari en emplegant lo boton de tornar enrè del navegador."

msgid "Track wizard progress in the URL by"
msgstr "Seguís lo progrès de l’assistent dins l’URL en"

msgid "Page name (?page=contact)"
msgstr "Nom de la pagina (?page=contact)"

msgid "Page index (?page=2)"
msgstr "Index de pagina (?page=2)"

msgid ""
"Properties do not have to prepended with a hash (#) character, the "
"hash character will be automatically added to the custom properties."
msgstr ""
"Las proprietats an pas besonh d'estar precedidas per un caractèr "
"dièris (#), lo caractèr dièris serà apondut automaticament a las "
"proprietats personalizadas."

msgid ""
"If saving of submissions is disabled, submission settings, submission "
"limits, purging and the saving of drafts will be disabled. Submissions "
"must be sent via an email or processed using a custom <a "
"href=\":href\">webform handler</a>."
msgstr ""
"Se la salvagarda de las submissons es desactivada, las configuracions "
"de submisson, los limits de submisson, l'espurgada e la salvagarda "
"dels esboçes seràn desactivats. Las submissons deuon èsser mandat "
"per e-mail o tractadas en utilizant un <a href=\":href\">gestor de "
"formularis web</a> personalizat."

msgid "Convert anonymous user drafts and submissions to authenticated user"
msgstr ""
"Convertissètz los borradors e las sosmissions d'utilizaires anonims a "
"d'utilizaires autenticats"

msgid ""
"If checked users will be able to update a submission using the "
"webform's URL appended with the submission's (secure) token."
msgstr ""
"Se seleccionat, los utilizaires pòdon actualizar una sosmission "
"emplegant l'URL del formulari web acompanhat del token (segur) de la "
"sosmission."

msgid ""
"Only webforms that are open to new submissions can be updated using "
"the secure token."
msgstr ""
"Solament los formularis web que son dobrats a nòvas sosmetudas pòdon "
"èsser actualizats en utilizant lo token segur."

msgid "All submission event are being logged for all webforms"
msgstr ""
"Totes los eveniments d'envesida son enregistrats per totes los "
"formularis web"

msgid ""
"Submissions accessed using the (secure) token will by-pass all webform "
"submission access rules."
msgstr ""
"Las sotmession accedidas amb lo token (segur) passaràn a drecha per "
"totas las règlas d'accès a la sotmession del webform."

msgid ""
"Limit the number of submissions per user. A user is identified by "
"their user id if logged-in, or by their Cookie if anonymous."
msgstr ""
"Limita lo nombre de submissions per utilizator. Un utilizator es "
"identificat per son id d'utilizator se es connectat, o per son Cookie "
"se es anonim."

msgid "Above test data is keyed by element #type."
msgstr "Las donadas de test sul ocean son clavadas per l'element #type."

msgid ""
"Batch email size is used by any handler that sends out bulk emails. "
"This include the scheduled email handler."
msgstr ""
"La talha del lot de corrièrs es utilizada per qualsevol gestor que "
"manda de corrièrs en massa. Aquò inclutz lo gestor de corrièrs "
"programats."

msgid ""
"Allowed tags are applied to any element property that may contain HTML "
"markup. Element properties which can contain HTML markup include "
"#title, #description, #field_prefix, and #field_suffix."
msgstr ""
"Las etiquetas autorizadas se aplican a qualsevol proprietat d’un "
"element que pòsca conté de marcacion HTML. Las proprietats "
"d’elements que pòdon conté de marcacion HTML incluyen #title, "
"#description, #field_prefix e #field_suffix."

msgid ""
"The label to show for the first default option for a required select "
"menus."
msgstr ""
"L'etiqueta a mòstrar per la primièra opcion per defaut dins los "
"menús de seleccion obligatòris."

msgid ""
"The label to show for the first default option for an optional select "
"menus."
msgstr ""
"L'etiqueta a mostrar per la primièra opcion per defaut dins de menús "
"de seleccion opcionals."

msgid ""
"Redirect anonymous users to login when attempting to access private "
"file uploads"
msgstr ""
"Redirigir los utilizaires anonims cap al vesitar de connexion quand "
"anóncia l'accès a telecargas de fichièrs privats"

msgid ""
"If checked, anonymous users will be redirected to the user login page "
"when attempting to access private file uploads."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, los utilizaires anonims seràn redirigits cap a la "
"pagina de connexion d’utilizaire quand préne l'accès a de "
"telecargas de fichièrs prives."

msgid "Display collapse/expand all details link on all webforms"
msgstr ""
"Afichar lo ligam per plegar/dinamizar totes los detalhs sus totes los "
"formularis web"

msgid ""
"If checked, an expand/collapse all details link will be added to all "
"webforms which contain two or more details elements."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, un ligam per expandir/plegar totas las detalhs serà "
"apondut a totes los formularis web que contenon dos o mai elements de "
"detalhs."

msgid ""
"The default email address that a recipient will see when they are "
"replying to an email. Leave blank to automatically use the 'From "
"email' address. Setting the 'Reply-to' to the 'From email' prevent "
"emails from being flagged as spam."
msgstr ""
"L'adreiça electronica per defaut que un destinatari vei quand respon "
"a un corrièr electronic. Deissatz en blanc per utilizar "
"automaticament l’adreiça 'De l’adreiça electronica'. Definir lo "
"'Répondre a' coma 'De l’adreiça electronica' impedís que los "
"corrièrs sián marcats coma spam."

msgid ""
"The default email address to which bounce messages are delivered. "
"Leave blank to automatically use the 'From email' address."
msgstr ""
"L'adreça email per defaut a la qual son livradas las messages de "
"rebomb. Deissetz vuidar per utilizar automàticament l'adreça email "
"« De »."

msgid ""
"The default sender name which is used along with the default sender "
"email address."
msgstr ""
"Lo nom de l'emissor per defaut qu'es utilizat amb l'adreça mejana de "
"l'emissor per defaut."

msgid ""
"Enter the amount of submissions to be purged during single cron run. "
"You may want to lower this number if you are facing memory or timeout "
"issues when purging via cron."
msgstr ""
"Introduís la quantitat de sosmissions a èsser netejadas pendent una "
"sola execucion de cron. Poiriás voler redusir aqueste nombre se "
"rencontres de problèmas de memòria o de temps de rèsta pendent lo "
"netejament via cron."

msgid "Multiple settings"
msgstr "Configuracions multiples"

msgid ""
"If checked, the composite sub-element titles will be displayed as the "
"table header labels."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, los títols dels subelements compausats s'aficharàn "
"coma las etiquetas de l'encàbal de la taula."

msgid ""
"This is used as the table header for this webform element when "
"displaying multiple values."
msgstr ""
"Aqueste es utilizado coma capçalha de taula per aqueste element de "
"formulari web quand se mòstran mantun valors."

msgid "Number of empty items"
msgstr "Nombre d'elements voides"

msgid "Number of add more items"
msgstr "Nombre d’articles apondre mai"

msgid "If unchecked, the elements will no longer be sortable."
msgstr "Se deseleccionat, los elements serà pas mai ordenables."

msgid ""
"If unchecked, the add/remove (+/x) buttons will be removed from each "
"table row."
msgstr ""
"Se desmarcat, los botons apondre/enlever (+/x) seràn suprimits de "
"cada linha de taula."

msgid "The click-able label used to open and close more text."
msgstr "L’etiqueta clicable utilizada per dobrir e clavar mai de tèxt."

msgid "More text"
msgstr "Mès de tèxt"

msgid ""
"A long description of the element that provides form additional "
"information which can opened and closed."
msgstr ""
"Una descripcion longa de l'element que provesís d'informacions "
"adicionalas al formulari e que pòt èsser dubèrta e serrada."

msgid ""
"Check that entered values for this element are unique for the current "
"user."
msgstr ""
"Verificatz que los valors inserits per aqueste element sián unics per "
"l'usuari actual."

msgid ""
"If set, this message will be used when an element's value are not "
"unique, instead of the default \"@message\" message."
msgstr ""
"Se es definit, aqueste messatge serà utilizat quand la valor d'un "
"element es pas unica, al liure del messatge per defaut \"@message\"."

msgid "Item format custom HTML"
msgstr "Format d'element HTML personalizat"

msgid "Item format custom Text"
msgstr "Format d'item personalizat Tèxt"

msgid "Items format custom HTML"
msgstr "Format d’articles HTML personalizat"

msgid "Items format custom Text"
msgstr "Format personalizat d’elements de tèxt"

msgid ""
"Properties do not have to be prepended with a hash (#) character, the "
"hash character will be automatically added to the custom properties."
msgstr ""
"Las proprietats an pas besonh d'estar precedidas per un caractèr "
"dièze (#), lo caractèr dièze serà apondut automaticament a las "
"proprietats personalizadas."

msgid "Display limit and total submissions for the"
msgstr "Límit d'afichatge e total de sosmissions per la"

msgid ""
"Restrict limit and total submissions to current or specified source "
"entity"
msgstr ""
"Restringís lo nombre limitat e lo nombre total de submissions a "
"l'entitat sorga actuala o especificada"

msgid ""
"You may use tokens. Tokens should use the 'html_date' or "
"'html_datetime' date format. (i.e. @date_format)"
msgstr ""
"Pòtz utilizar de tokens. Los tokens devon utilizar lo format de data "
"'html_date' o 'html_datetime'. (per exemple @date_format)"

msgid "Output the range's value"
msgstr "Donatz la valor de la zòna"

msgid "Include existing submission values"
msgstr "Incluir los valors de submissió ja existents"

msgid ""
"Provides a form element to create custom composites using a grid/table "
"layout."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona un element de formulari per crear de composites "
"personalizats en utilizant un quadrilh/layout de taula."

msgid ""
"If 'Automatic' is selected Flexbox layout will only be used if a "
"'Flexbox layout' element is included in the webform."
msgstr ""
"Se s'es causit 'Automatique', la disposicion Flexbox serà utilizada "
"solament se un element 'Disposicion Flexbox' es includit dins lo "
"formulari web."

msgid "@title help text"
msgstr "@títol tèxte d'ajuda"

msgid ""
"Randomizes the order of the images when they are displayed in the "
"webform"
msgstr ""
"Torna ordenar aleatòriament las imaginas quand son mostradas dins lo "
"formulari web"

msgid "Use the browser's Geolocation as the default value"
msgstr "Utiliza la geolocalizacion del navigador coma valor per defaut"

msgid ""
"Hide the location element and collect the browser's Geolocation in the "
"background"
msgstr ""
"Amagar l'element de localizacion e recuèlher la Geolocalizacion del "
"navegador en tèrra de fons"

msgid "Title/Placeholder"
msgstr "Títol/Marcador"

msgid "Provides an element for a section/group of form elements."
msgstr "Proporciona un element per una seccion/grop d’elements de formulari."

msgid "Image, the signature's <a href=\":href\">Data URI</a>."
msgstr "Imatge, lo <a href=\":href\">URI de donadas</a> de la signatura."

msgid "Status, displays 'signed' or 'no signed'"
msgstr "Estat, aficha 'signat' o 'pas signat'"

msgid "Horizontal rule CSS classes"
msgstr "Classes CSS per las règlas oraizontalas"

msgid ""
"A list of classes that will be provided in the \"Horizontal rule  CSS "
"classes\" dropdown. Enter one or more classes on each line. These "
"styles should be available in your theme's CSS file."
msgstr ""
"Una lista de classas que serà provesida dins lo menú desplegable "
"\"Classes CSS de la règlas orizontala\". Entrez un o mai classas sus "
"cada linha. Aquestes estils devon èsser disponiblas dins lo fichièr "
"CSS de vòstre tèma."

msgid "The total submissions interval per user for the webform."
msgstr "L'intervalle total d'envois per utilizator per lo formulari web."

msgid "Per user submission limit interval per source entity"
msgstr "Intervalle del limita de submession per usatgièr per entitat de sorga"

msgid "Submit previous wizard page when browser back button is clicked"
msgstr ""
"Enviar la pagina anteriora del bruxolèr quand se fa clic sul boton "
"tornar enèr de l’espleitajaire"

msgid "Limit total interval"
msgstr "Limitar l'intervalle total"

msgid "Limit user interval"
msgstr "Intervale limitat per l'utilizaire"

msgid "Entity limit total interval"
msgstr "Intervale total de limita d'entitat"

msgid "Entity limit user interval"
msgstr "Intervalle de limita d’utilizaire d’entitat"

msgid "Webform select display format settings"
msgstr "Paramètres del format d'afichatge de la seleccion de Webform"

msgid "Default submission exception message"
msgstr "Messatge d'excepcion per la somission per defaut"

msgid "Promotions: Drupal Association"
msgstr "Promocions : Associacion Drupal"

msgid "Submit previous page when browser back button is clicked"
msgstr ""
"Enviar la pagina precedenta quand se clica sul boton tornar del "
"navegador"

msgid "Browser back button submits the previous page for all forms."
msgstr ""
"Lo boton de tornar en arrière del navegator manda la pagina "
"precedenta per totas las formularis."

msgid ""
"Optionally specify an alternative URL by which the webform submit page "
"can be accessed. Any value entered here will overwrite ALL aliases you "
"may have created for this form via the <a "
"href=\":path_alias\">path</a> module."
msgstr ""
"Opcionalament, especificatz una adreiça URL alternativa per la pagina "
"de sosmetuda del formulari web. Qualsevol valor inserit aquí "
"remplacarà TOTES las alias que podètz aver creatas per aqueste "
"formulari amb lo <a href=\":path_alias\">module de camin</a>."

msgid "A message to be displayed if submission handling breaks."
msgstr ""
"Un messatge que deurà èsser afichat se lo tractament de la "
"submissió es en panne."

msgid "All URL aliases for all webforms have to be manually created."
msgstr ""
"Totas las alias d'URL per totes los formularis web devon èsser "
"creadas manualament."

msgid ""
"Submit previous page when browser back button is clicked for all "
"webforms"
msgstr ""
"Enviar la pagina anteriora quand se clica lo boton tornar en arrière "
"del navigador per totes los formularis web"

msgid "Prepopulation is enabled for all form elements."
msgstr "La prepopulacion es activada per totes los elements de formulari."

msgid "Please note when an element is hidden it will not be required."
msgstr "Per favor remarca que quand un element es amagatz, es pas obligatoriu."

msgid "Enable default submission data (YAML)"
msgstr "Activar las donadas de sometuda per defaut (YAML)"

msgid ""
"If checked, site builders will be able to define default submission "
"data (YAML)"
msgstr ""
"Se es cochat, los dobrièrs del site podran definir las donadas de "
"sòmia per defaut (YAML)"

msgid "Default submission data: @default_data"
msgstr "Dadas de submissió per defaut: @default_data"

msgid "Custom composite"
msgstr "Composit personalizat"

msgid ""
"The 'File' element is unavailable because a <a "
"href=\"https://www.ostraining.com/blog/drupal/creating-drupal-8-private-file-system/\">private "
"files directory</a> has not been configured and public file uploads "
"have not been enabled. For more information see: <a "
"href=\"https://www.drupal.org/psa-2016-003\">DRUPAL-PSA-2016-003</a>"
msgstr ""
"L'element « File » es pas disponible perque un <a "
"href=\"https://www.ostraining.com/blog/drupal/creating-drupal-8-private-file-system/\">repertòri "
"de fichièrs privats</a> a pas estat configurat e las cargas de "
"fichièrs publics son pas estadas activadas. Per mai d’informacions, "
"vei : <a "
"href=\"https://www.drupal.org/psa-2016-003\">DRUPAL-PSA-2016-003</a>"

msgid "Update the below submission data. (YAML)"
msgstr "Actualiza las donadas de la sosmesa josenca. (YAML)"

msgid "Available element keys"
msgstr "Claus d'element disponibles"

msgid "Debug: Action: @title"
msgstr "Depuratge : Accion : @title"

msgid "Use as Likert"
msgstr "Utilizar coma Likert"

msgid ""
"The <strong>Access</strong> settings page allows an administrator to "
"determine who can administer a webform and/or create, update, delete "
"and purge webform submissions."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de parametratges <strong>Accés</strong> permet a un "
"administrator de determinar quina persona pòt administrar un "
"formulari web e/o crear, aggiornar, suprimir e netejat las submissiás "
"del formulari web."

msgid "Use as likert"
msgstr "Utiliza coma Likert"

msgid ""
"Only webform administrators and user's assigned the 'Edit webform Twig "
"templates' permission are allowed to edit this Twig template."
msgstr ""
"Solament los administrators de webform e los utilizaires assignats amb "
"la permissió 'Modificar los modèls Twig de webform' son autorizats a "
"modificar aqueste modèl Twig."

msgid "Not Pattern"
msgstr "Pas modèl"

msgid "@label description"
msgstr "@label descripcion"

msgid "Questions description display"
msgstr "Afichatge de la descripcion de las preguntas"

msgid "Sanitize file name"
msgstr "Neteja lo nom del fichièr"

msgid "Autofill with previous submission"
msgstr "Complir automaticament amb la submissió anterior"

msgid "Autofill with previous submission message"
msgstr "Remplir automaticament amb lo messatge de soumission precedenta"

msgid "Autofill excluded elements"
msgstr "Elements exclus d'autocompletatge"

msgid "Display required indicator label"
msgstr "Afichar l’etiqueta d’indicador necessari"

msgid "Default submission locked message"
msgstr "Messatge per defecte de mandat blocat"

msgid "Default submission autofill message"
msgstr "Messatge d'autocompletatge per defaut de la submissió"

msgid ""
"Elements contain a duplicate element key %name found on line "
"@line_numbers."
msgid_plural ""
"Elements contain a duplicate element key %name found on lines "
"@line_numbers."
msgstr[0] ""
"Los elements contenon una clau d'element dobla %name trobada a la "
"linha @line_numbers.  \n"
"Los elements contenon una clau d'element "
"dobla %name trobada a las linhas @line_numbers."

msgid "Generate %title submissions"
msgstr "Generar enviar %title"

msgid "If checked, this submissions will be starred when reviewing results."
msgstr ""
"Se marcadas, aquelas submissions seràn estrelhadas pendent la revison "
"dels resultats."

msgid ""
"To customize only webform specific elements, you should use the "
"'.webform-submission-form' selector"
msgstr ""
"Per personalizar sonque los elements especifics del formulari web, cal "
"utilizar lo selector '.webform-submission-form'"

msgid "Required indicator is displayed on all forms."
msgstr "L'indicador necessari es afichat sus totas las formas."

msgid ""
"If checked, a required elements indicator will be added to this "
"webform."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, un indicador d'elements obligatòris serà apondut a "
"aqueste formulari web."

msgid "Autofill with previous submission data"
msgstr "Preen plen amb las donadas de la submissió previa"

msgid "Autofill message"
msgstr "Messatge d’autocompletatge"

msgid ""
"A message to be displayed when form is autofilled with previous "
"submission data."
msgstr ""
"Un messatge que se mostrarà quand lo formulari es emplenat "
"automaticament amb las dadas de la submissió anteriora."

msgid "Autofill elements"
msgstr "Elements d’autocompliment"

msgid "If checked, all off-canvas system trays will be disabled."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, totes los taulèrs del sistèma fòra de l'esquina "
"seràn desactivats."

msgid "Test data by element key"
msgstr "Données de test per clau d’element"

msgid ""
"Above test data is keyed by full or partial element keys. For example, "
"using 'zip' will populate element keys that are 'zip' and 'zip_code' "
"but not 'zipcode' or 'zipline'."
msgstr ""
"Los donadas de tèst ci-dessús son indicadas per de clauses "
"d’element complèts o parcials. Per exemple, utilizar 'zip' "
"emplenarà las clauses d’element que son 'zip' e 'zip_code', mas pas "
"'zipcode' ni 'zipline'."

msgid "Default required indicator label"
msgstr "Etiqueta per l'indicador requerit per defaut"

msgid "Display required indicator on all webforms"
msgstr "Afichar l'indicador requis sus totes los formularis web"

msgid ""
"If checked, a required elements indicator will be added to all "
"webforms."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, un indicador d'elements requerits serà apondut a totes "
"las fòrmularis web."

msgid "Default locked message"
msgstr "Messatge barrat per defaut"

msgid "Default autofill message"
msgstr "Messatge d'autocompletatge per defaut"

msgid "Range output settings"
msgstr "Paramètres de sortida de la gamma"

msgid "Webform Image Select"
msgstr "Seleccion d'imatge dins un formulari web"

msgid "Provides a webform element for a selecting an image."
msgstr "Propausa un element de formulièr web per seleccionar una image."

msgid "Webforms: Images"
msgstr "Formularis web : Imatges"

msgid "The %title images are being altered by the %module_names @module."
msgstr "Las imatges %title son alteradas pel %module_names @module."

msgid ""
"Order submissions by ascending (oldest first) or descending (newest "
"first)."
msgstr ""
"Tria l'òrdre dels envòis per ascendent (los mai vièlhs primièr) o "
"descendant (los mai recents primièr)."

msgid "Inline form errors is disabled for all forms."
msgstr ""
"Las errors dins la forma en línia son desactivadas per totas las "
"formas."

msgid ""
"If checked, <a href=\":href\">inline form errors</a> will be disabled "
"for this form."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, los <a href=\":href\">errors de burèus en "
"linha</a> seràn desactivats per aqueste burèu."

msgid "If checked, events will be logged for submissions to this webform."
msgstr ""
"Se es cofat, los eveniments seràn enregistrats per las sometudas a "
"aqueste formulari web."

msgid "Webform submissions store passwords as plain text."
msgstr ""
"Las sosmissions de formularis web almacenan los senhals coma tèxt "
"clar."

msgid ""
"Any webform that includes this element should enable <a "
"href=\":href\">encryption</a>."
msgstr ""
"Qualques formularis web que contenon aqueste element deurian activar "
"<a href=\":href\">l’encriptacion</a>."

msgid "Disable inline form errors for all webforms"
msgstr ""
"Desactivar las errors de formulari en linha per totes los formulàris "
"web"

msgid ""
"If checked, <a href=\":href\">inline form errors</a>  will be disabled "
"for all webforms."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, los <a href=\":href\">errors de formulari en linha</a> "
"seràn desactivats per totes los formularis web."

msgid "<a href=\":href\">Encryption</a> should be enabled for this element."
msgstr ""
"<a href=\":href\">L'encryptatge</a> deu èsser activat per aqueste "
"element."

msgid ""
"Rename uploaded files to this tokenized pattern. Do not include the "
"extension here. The actual file extension will be automatically "
"appended to this pattern."
msgstr ""
"Renòmbar los fichièrs telecargats amb aqueste patron tokenizat. Ne "
"deuri pas inclure l'extension aicí. L'extension reala del fichièr "
"serà aponduda automàticament a aquel patron."

msgid "Multiple value is not supported for %title (@type)."
msgstr "Lo nombre multiple non es sostengut per %title (@type)."

msgid "Exclude query string from confirmation URL"
msgstr "Exclure la cadena de consulta de l'URL de confirmacion"

msgid "Exclude token from confirmation URL"
msgstr "Exclure lo token de l'URL de confirmacion"

msgid "Exclude query string from Confirmation URL"
msgstr "Exclure la cadena de consulta de l'URL de confirmacion"

msgid ""
"If checked, all query string parameters will be removed from the "
"Confirmation URL."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, totes los paramèters de cadena de consulta seràn "
"enlevats de l'URL de confirmacion."

msgid "Exclude token from Confirmation URL"
msgstr "Exclude la token de l'URL de confirmacion"

msgid "Item label"
msgstr "Etiqueta de l'element"

msgid "Getting Involved Guide | Drupal.org"
msgstr "Guida per participar | Drupal.org"

msgid "Connecting with the Community | Drupalize.me"
msgstr "Se connectar amb la Comunitat | Drupalize.me"

msgid "Concept: Drupal Licensing | Drupalize.me"
msgstr "Concept : Licéncia Drupal | Drupalize.me"

msgid ""
"This screencast walks through how to install the Webform and external "
"libraries."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta captura de pantalla explica coma installar lo module Webform e "
"las librariás externas."

msgid ""
"This screencast provides an overview of how to create, build, edit and "
"test forms and templates."
msgstr ""
"Aquel screencast balha una vista d'ensemble sus cossí crear, montar, "
"editar e testar de fòrmularis e de moclas."

msgid "Form API Life Cycle | Drupalize.me"
msgstr "Cicle de Vida de l'API de Formularis | Drupalize.me"

msgid "Fun with Forms in Drupal 8 | DrupalCon Austin"
msgstr "Divertiment amb los formularis dins Drupal 8 | DrupalCon Austin"

msgid "Render arrays | Drupal.org"
msgstr "Arrays de rendença | Drupal.org"

msgid "Render API Overview | Drupalize.me"
msgstr "Vista generala de l'API de render | Drupalize.me"

msgid "Form Element Reference | Drupalize.me"
msgstr "Referéncia d'element de fòrmulari | Drupalize.me"

msgid "What Are Render Elements? | Drupalize.me"
msgstr "Que son los elements de renderizat? | Drupalize.me"

msgid "Create a Webform Handler in Drupal 8 | Matt Arnold"
msgstr "Crear un manejador de formulièr web dins Drupal 8 | Matt Arnold"

msgid "The Drupal mail system | Pronovix"
msgstr "Lo sistèma de correu de Drupal | Pronovix"

msgid "Entity–attribute–value model | Wikipedia"
msgstr "Modèl entitat–atribut–valor | Wikipedia"

msgid ""
"This screencast walks through all the configuration settings available "
"to manage forms, submissions, options, handlers, exporters, libraries "
"and assets."
msgstr ""
"Aqueste screencast recòrre totas las configuracions disponiblas per "
"gerir los formularis, las submisses, las opcions, los gestionaris, los "
"exporters, las bibliotècas e los extends."

msgid "Unraveling the Drupal 8 Plugin System | Drupalize.me"
msgstr "Desvelhar lo sistèma de plugins de Drupal 8 | Drupalize.me"

msgid "Configuration API for Developers | Drupalize.me"
msgstr "API de configuracion per desvelopaires | Drupalize.me"

msgid "Webform: There is this for that"
msgstr "Webform: I a aquò per aquò"

msgid ""
"Response data can be passed to response message using "
"[webform:handler:{machine_name}:{key}] tokens. (i.e. "
"[webform:handler:remote_post:message])"
msgstr ""
"Las donadas de responsa se pòdon passar al messatge de responsa en "
"utilizant los tokens [webform:handler:{machine_name}:{key}]. (per "
"exemple [webform:handler:remote_post:message])"

msgid "Enter custom response messages for specific status codes."
msgstr ""
"Entratz de messatges de responsa personalizats per de còdis d'estat "
"especifics."

msgid ""
"Webforms can only be translated via the Webform's (Configuration) "
"Translate tab."
msgstr ""
"Los formularis web pòdon èsser traduïts sonque a travèrs de "
"l'onglet Traduire del formulari web (Configuracion)."

msgid "Unused webform submission files should be marked temporary"
msgstr ""
"Los fichièrs de submissió d’un formulari web inutilizats deuràn "
"èsser marcats coma temporari."

msgid ""
"Uploaded files will be temporarily stored on the server and referenced "
"in the database for %interval."
msgstr ""
"Los fichièrs telecargats seràn provisionalament emmagazinats sul "
"servidor e referenciats dins la basa de donadas per %interval."

msgid ""
"Add ':clear' to the end token to return an empty value when the token "
"is missing."
msgstr ""
"Apondètz ':clear' al token final per tornar una valor voida quand lo "
"token es mancant."

msgid "Previous submission message"
msgstr "Mensagem de submession precedenta"

msgid "Previous submissions message"
msgstr "Messatge de sosmetudas precedentas"

msgid "Open referenced webform in modal dialog"
msgstr "Dobrir lo formulari web referenciat dins una fenèstra modala"

msgid "Default previous submission message"
msgstr "Messatge de premsa predefinit anterior"

msgid "Default previous submissions message"
msgstr "Messatge per las submisssions anterioras per defaut"

msgid "Enable webform dialog support"
msgstr "Activar lo supòrt del dialog de webform"

msgid "Dialog options"
msgstr "Opcions de dialog"

msgid ""
"Submitting the below values will trigger the %title webform's "
"::validateFormValues() and ::submitFormValues() callbacks."
msgstr ""
"Enviar los valors joscrivuts activaràn los retors "
"::validateFormValues() e ::submitFormValues() del formulari web "
"%title."

msgid ""
"Below are links and code snippets that can be inserted into your "
"website to open this form in a modal dialog."
msgstr ""
"Apondèm aicí de ligams e de còdis que pòdon èsser inserits dins "
"vòstre sit web per dubrir aqueste formulari dins una fenèstra "
"modala."

msgid "A message to be displayed if submission is locked."
msgstr "Un messatge per èsser afichat se la mesa en linha es barricada."

msgid "A message to be displayed when there is previous submission."
msgstr "Un messatge a afichar quand i a una submissió precedenta."

msgid "Dialog machine name"
msgstr "Nom de la maquina de dialòg"

msgid "Enable site-wide dialog support"
msgstr "Activar lo supòrt de dialog dins tot lo site"

msgid ""
"<strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> To insert dialog links using the @labels "
"<a href=\":href\">text formats</a> the @tag must be added to the "
"allowed HTML tags."
msgstr ""
"<strong>IMPORTANT :</strong> Per inserir de ligams de dialògue en "
"utilizant los @labels <a href=\":href\">formats de tèxt</a>, lo @tag "
"deu èsser apondut a las balisas HTML autorizadas."

msgid ""
"Make this element non-editable with the user entered (e.g. via "
"developer tools) value <strong>ignored</strong>. Useful for displaying "
"default value. Changeable via JavaScript."
msgstr ""
"Fai que aquest element siá non-editable amb la valor intrada per "
"l’utilizaire (per exemple via d'aisinas de desvolopaire) "
"<strong>ignoradas</strong>. Util per afichar una valor per defaut. "
"Modificable per JavaScript."

msgid ""
"Make this element non-editable with the user entered (e.g. via "
"developer tools) value <strong>submitted</strong>. Useful for "
"displaying default value. Changeable via JavaScript."
msgstr ""
"Fai que aqueste element siá non-editaire amb la valor "
"<strong>submitida</strong> inserida per l’utilizaire (per exemple a "
"travèrs d’eines de desvolopaire). Utile per afichar una valor per "
"defaut. Modificable amb JavaScript."

msgid "Add more button label"
msgstr "Apondre mai d'etiquetas per de botons"

msgid ""
"This is used as the add more items button label for this webform "
"element when displaying multiple values."
msgstr ""
"Es utilizat coma l'etiqueta del boton apondre mai d'elementes per "
"aqueste element de la fòrmula web quand se mòstran de valors "
"multiples."

msgid "Add more input label"
msgstr "Apondre mai d'etiqueta d'entrada"

msgid ""
"This is used as the add more items input label for this webform "
"element when displaying multiple values."
msgstr ""
"Aquò es utilizat coma l’etiqueta de l’entrada per apondre mai "
"d’articles per aqueste element de formulari web quand s’afichan de "
"valors multiples."

msgid "Enter additional attributes to be added to the element's wrapper."
msgstr ""
"Introduïtz d'atributs addicionals per èsser aponduts al contingent "
"de l'element."

msgid "Dialog: @dialog"
msgstr "Dialog: @dialog"

msgid "- Select dialog -"
msgstr "- Seleccionar lo dialòg -"

msgid ""
"For a list of the currently available source entity related tokens, "
"please see <a href=\":href\">token help</a>."
msgstr ""
"Per una lista dels tokens ligats a d’entitats sorgissentas "
"actualament disponiblas, vos cal consultar <a href=\":href\">l’ajuda "
"pels tokens</a>."

msgid "Preview exclude unselected checkboxes"
msgstr ""
"Previsualizar çò que s'excludís las caissas de verificacion pas "
"seleccionadas"

msgid "Exclude unselected checkboxes"
msgstr "Exclure las caissas de seleccion pas seleccionadas"

msgid "Test @title"
msgstr "Tèst @title"

msgid "Test Custom"
msgstr "Test Personalizat"

msgid "No items message"
msgstr "Messatge de pas d’objèctes"

msgid "This is used when there are no items entered."
msgstr "Es utilisat quand i a pas d'elements soscrit."

msgid ""
"Minimum items defaults to 0 for optional elements and 1 for required "
"elements."
msgstr ""
"Lo nombre minim d'articles es fixat a 0 pels elements opcionals e a 1 "
"pels elements obligatòris."

msgid "Submission user duplicate"
msgstr "Utilizaire de mòda duplicada"

msgid "Allow users to duplicate previous submissions"
msgstr "Permetètz als utilisateurs de dupliquíser las sosmissions anterioras"

msgid ""
"If checked, users will be able to duplicate their previous "
"submissions."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, los utilizaires podran dupliquar lors sosmissions "
"previas."

msgid "Enable inline form errors"
msgstr "Activar las errors de fomulari en linha"

msgid "Provides example webforms for reviewing and testing accessibility."
msgstr ""
"Propausa de formularis web d’exemple per revisar e testar "
"l’accessibilitat."

msgid "This @label handler was @op."
msgstr "Aqueste manipulador @label foguèt @op."

msgid "Webform Accessibility"
msgstr "Accessibilitat del Webformulàri"

msgid "Drupal 8 Accessibility"
msgstr "Accessibilitat dins Drupal 8"

msgid ""
"Progress tracking allows analytic software to capture a multi-step "
"form's progress."
msgstr ""
"Lo seguiment del progrès permet al logiciel analitic de capturar lo "
"progrès d'un formulari amb multiples passes."

msgid ""
"If checked, users will be able to reset a form and restart multi-step "
"wizards. Current drafts will be deleted when the form is reset."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, los utilizators podran tornar initializar un "
"formulari e tornar començar los assistents amb mantunas etapas. Los "
"esboçes actuals seràn suprimits quand lo formulari es tornat "
"inicializat."

msgid ""
"A local file system path where temporary export files will be stored. "
"This directory should be persistent between requests and should not be "
"accessible over the web."
msgstr ""
"Un camin de sistèm de fichièrs local ont se tornaràn a maitenir los "
"fichièrs d'exportacion temporaris. Aqueste repertòri deu èsser "
"persistent entre las requèstas e deu pas èsser accessible via "
"internet."

msgid "Dependent_locality"
msgstr "Localitat_dependenta"

msgid "(Display purposes only)"
msgstr "(Per de veson solament)"

msgid ""
"If checked, any element used within the computed value/markup will "
"trigger any automatic update."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, tot element utilizat dins la valor/etiqueta calculada "
"activarà tota actualizacion automatica."

msgid "Validation error message"
msgstr "Messatge d'error de validacion"

msgid ""
"Tokens related to user roles that can receive email. <em>This token is "
"only available to a Webform email handler's 'To', 'CC', and 'BCC' "
"email recipients.</em>"
msgstr ""
"Tòkens ligats als ròtles dels utilizaires que pòdon recebre de "
"correus electronics. <em>Aqueste tòken es disponible sonque per als "
"destinataris de correus electronics 'A', 'CC' e 'CCI' d’un gestor de "
"correus electronics d'un Webform.</em>"

msgid "Purge any submissions"
msgstr "Purgar totas las submissions"

msgid "Element text format"
msgstr "Format de tèxte d'element"

msgid "Mail text format"
msgstr "Format del tèxte del correu electronic"

msgid ""
"Input masks ensures a predefined format is entered. This can be useful "
"for dates, numerics, phone numbers, etc…"
msgstr ""
"Las mascas d'entrée asseguran qu'un format predefinit siá entrat. "
"Aquò pòt èsser util per las datas, los nombres, los numèros de "
"telefon, etc."

msgid ""
"Apply classes to the @type. Select 'custom…' to enter custom "
"classes."
msgstr ""
"Aplica las classas al @type. Selecciona 'personalizat…' per inserir "
"de classas personalizadas."

msgid "Enter key…"
msgstr "Clau de entrada…"

msgid "Enter placeholder…"
msgstr "Introduïtz un tèxte de plaça..."

msgid "Enter other…"
msgstr "Entrar autrament…"

msgid ""
"If checked, the confirmation page will be included in the progress "
"bar."
msgstr ""
"Se es cofat, la pagina de confirmacion serà inclusa dins la barra de "
"progres."

msgid ""
"The first page label in the progress bar. Subsequent pages are titled "
"by their wizard page title."
msgstr ""
"Lo primièr títol de pagina dins la barra de progrès. Las paginas "
"seguentas son tòtladas pel títol de la pagina de l'encantador."

msgid "The confirmation page label's in the progress bar."
msgstr "L’etiqueta de la pagina de confirmacion dins la barra de progrès."

msgid ""
"Allow (dialog) source entity to be populated using query string "
"parameters"
msgstr ""
"Permetre a l'entitat sorgent (dialog) d'èsser emplenada en utilizant "
"los paramètres de la frasa de requèsta"

msgid ""
"Weight is used when multiple webforms are associated to the same "
"webform node."
msgstr ""
"Lo pes es utilizat quand mai d'un formulario web son associats al "
"meteis node de formulario web."

msgid "Please note: Drafts will always be linked to submission form."
msgstr ""
"Remarquiatz que : Los esboços seràn totjorn ligats al formulari de "
"someténcia."

msgid "Enter submitted to…"
msgstr "Entrar mandat a…"

msgid "Filter by submitted to"
msgstr "Filtrar per mandatari"

msgid ""
"Batch export size is used when submissions are being "
"exported/downloaded."
msgstr ""
"La talha de l'exportacion per traches es utilizada quand las "
"sosmetudas son exportadas/telècargadas."

msgid "Batch update size is used when submissions are being bulk updated."
msgstr ""
"La talha de la màssa de la mitanada es utilizada quand se meton a "
"jorn d'enviaments en gran nombre."

msgid "Batch delete size is used when submissions are being cleared."
msgstr ""
"La talha de supression per lot es utilizada quand se suprimisson de "
"submissons."

msgid ""
"The (read) more label used to hide/show more information about an "
"element."
msgstr ""
"L’etiqueta (legir mai) utilizada per amagar/mostrar mai "
"d’informacions sus un element."

msgid ""
"If checked, the webform dialog library will be added to every page on "
"your website, this allows any webform to be opened in a modal dialog."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, la librariá de dialog de webform serà aponduda a "
"cada pagina del vòstre siti web, çò que permetrà d'abrir quina que "
"siá webform dins un dialog modal."

msgid ""
"Webform specific dialog links will be included on all webform settings "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Los ligams especifics del dialòg de Webform seràn incluses dins "
"totes los formularis de configuracion de webform."

msgid "Help title"
msgstr "Títol d'ajuda"

msgid "Defaults to the element's title"
msgstr "Per defaut al títol de l'element"

msgid "Displays a read more hide/show widget below the element's description."
msgstr ""
"Aficha un grop de cercar mai amagar/mostrar jos la descripcion de "
"l’element."

msgid "More title"
msgstr "Mai de títol"

msgid ""
"Apply classes to the element's wrapper around both the field and its "
"label. Select 'custom…' to enter custom classes."
msgstr ""
"Aplica las partidas al contorn de l'element al torn del camp e de son "
"etiqueta. Selecciona « personalizat… » per dintrar de partidas "
"personalizadas."

msgid "Create submission"
msgstr "Crear un envieu"

msgid "Enter 'name': 'value' pairs…"
msgstr "Entrar de parelhs 'nom': 'valor'…"

msgid ""
"You should consider using a dedicated Time element, instead of this "
"Date/time element, which will prepend the current date to the "
"submitted time."
msgstr ""
"Deuriatz considerar l’utilizacion d’un element de Temps dedicat, "
"en loc d’aqueste element de Data/temps, que préposarà la data "
"correnta a l’ora sosmesa."

msgid "Please select predefined options."
msgstr "Vaquí seleccionar d'opcions predefinidas."

msgid "@title visible"
msgstr "@title visibla"

msgid "@title title display"
msgstr "@title afichatge del títol"

msgid "Remove whitespace around the"
msgstr "Supprime los espacis al torn deth"

msgid "computed value and between HTML tags"
msgstr "valor calculada e entre de balises HTML"

msgid ""
"If checked, the answers will float at the top of the page as the user "
"scrolls-thru the questions."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, las responsas flotaran al cap de la pagina mentre "
"que l'utilizaire fai passar las questions."

msgid "Form access denied message attributes"
msgstr "Atributs del messatge d'accès al formulari refusat"

msgid "Submission views"
msgstr "Vistas de submissions"

msgid "Submission view"
msgstr "Vista de sosmession"

msgid "Submission view replace"
msgstr "Substitucion de la vista de presentacion"

msgid "Replace to global"
msgstr "Remplaçar per global"

msgid "Replace to webform"
msgstr "Remplaçar per webformulari"

msgid "Replace to node"
msgstr "Remplaçar per vòrtice"

msgid "Submission access denied action"
msgstr "Accion de refus d'accès a la submissió"

msgid "Submission access denied title"
msgstr "Accès a l’enviament refusat títol"

msgid "Submission access denied message"
msgstr "Messatge d'accès a la submissió refusat"

msgid "Submission access denied message attributes"
msgstr "Atributs del messatge d'accès refusat a la submissió"

msgid "Default submission view replace"
msgstr "Desplegament per defaut de la vista de mesa a jorn"

msgid "Default submission access denied message"
msgstr "Messatge d'accès negat per defaut a l'enviament"

msgid "Default Algolia application id"
msgstr "ID d'aplicacion Algolia per defaut"

msgid "Controls if unused webform submission files should be marked temporary"
msgstr ""
"Contròla se los fichièrs d’enviaments de formularis web non "
"utilizedes deuràn èsser marcats coma temporaris"

msgid "Immediately deleted temporary managed webform submission files"
msgstr ""
"Fichièrs d’enviament de formulari web gestionats temporàriament "
"suprimits immediatament"

msgid ""
"Existing submissions that have conditionally hidden elements will have "
"the element's submission data cleared when the submission is updated."
msgstr ""
"Las sosmissions existentas que contenon d’elements amagats "
"condicionalament auràn las donadas de sosmission dels elements "
"sarradas quand la sosmission es actualizada."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Access group</strong> page lists reusable groups used to "
"access webform source entity and users."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Grop d'accès</strong> lista los gropes "
"reutilizables utilizats per accedir a l'entitat de mòstras web e als "
"utilizaires."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Access type</strong> page lists types of groups used to "
"send email notifications to users."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Tipus d'accès</strong> enumèra los tipes de grops "
"utilizats per mandar de notificacions per corrièr electronic als "
"utilizaires."

msgid "Provides webform access controls for webform nodes."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona de contròles d'accès a las webforms pels nòds de "
"webform."

msgid "Prevent scheduling past actions"
msgstr "Empesir la programacion d'accions passadas"

msgid "Ignore past:"
msgstr "Ignorar lo passat:"

msgid "Save + Add element"
msgstr "Enregistra + Apondre element"

msgid "Webform access controls"
msgstr "Controles d'accès a las Webforms"

msgid "Access Control | Tag1 Consulting"
msgstr "Contraròtle d'acces | Tag1 Consulting"

msgid "Opening webforms in modal dialogs"
msgstr "Dobrir de formularis web dins de fenèstras modalas"

msgid "This screencast shows how to open webforms in modal dialogs."
msgstr ""
"Aqueste screencast mòstra cossí dobrir los formularis web dins de "
"caïchas modalas."

msgid "Creating a modal in Drupal 8 | Befused"
msgstr "Creacion d’un modal dins Drupal 8 | Befused"

msgid "Display forms in a modal dialog with Drupal 8 | Agaric"
msgstr "Afichar de formularis dins una fenèstra modala amb Drupal 8 | Agaric"

msgid "Webform views integration"
msgstr "Integracion de vistas Webform"

msgid "D8 Webform and Webform Views Integration @ Drupalcamp Colorado"
msgstr "Integracion de D8 Webform e Webform Views al Drupalcamp Colorado"

msgid "RateIt is used to provide a customizable rating element."
msgstr ""
"RateIt es utilizat per proveire un elemento de valoracion "
"personalizable."

msgid "more submission views"
msgstr "mai de vistas de submissió"

msgid ""
"A webform submission embed display. The selected view should also "
"include contextual filters. "
"{webform_id}/{source_entity_type}/{source_entity_id}/{account_id}/{in_draft}"
msgstr ""
"Una mostracion embedida d’una submession de formulari web. La vista "
"causida deu tanben incluir de filtres contextuals. "
"{webform_id}/{source_entity_type}/{source_entity_id}/{account_id}/{in_draft}"

msgid ""
"The name to be displayed in the URL when there are multiple submission "
"views available."
msgstr ""
"Lo nom que deu èsser afichat dins l’URL quand i a mantunas vistas "
"d’enviament disponiblas."

msgid ""
"The title to be display in the dropdown menu when there are multiple "
"submission views available."
msgstr ""
"Lo títol que se mòstra dins lo menú desplegable quand i a mantunas "
"vistas de submissió disponiblas."

msgid "Replace the global results with submission views"
msgstr "Remplaçar los resultats globals per de vistas de submissió"

msgid "Replace the webform results with submission views"
msgstr ""
"Remplaçar los resultats del formulari web pels agachadas de "
"sosmetudas"

msgid "Replace the node results with submission views"
msgstr "Remplaçar los resultats de nòde amb de vistas de remesas"

msgid ""
"Only 'Inline', 'Message', 'Modal', and 'None' confirmation types are "
"fully supported by Ajax."
msgstr ""
"Solament los types de confirmacion 'Inline', 'Message', 'Modal' e "
"'None' son completament suportats per Ajax."

msgid "When a user is denied access to this webform"
msgstr "Quand un utilizator a pas accès a aqueste formulaire web"

msgid "Login (Redirects to user login form and displays message)"
msgstr ""
"Connexion (Redirige cap al formulari de connexion de l'utilizaire e "
"aficha un messatge)"

msgid ""
"Will be displayed either in-line or as a status message depending on "
"the setting above."
msgstr ""
"Serà afichat o ben en linha o ben coma un messatge d’estatut segon "
"la configuracion ça-dessus."

msgid "Access denied message attributes"
msgstr "Atributs del messatge d'accès refusat"

msgid ""
"For example, appending "
"<code>?source_entity_type=node&source_entity_id=1</code> to a "
"webform's URL would set a submission's 'Submitted to' value to "
"'node:1'."
msgstr ""
"Per exemple, apondre "
"<code>?source_entity_type=node&source_entity_id=1</code> a l’URL "
"d’un formulari web fixariá la valor 'Submés a' d’una submission "
"a 'node:1'."

msgid ""
"You can also append "
"<code>?source_entity_type=ENTITY_TYPE&amp;source_entity_id=ENTITY_ID</code> "
"and the <code>ENTITY_TYPE</code> and <code>ENTITY_ID</code> parameters "
"will automatically be replaced based on the current page's source "
"entity."
msgstr ""
"Podètz tanben apondre "
"<code>?source_entity_type=ENTITY_TYPE&amp;source_entity_id=ENTITY_ID</code> "
"e los paramètres <code>ENTITY_TYPE</code> e <code>ENTITY_ID</code> "
"seràn remplaçats automàticament en foncion de l'entitat sorsa de la "
"pagina actuala."

msgid "When a user is denied access to a submission"
msgstr "Quand un utilizator se vènia refusat l'accès a una submetuda"

msgid "Page (Displays message when access is denied to a submission)"
msgstr "Pagina (Aficha un messatge quand l'accès a una sotmission es refusat)"

msgid ""
"To expose your webform elements to your webform submission views. "
"Please install the <a href=\":href\">Webform Views Integration</a> "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Per expondre los elements del vòstre formulari web dins las vistas de "
"sosmissions del formulari web. Mercés d'installar lo <a "
"href=\":href\">module Webform Views Integration</a>."

msgid "Create new submission view"
msgstr "Crear una nòva vista de presentacion"

msgid ""
"If checked, help text will be removed from every webform page and "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, lo tèxte d'ajuda serà enlevat de cada pagina e "
"fòrmulari web."

msgid ""
"Files uploaded via the CKEditor file dialog to webform elements, "
"settings, and configuration will not be exportable."
msgstr ""
"Los fichièrs uploads a travèrs de la fenèstra de fichièrs del "
"CKEditor als elements de webform, configuracions e paramètrages "
"seràn pas exportables."

msgid ""
"It is recommended to use the <a href=\":href\">IMCE module</a> to "
"manage webform elements, settings, and configuration files."
msgstr ""
"Es recomandat d’utilizar lo <a href=\":href\">modul IMCE</a> per "
"gerir los elements de formularis web, las configuracions, e los "
"fichièrs de configuracion."

msgid "Randomize elements"
msgstr "Aleatòriar los elements"

msgid ""
"Randomizes the order of the sub-element when they are displayed in the "
"webform."
msgstr ""
"Mescla l'òrdre dels subelements quand s'afichan dins lo formulari "
"web."

msgid "My Regional Webforms"
msgstr "Los meus mòdes web regionals"

