"'Date/time' minimum or maximum should not be used with 'Date' or "
"'Time' specific minimum or maximum."
msgstr ""
"Lo 'data/ora' minimum o maxim deveriá pas èsser utilizat amb un "
"minimum o maxim especific de 'Data' o 'Ora'."

