msgstr "Data/ora minima"

msgid "Specifies the minimum date/time."
msgstr "Especifica la data/ora minima."

msgid ""
"Accepts any date in any <a "
"href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/tar/manual/html_chapter/tar_7.html#Date-input-formats\">GNU "
"Date/Time Input Format</a>. Strings such as today, +2 months, and Dec "
"9 2004 10:00 PM are all valid."
msgstr ""
"Accepta quina data que siá dins quina que siá <a "
"href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/tar/manual/html_chapter/tar_7.html#Date-input-formats\">Forma "
"d'Entrada de Data/ora GNU</a>. De cadenes coma uèi, +2 meses, e 9 de "
"desembre de 2004 a 22:00 son totas validas."

