msgstr ""
"Enregistrament e raport dedicats per las sosmessions de formularis "
"web."

msgid "The element key %name on line @line_number is a reserved key."
msgstr "La clau d'element %name a la linha @line_number es una clau reservada."

msgid ""
"The webform submission log will track more detailed user information "
"including email addresses and subjects."
msgstr ""
"Lo registre de las submissiòs de formularis web seguirà "
"d’informacions mai detalhadas sus los utilizators, inclusent "
"d’adreças electronicas e de subjèctes."

