"Go to <a href=\":href\">form settings</a> to select what happens when "
"a user is denied access to a webform."
msgstr ""
"Anatz a <a href=\":href\">las configuracions del fòrmulari</a> per "
"seleccionar çò que capita quand un utilizator a pas accès a un "
"fòrmulari web."

msgid "Wrap long lines of text"
msgstr "Enrollar linhas longas de tèxt"

msgid "200 OK"
msgstr "200 D'acòrdi"

msgid ""
"Please make sure to enable 'Include files as attachments' for each "
"email handler that you want to send this attachment."
msgstr ""
"Asseguratz-vos d'activar «Inclure los fichièrs coma atalhs» per "
"cada gestor de corrièl perque volètz mandar aqueste atalh."

msgid ""
"Please enter the attachment's file name with a file extension. The "
"file extension will be used to determine the attachment's content "
"(mime) type."
msgstr ""
"Mercés d'entrar lo nom del fichièr de l'anèx amb una extension de "
"fichièr. L'extension de fichièr serà utilizada per determinar lo "
"tipe de contengut (mime) de l'anèx."

msgid ""
"Make sure the attachment URL/Path is publicly accessible. The "
"attachment's URL/path will never be displayed to end users."
msgstr ""
"Asseguratz-vos que l'URL/espaci del fichièr jontat siá accessibla "
"publicament. L'URL/espaci del fichièr jontat serà jamai afichat als "
"utilizaires finals."

msgid ""
"Webforms must first be <a href=\":href\">created</a> before "
"referencing them."
msgstr ""
"Las formas web deuon èsser <a href=\":href\">creadas</a> abans "
"d'èsser referenciadas."

msgid "Sending webform email attachments"
msgstr "Mandar los fichièrs en pòst electrònic d'un formulaire web"

msgid ""
"This presentation shows how to set up and add email attachments via an "
"email handler."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta presentacion mòstra cossí configurar e ajustar de "
"pieces-jointas dins un gestor de e-mails."

msgid "How to send email attachments? | Drupal.org"
msgstr "Cossí mandar d’alegats per corrièl ? | Drupal.org"

msgid ""
"Multiple test submissions can be created using the Devel generate "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Se pòdon crear mantunas sosmetudas de pròva en utilizant lo modul "
"Devel generate."

msgid "Form access denied settings"
msgstr "Paramètres de refus d'accès al formulari"

msgid "Form preview settings"
msgstr "Configuracions de previsualizacion del formulari"

msgid "Form custom settings"
msgstr "Configuracions personalizadas del formulari"

msgid "Form method"
msgstr "Mèta de formulari"

msgid "Form action"
msgstr "Accion del formulari"

msgid "Form custom properties"
msgstr "Proprietats personalizadas del formulari"

msgid "Submission general settings"
msgstr "Paramètres generals de submissió"

msgid "Submission user settings"
msgstr "Opcions de l'utilizaire per l'enviament"

msgid "Submission access denied settings"
msgstr "Configuracions d'accès al submetent refusadas"

msgid "Submission limit settings"
msgstr "Paramètres de limitacion d'enviament"

msgid "Submission draft settings"
msgstr "Paramètres de l'esquisse de sosmetuda"

msgid "Submission autofill settings"
msgstr "Paramètres d'autocomplecion de la mesa en facha"

msgid "Submission views settings"
msgstr "Configuracions de las vistas de submissió"

msgid "Form confirmation settings"
msgstr "Configuracions de confirmacion de formulari"

