msgstr "Paramètres de la fenèstra de dialòg"

msgid ""
"The HTML to display for a single element value. You may include HTML "
"or <a href=\":href\">Twig</a>. You may enter data from the submission "
"as per the \"variables\" below."
msgstr ""
"L'HTML per afichar una valor d'un sol element. Podètz includir de "
"HTML o <a href=\":href\">Twig</a>. Podètz inserir de donadas de la "
"mesa jos coma indicat dins las « variables » çai jos."

msgid ""
"The text to display for a single element value. You may include <a "
"href=\":href\">Twig</a>. You may enter data from the submission as per "
"the \"variables\" below."
msgstr ""
"Lo tèxt a afichar per una sola valors d'element. Pòdes inclure <a "
"href=\":href\">Twig</a>. Pòdes inserir de donadas de la submissió "
"segon las \"variables\" josèrtas."

msgid ""
"The HTML to display for multiple element values. You may include HTML "
"or <a href=\":href\">Twig</a>. You may enter data from the submission "
"as per the \"variables\" below."
msgstr ""
"L'HTML per afichar mantun valor d'element. Podètz inclure HTML o <a "
"href=\":href\">Twig</a>. Podètz entrar de donadas de la submission "
"segon las « variables » qu’i a jos."

msgid ""
"The text to display for multiple element values. You may include <a "
"href=\":href\">Twig</a>. You may enter data from the submission as per "
"the \"variables\" below."
msgstr ""
"Lo tèxt a afichar per mai d'una valor d'element. Podètz including <a "
"href=\":href\">Twig</a>. Podètz intrar de donadas dempuèi la sòma "
"segon las «variables» çai jos."

msgid ""
"Editing webform source code allows users to alter and possibly break a "
"webform's render array."
msgstr ""
"Modificar lo còde font d’un formulari web permet als utilizaires de "
"cambiar e eventualament d’esbucar l’òrdre de renderizacion del "
"formulari web."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Upload</strong> page allows a CSV (comma separated values) "
"file or URL to be uploaded, converted, and imported into webform "
"submissions."
msgstr ""
"La pagina <strong>Envèia</strong> permet d’envèiar un fichièr CSV "
"(valors separats per virgula) o una URL, de los convertir e de los "
"importar dins las sosmissions de formularis web."

msgid "Provides the ability to export and import submissions."
msgstr "Provesís la capacitat d'exportar e d'importar de sosmissions."

msgid "Unable to locate source entity (@entity_type:@entity_id)"
msgstr "Incapable de trobar l'entitat sorgenta (@entity_type:@entity_id)"

msgid ""
"The upload directory %directory for the file element %name could not "
"be created or is not accessible. A newly uploaded file could not be "
"saved in this directory as a consequence, and the upload was canceled."
msgstr ""
"Lo repertòri de mòrtia %directory per l'element de fichièr %name "
"foguèt pas pogut crear ni accedir. Un fichièr novèl cargat podrà "
"pas èsser enregistrat dins aqueste repertòri per consequéncia, e lo "
"cargament foguèt annulat."

msgid "Importing submissions is a new and experimental feature."
msgstr ""
"L'importacion de sosmissions es una foncionalitat novèla e "
"experimentala."

msgid ""
"Please test and review your imported submissions using a "
"development/test server."
msgstr ""
"Per favor, ensajatz e reviseu vòstras sosmetas importadas en "
"utilizant un servidor de desvolopament/de test."

msgid "All submission properties and data is optional."
msgstr "Totes las proprietats e donadas de submissió son opcionals."

msgid "If UUIDs are included, existing submissions will always be updated."
msgstr ""
"Se los UUID son includits, las submisssions existentas seràn totjorn "
"actualizadas."

msgid ""
"If UUIDs are not included, already imported and unchanged records will "
"not create duplication submissions."
msgstr ""
"Se los UUIDs son pas inclutz, los registres ja importats e pas "
"modificats crearàn pas de submetudas duplicadas."

msgid ""
"File uploads must use publicly access URLs which begin with http:// or "
"https://."
msgstr ""
"Los telecargaments de fichièrs devon utilizar d'URLs d'accès public "
"que comencen per http:// o https://."

msgid "Entity references can use UUIDs or entity IDs."
msgstr ""
"Las referéncias d'entitat pòdon utilizar de UUIDs o d'identificators "
"d'entitat."

msgid ""
"Composite (single) values are annotated using double underscores. "
"(e.g. ELEMENT_KEY__SUB_ELEMENT_KEY)"
msgstr ""
"Los valors composites (unic) son anotats en utilizant de dobles traits "
"de soubretot. (per exemple ELEMENT_KEY__SUB_ELEMENT_KEY)"

msgid ""
"Multiple composite values are formatted using <a href=\":href\">inline "
"YAML</a>."
msgstr ""
"Diferents valors composts son formatats en utilizant <a "
"href=\":href\">YAML en linha</a>."

msgid "Import maximum execution time limit is @time."
msgstr "La durada màxima d'execucion importada es de @time."

msgid ""
"<a href=\":href_view\">View</a> or <a "
"href=\":href_download\">download</a> an example submission CSV."
msgstr ""
"<a href=\":href_view\">Vesar</a> o <a "
"href=\":href_download\">telecargar</a> un fichièr CSV d'exemple de "
"submissió."

msgid "Import data source"
msgstr "Importar la sorga de donadas"

msgid "Upload Submission CSV file"
msgstr "Telecargar lo fichièr CSV de sosmission"

msgid "Enter Submission CSV remote URL"
msgstr "Entrar l'URL remota CSV de sosmetuda"

msgid "Remote URL could be a <a href=\":href\">published Google Sheet</a>."
msgstr ""
"L'URL remòta pòt èsser una <a href=\":href\">feilha Google "
"publicada</a>."

msgid "Submission CSV (Comma Separated Values) file"
msgstr "Fichièr CSV de sosmesa (valors separats per vírgula)"

msgid "Are you sure you want to import @submissions?"
msgstr "Sès segur que vòls importar @submissions?"

msgid ""
"No UUID or token was found in the source (CSV). A unique hash will be "
"generated for the each CSV record. Any changes to already an imported "
"record in the source (CSV) will create a new submission."
msgstr ""
"Cap UUID o token foguèt trobat dins la sorga (CSV). Un hash unic "
"serà generat per cada enregistrament CSV. Qualques modificacions "
"d’un enregistrament ja importat dins la sorga (CSV) crearàn una "
"nòva submissió."

msgid "Import mapping"
msgstr "Importacion de la mapa"

msgid "Importing submissions"
msgstr "Importacion de las submisses"

msgid "Imported @count of @total submissions…"
msgstr "Importadas @count de @total de sosmissions…"

msgid ""
"Submission import completed. (total: @total; created: @created; "
"updated: @updated; skipped: @skipped)"
msgstr ""
"Importacion de sosmession finalizada. (total : @total ; creat : "
"@created ; actualizat : @updated ; saltat : @skipped)"

msgid "Webform module now supports importing submissions | Drupal.org"
msgstr ""
"Lo module Webform supòrta ara l'importacion de submissions | "
"Drupal.org"

msgid ""
"Batch import size is used when submissions are being "
"imported/uploaded."
msgstr ""
"La talha de l'importacion per lots se utiliza quand los envòis son "
"importats/telècargats."

msgid "If checked, users will be able search/filter images by their labels."
msgstr ""
"Se foguèt seleccionat, los utilizaires poiràn cercar/filter las "
"imatges segon lors legendas."

msgid "Filter placeholder label"
msgstr "Mòstra d'espaci per filtrar"

msgid "Filter single item label"
msgstr "Filtrar l'item unic etiqueta"

msgid "Filter plural items label"
msgstr "Etiqueta de filtrar los elements plurals"

msgid "Filter no results label"
msgstr "Etiqueta per cap de resultats del filtres"

msgid ""
"CSV data that can't be converted to submission data will display a "
"warning. If checked, these warnings will be treated as errors and "
"prevent the submission from being created."
msgstr ""
"Las donadas CSV que pòdon pas èsser convertidas en donadas "
"d'enviament mostraràn un avertiment. Se es cochada, aquestas "
"avertiments seràn considerats coma d'eròr e empediran la creacion de "
"l'enviament."

msgid "Webforms for Healthcare"
msgstr "Formulàris web per la sanitat"

msgid ""
"This presentation discusses how healthcare organizations can leverage "
"the Webform module for Drupal 8."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta presentacion explica cossí las organizacions de santat pòdon "
"aprofechar lo mòdule Webform per Drupal 8."

