msgstr "Un modèl de formulari web de demanda de consulta mèdica."

msgid ""
"Your request has been sent. A care specialist will call you back "
"within XX hours to schedule an appointment."
msgstr ""
"La vòstra demanda es estada mandatada. Un expert de l'assisténcia "
"vos chiamarà tornarmai dins XX oras per programar un rendez-vous."

msgid ""
"Selecting a custom POST or GET method will automatically disable "
"wizards, previews, drafts, submissions, limits, purging, "
"confirmations, emails, computed elements, and handlers."
msgstr ""
"Seleccionar un metòde POST o GET personalizat desactivarà "
"automaticament los assistents, las previsualizacions, los esboças, "
"las submetudas, los limits, lo netejament, las confirmacions, los "
"correus electronics, los elements calculats, e los manejaires."

