msgstr "Los fichièrs cargats incluron l’id del fichièr, son nom e sa uri."

msgid ""
"Here is a detailed feature-comparison of Webform and Contact Storage "
"8.x-1.x.&nbsp;It's worth noting that Contact Storage relies on the "
"Contact module which in turn relies on the Field UI; Contact Storage "
"out of the box is a minimalistic solution with limited (but useful!) "
"functionality. This means it can be extended with core mechanisms such "
"as CRUD entity hooks and overriding services; also there's a greater "
"chance that a general purpose module will play nicely with it (eg. the "
"Conditional Fields module is for entity form displays in general, not "
"the Contact module)."
msgstr ""
"Aquí sètz una comparason detalhada de las foncionalitats de Webform "
"e Contact Storage 8.x-1.x.&nbsp;Cal notar que Contact Storage depend "
"del mòdule Contact que, per son torn, depend del Field UI; Contact "
"Storage tal coma ven es una solucion minimalista amb de foncionalitats "
"limitadas (mas utilizas!). Aquò significa que pòt èsser estendut "
"amb de mecanismes del nucli coma los espleches CRUD d'entitat e la "
"suscripcion dels servicis; tanben i a mai de possibilitats qu’un "
"mòdule de tòca generala siaga compatible amb el (per exemple, lo "
"mòdule Conditional Fields es per las exibicions de formularis "
"d’entitat en general, pas per lo mòdule Contact)."

msgid ""
"If checked, options will be available as answers to Likert elements. "
