msgid "Use a lazy builder to render the form after the page is built/loaded."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza un constructor perqueu per renderizar lo formulari après que "
"la pagina siá estacionada/carregada."

msgid ""
"If checked, the form will be loaded after the page has been built and "
"cached. Lazy builders work best when using the <a "
"href=\":href\">BigPipe</a> module."
msgstr ""
"Se seleccionat, lo formulari serà cargat après que la pagina aja "
"siá construïda e mise en cache. Los constructors paresseires "
"foncionan melhor quand s'utiliza lo mòdule <a "
"href=\":href\">BigPipe</a>."

msgid "The URL where the user submitted the webform submission."
msgstr "L'URL ont l'utilizaire a sosmés la sosmession del formulari web."

msgid ""
"Click OK to submit the form without finishing the file upload or "
"cancel to return to form."
msgstr ""
"Clicatz sus OK per enviar lo formulari sens acabar lo telecargament "
"del fichièr o clicatz sus anul·lar per tornar al formulari."

msgid ""
"The automatic saving of drafts only applies to previewing when using "
"cards. Please try using the <a href=\":href\">Webform autosave "
"module</a>."
msgstr ""
"L’enregistrament automatic dels esboças s’aplica solament a "
"l’apercebut quand s’utilizan de cartas. Mercés d’ensajar "
"d’utilizar lo <a href=\":href\">modul d’enregistrament automatic "
"de Webform</a>."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Forms</strong> management page lists all available "
"webforms, which can be filtered by the following: keyword (including "
"title, description, elements, user name, or role), category, and "
"status."
msgstr ""
"La pagina de gestion dels <strong>Formulàris</strong> aficha totes "
"los formularis web disponibles, que se pòdon filtrar pels elements "
"seguents : mot-clau (incluent títol, descripcion, elements, nom "
"d’utilizaire o ròtle), categoria e estat."

msgid ""
"Hiding the %label button can cause unexpected issues. If checked, make "
"sure there is another 'Submit button(s)' element in your form."
msgstr ""
"Amagar lo boton %label pòt causar de problèmas inesperats. Se es "
"seleccionat, asseguratz-vos qu’i a un autre element \"Submit "
"button(s)\" dins vòstre formulari."

msgctxt "form"
msgid "Webform"
msgstr "Formulari web"

msgid "Default confirmation noindex"
msgstr "Confirmacion per defecte noindex"

msgid "Example textarea"
msgstr "Exemple de zòna de tèxt"

msgid "Please enter some text."
msgstr "Per favor, introdusissètz quauquau tèxt."

msgid ""
"<strong>Warning:</strong> Opening %type files with spreadsheet "
"applications may expose you to <a href=\":injection_href\">formula "
"injection</a> or other security vulnerabilities. When the submissions "
"contain data from untrusted users and the downloaded file will be used "
"with Microsoft Excel, use the <a href=\":excel_href\">Webform XLSX "
"export</a> module."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Alerta :</strong> Dobrir de fichièrs %type amb "
"d'aplicacions de taulèras de calcul pòt vos metre a risc d'una <a "
"href=\":injection_href\">injeccion de foromulas</a> o d'autras "
"vulnerabilitats de seguretat. Se las sosmissions contenon de donadas "
"d'utilizaires pas fisables e que lo fichièr telecargat serà utilizat "
"amb Microsoft Excel, emplegatz lo mòde <a "
"href=\":excel_href\">Exportacion XLSX per Webform</a>."

msgctxt "module"
msgid "Webform"
msgstr "Formulària web"

msgid "Default confirmation robots noindex"
msgstr "Robots de confirmacion per defecte noindex"

msgid ""
"If checked, a meta tag robots noindex directive  will be added to the "
"confirmation page of all webforms."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, una directiva meta tag robots noindex serà aponduda a "
"la pària de confirmacion de totes las formòlas web."

msgid "Webform submissions can only be unlocked programmatically."
msgstr ""
"Las mòstras de formularis web pòdon èsser desbloquejadas sonque per "
"programa."

msgid ""
"An error occurred while trying to validate the submission. Please save "
"your work and reload this page."
msgstr ""
"Se produguèt una error en mòde de verificar la mesa a disposicion. "
"Mercés de salvar vòstre trabalh e de tornar cargar aquesta pagina."

msgid "@label (Users, custom email addresses, Administrators)"
msgstr ""
"@label (Utilizaires, adreças de corrièl personalizadas, "
"Administrators)"

msgid ""
"If you enjoy and value Drupal and the Webform module consider <a "
"href=\":href_involved\">getting involved in the Drupal community</a>, "
"<a href=\":href_join\">joining the Drupal Association</a>, and <a "
"href=\":href_opencollective\">contributing funds to the Webform "
"module's Open Collective</a>."
msgstr ""
"Se agradatz e valoratz Drupal e lo module Webform, consideratz <a "
"href=\":href_involved\">vos implicar dins la comunautat Drupal</a>, <a "
"href=\":href_join\">rejonher l'Associacion Drupal</a>, e <a "
"href=\":href_opencollective\">contribuir amb de fons al Open "
"Collective del module Webform</a>."

msgid "This behavior is not supported when Ajax is enabled."
msgstr "Aqueste comportament es pas sostengut quand Ajax es activat."

msgid ""
"If checked, the browser back button will submit the previous page and "
"navigate back emulating the behavior of user clicking a wizard or "
"preview page's back button."
msgstr ""
"Se seleccionat, lo boton de retorn del navegador enviarà la pagina "
"anteriora e tornarà en arrière, emulant lo comportament d'un "
"utilizator que clicaria sul boton de retorn d'un assistent o d'una "
"pagina de previsualizacion."

msgid "@name must be %max @type but is currently %length @type long."
msgstr ""
"@name deu èsser %max @type mas actualament es de %length @type de "
"long."

msgid "@name must be at least %min @type but is currently %length @type long."
msgstr ""
"@name deu èsser almens %min @type mas es actualament de %length @type "
"de long."

msgid "Decimal (-)"
msgstr "Decimal (-)"

msgid "Decimal (+/-)"
msgstr "Decimal (+/-)"

msgid "If checked, variants will be available using query string parameters."
msgstr ""
"Se es cochat, las variantas seràn disponiblas utilizant de "
"paramètres dins la cadena de consulta."

msgid ""
"This is used for the Previous Page button on the page before this page "
"break."
msgstr ""
"Aquò es utilizat per lo boton de la pagina precedenta sus la pagina "
"abans d’aqueste trencament de pagina."

msgid ""
"This is used for the Next Page button on the page after this page "
"break."
msgstr ""
"Es utilizat pel boton Pagina Seguenta dins la pagina aprèp aquel "
"trencament de pagina."

msgid ""
"<strong>Warning:</strong> Opening %type files with spreadsheet "
"applications may expose you to <a href=\":injection_href\">formula "
"injection</a> or other security vulnerabilities. When the submissions "
"contain data from untrusted users and the downloaded file will be used "
"with Microsoft Excel, use the <strong>XLSX</strong> export format."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Atencion :</strong> Dobrir de fichièrs %type amb "
"d'aplicacions de taulèlas de calcul pòt vos exposar a <a "
"href=\":injection_href\">injection de fórmulas</a> o d'autras "
"vulnerabilitats de seguretat. Quand las submissiás contenon de "
"donadas d'utilizators pas fisables e lo fichièr telecargat serà "
"utilizat amb Microsoft Excel, utilizatz lo fòrmato d'esportacion "
"<strong>XLSX</strong>."

msgid ""
"The Drupal Association is an educational non-profit organization that "
"tasks itself with fostering and supporting the Drupal software "
"project, the community and its growth."
msgstr ""
"L'Associacion Drupal es una organizacion educativa sens ànim de lucre "
"que se dona coma mission de promòure e sosténer lo projècte del "
"logiciel Drupal, la comunautat e son desvolopament."

