msgid ""
"The <em>Context</em> module lets users define conditions for when "
"certain reactions should take place."
msgstr ""
"Lo <em>module Context</em> permet als utilizaires de definar de "
"condicions per quand certanas reaccions devon se passar."

msgid ""
"An example of a condition could be when viewing a certain node type "
"and blocks should be placed as a reaction when viewing a page with "
"this node type."
msgstr ""
"Un exemple de condicion poiriá èsser quand se vesiá un tipe de naut "
"de pagina de tipe determinat e los blòcs deurian èsser plaçats coma "
"reaccion al veire una pagina amb aqueste tipe de naut."

msgid "Managing Context"
msgstr "Gestionar lo contèxt"

msgid ""
"Users with <em>Administer contexts</em> permission can add contextual "
"conditions and reactions for different portions of their site. For "
"each context, they can choose the conditions that trigger this context "
"to be active and choose different aspects of their site that should "
"react to this active context."
msgstr ""
"Los utilizators amb la <em>permisison Administrar los contèxtes</em> "
"pòdon apondre de condicions contextualas e de reaccions per de parts "
"diferentas del lor siti. Per cada contèxt, pòdon causir las "
"condicions que desencadenan l'activacion d'aquel contèxt e causir "
"d'aspects diferents del lor siti que devon reagir a aqueste contèxt "
"activ."

msgid "Adding new custom reactions"
msgstr "Apondre nòu reaccions personalizadas"

msgid ""
"Reactions for the context module are defined trough the new <a "
"href=\"https://www.drupal.org/developing/api/8/plugins\">Drupal 8 "
"Plugin API</a>."
msgstr ""
"Las reaccions pel moduèli de contèxt son definidas a travèrs de la "
"novèla <a "
"href=\"https://www.drupal.org/developing/api/8/plugins\">API de "
"Plugins de Drupal 8</a>."

msgid ""
"The Context module defines a plugin type named ContextReaction that "
"users can extend when creating their own plugins."
msgstr ""
"Lo module Context definís un tipe de plugin nomenat ContextReaction "
"que los utilizaires pòdon estendre quand crean lors pròpris plugins."

msgid ""
"A context reaction requires a configuration form and execute method. "
"The execution of the plugin is also something that will have to be "
"handled by the author of the reaction."
msgstr ""
"Una reacció de contèxt requerís un formulari de configuracion e una "
"metodologia d'execucion. L'execucion del plugin serà tanben quicòm "
"que l'autor de la reacció haurà de manejar."

