msgid ""
"Below is an example of how to programmatically validate and submit a "
"webform submission using PHP."
msgstr ""
"Abaix i a un exemple de cossí validar e enviar programaticament una "
"submission de formulari web utilizant PHP."

msgid "Unable to parse CSV file. Please review the CSV file's formatting."
msgstr ""
"Impossible d'analisar lo fichièr CSV. Mercés de verificar la formata "
"de lo fichièr CSV."

msgid "Administer webform overview"
msgstr "Gestion general del formulari web"

msgid "Filter webforms and perform bulk actions on overview page."
msgstr ""
"Filtrar los formularis web e efectuar d’accions en massa sus la "
"pagina de vista d’ensems."

msgid "File upload limit message"
msgstr "Messatge de limita de tustar de fichièrs"

msgid "Check if an element is displayed"
msgstr "Comprova se un element es afichat"

msgid "Default file upload limit per form message"
msgstr "Messatge de limita de mòrt de telecargament de fichièr per formulari"

msgid "Webform deprecated modules"
msgstr "Moduls obsolets de Webform"

msgid ""
"The following webform sub-modules have been deprecated: @module_list. "
"Please download the <a href=\":url\">Webform Deprecated</a> project."
msgstr ""
"Los sub-moduls de formàs web seguents son estat desfatjats : "
"@module_list. Mercés de telecargar lo projecte <a "
"href=\":url\">Formàs Web Desfatjat</a>."

msgid ""
"@element_file_limit limit per file. The accumulated size of all files "
"in this form cannot exceed @webform_file_limit."
msgstr ""
"@element_file_limit limit per fichièr. La talha acumulada de totes "
"los fichièrs dins aqueste formulari pòt pas superar "
"@webform_file_limit."

msgid ""
"The accumulated size of all files in this form cannot exceed "
"@webform_file_limit."
msgstr ""
"La talha acumulada de totes los fichièrs dins aqueste formulari pòt "
"pas excedir @webform_file_limit."

msgid ""
"Note: This is only to be used with the Drupal Bootstrap Theme, NOT "
"with other Bootstrap Framework related Themes (like Radix)."
msgstr ""
"Nota: Aquò deu èsser utilizat sonque amb lo Tèma Drupal Bootstrap, "
"MAS PAS amb d'autres Tèmas relacionats amb lo Framework Bootstrap "
"(coma Radix)."

msgid "Send on (date / datetime string or [token])"
msgstr "Enviar lo (data / cadena de dataora o [token])"

msgid "Please delete submissions from the %title webform."
msgstr "Per favor, suprimissètz las sosmissions del formulari web %title."

msgid "%title webform has @total submissions."
msgstr "%title webform a @total de submetudas."

msgid ""
"You may not delete %title webform until you have removed all of the "
"%title submissions."
msgstr ""
"Podètz pas suprimir lo formulari web %title fins a que siáretz "
"eliminat totas las sosmissions %title."

msgid ""
"Please make sure to install additional <a "
"href=\":libraries_href\">third-party libraries</a>, <a "
"href=\":submodules_href\">sub-modules</a> and optional <a "
"href=\":ecosystem_href\">add-ons</a>."
msgstr ""
"Asseguratz-vos d'installar d'<a href=\":libraries_href\">bibliotècas "
"de tercianes partit</a> complementàrias, de <a "
"href=\":submodules_href\">sos-moduls</a> e d'<a "
"href=\":ecosystem_href\">ajòts</a> opcionals."

msgid "File upload limit per form message"
msgstr "Limita de telecargament de fichièrs per messatge de formulari"

msgid ""
"Enter message to be displayed when file upload limit is reached. You "
"may use %quota as a placeholder."
msgstr ""
"Entratz lo messatge que serà afichat quand la limit de cargament de "
"fichièrs es raggiunta. Podètz utilizar %quota coma espaci reservat."

msgid ""
"You must allow users to post submissions from a dedicated URL to use "
"open this webform is a dialog."
msgstr ""
"Devez permetre a los utilizaires de enviar de sosmissions dempuèi una "
"adreça URL dedicada per utilizar aqueste formulari web que s'abrís "
"dins un quadre de dialog."

msgid "Please delete submissions from the selected webforms."
msgstr "Sètz plan, butatz plegats dels formularis web seleccionats."

msgid "The selected webforms have a total of @total submissions."
msgstr "Los formularis web seleccionats an un total de @total sosmissions."

msgid ""
"You may not delete these webforms until there is less than @batch "
"total submissions."
msgstr ""
"Podètz pas suprimir aqueles formularis web fins a que i aja mens de "
"@batch d’enviaments total."

msgid "Filter by data and/or notes"
msgstr "Filtrar per donadas e/o nòtas"

msgid ""
"If checked, support option, displayed on the <a "
"href=\":help_href\">Help</a> page will be disabled."
msgstr ""
"Se es seleccionat, l'opcion de sosten, afichada a la pagina <a "
"href=\":help_href\">Ajuda</a>, serà desactivada."

msgid "Minimum amount of items displayed"
msgstr "Quantitat minima d’elements afichats"

msgid "Date part title display"
msgstr "Afichatge del títol de la partida de data"

msgid "Determines the placement of the title for date parts."
msgstr "Determina lo plaça del títol pels fragments de data."

msgid ""
"For more advanced use-cases like rendered entities or more complex "
"entity filtering or sorting, you may want to use the \"Views: Filter "
"by an entity reference view\" reference method."
msgstr ""
"Per de cas d'utilizacion mai avançats coma las entitats rendudas o lo "
"filtratge o triatge mai complèxe d'entitats, pòt èsser util "
"d'utilizar la mòda de referéncia \"Views: Filtrar per una vista de "
"referéncia d'entitat\"."

msgid "Justify content"
msgstr "Justificar lo contengut"

msgid "Space between (space-between)"
msgstr "Espaci entre (space-between)"

msgid "Space around (space-around)"
msgstr "Espaci al entorn (space-around)"

msgid "Terms display"
msgstr "Afichatge dels tèrmns"

msgid "Terms link"
msgstr "Enlaç de tèrmens"

msgid "Enter the URL or path of the terms of service."
msgstr "Metti l'URL o lo camin dels termes de servici."

msgid "Terms link target"
msgstr "Objectiu del ligam de termes"

msgid "Language to render this email"
msgstr "Lengatge per generar aqueste corrier electronic"

msgid "Select the language that will be used to render this email."
msgstr ""
"Seleccionatz la lenga que serà utilizada per generar aqueste messatge "
"electronic."

msgid "Enter custom data that will be included in all remote CRUD requests."
msgstr ""
"Introduïtz de donadas personalizadas que seràn inclosas dins totas "
"las requèstas CRUD remotas."

msgid ""
"If checked, elements with 'Display element' unchecked (i.e., "
"<code>'#access': false</code> will not be included in the request "
"data."
msgstr ""
"Se es causit, los elements amb <code>'Exposar l’element'</code> "
"descausit (es a dire, <code>'#access': false</code>) serà pas inclus "
"dins las donadas de la demanda."

msgid "Remote CRUD request return @status_code status code."
msgstr "La demanda remota CRUD torna lo còde d'estat @status_code."

msgid "Remote HTTP operation successful!"
msgstr "Operacion HTTP remota realizada amb succès!"

msgid "Debug: Remote HTTP operation: @title [@state]"
msgstr "Depuracion : Operacion HTTP remota : @title [@state]"

msgid "Remote HTTP Operations"
msgstr "Operacions HTTP a distancia"

msgid ""
"Execute HTTP operation <small>(GET, POST, PUT, or PATCH request "
"methods)</small> to a URL, (optionally) including the webform "
"submissions."
msgstr ""
"Executar una operacion HTTP <small>(mètodes de demanda GET, POST, "
"PUT, o PATCH)</small> cap a una URL, (opcionalament) en includissent "
"las submisssions del formulari web."

