msgid ""
"Exclude individual content that has the Robots meta tag with "
"<em>Prevents search engines from indexing this page</em>."
msgstr ""
"Exclure lo contengut individual que ten la meta etiqueta Robots amb "
"<em>Empècha los motors de recèrca d’indexar aquesta pagina</em>."

msgid ""
"The minimum amount of time that will elapse before the sitemaps are "
"regenerated. The sitemaps will also only be regenerated on cron if any "
"links have been added, updated, or deleted.<br />Recommended value: "
"<em>1 day</em>."
msgstr ""
"La quantitat mínima de temps que s'elapçarà abans que los plans de "
"site sián regenerats. Los plans de site seràn tanben regenerats sul "
"cron sonque se quauquas ligams an estat aponduts, actualizats, o "
"suprimits.<br />Valor recomandada: <em>1 jorn</em>."

msgid ""
"Exclude individual items that has the Robots meta tag set to "
"<em>Prevents search engines from indexing this page</em>."
msgstr ""
"Exclude los elements individualuts que contenen la meta tag Robots "
"configurada a <em>Empècha los motors de recèrca d’indicar aquela "
"pagina</em>."

msgid ""
"Note this will ignore default metatags, only when items have "
"overridden the Robots meta tag."
msgstr ""
"Nòta qu’aquò ignorarà los metatgs per defaut, solament quand los "
"elements an remplaçat la meta etiqueta Robots."

msgid ""
"This can be disabled if other methods are being used to generate the "
"sitemap files, i.e. the <code>drush xmlsitemap:regenerate</code> "
"command."
msgstr ""
"Aquest pòt èsser desactivat se d'autras metòdas son utilizadas per "
"generar los fichièrs de mapa de site, per exemple la comanda "
"<code>drush xmlsitemap:regenerate</code>."

msgid ""
"XML Sitemap automatically creates a sitemap that conforms to the "
"sitemaps.org specification. This helps search engines keep their "
"search results up to date."
msgstr ""
"XML Sitemap crea automàticament una mapa del siti que se conforma a "
"l'especificacion de sitemaps.org. Aquò ajudariá los motors de "
"recèrca a mantenir sos resultats actualizats."

msgid ""
"You can adjust the settings for your site's sitemap at "
"admin/config/search/xmlsitemap. Your can view your site's sitemap at "
"http://yoursite.com/sitemap.xml."
msgstr ""
"Podètz ajustar las configuracions per la mapa del site de vòstre sit "
"al admin/config/search/xmlsitemap. Podètz veire la mapa del site de "
"vòstre sit a http://yoursite.com/sitemap.xml."

msgid ""
"When is necessary you can rebuild your sitemap at "
"admin/config/search/xmlsitemap/rebuild."
msgstr ""
"Quand es necessari, podes tornar bastir ton plan de site a l'adreça "
"admin/config/search/xmlsitemap/rebuild."

msgid ""
"You can configure all Custom Entities Settings at "
"admin/config/search/xmlsitemap/entities/settings"
msgstr ""
"Pòt configurar totas las configuracions de las Entitats "
"Personalizadas a admin/config/search/xmlsitemap/entities/settings"

msgid ""
"It is highly recommended that you have clean URLs enabled for this "
"project."
msgstr ""
"Es plan recomandat d'aver los URLs nets activats per aqueste "
"projècte."

msgid ""
"This action rebuilds your site's XML Sitemap and regenerates the "
"cached files, and may be a lengthy process. If you just installed XML "
"Sitemap, this can be helpful to import all your site's content into "
"the sitemap. Otherwise, this should only be used in emergencies."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta accion refà lo XML Sitemap del vòstre site e regenèra los "
"fichièrs en memòria entrepausada, e pòt èsser un procès long. Se "
"acabatz d’instalar XML Sitemap, aquò pòdon èsser util per "
"importar tot lo contengut de vòstre site dins lo sitemap. Ça que "
"plaça, aquò deu èsser utilizat sonque en cas d’emergéncias."

msgid ""
"XML Sitemap settings have been modified and the files should be "
"regenerated. You can <a href=\"@run-cron\">run cron manually</a> to "
"regenerate the cached files."
msgstr ""
"Las configuracions de XML Sitemap an estat modificadas e caldrà "
"regenarar los fichièrs. Podètz <a href=\"@run-cron\">lancar cron "
"manualament</a> per regenarar los fichièrs en cauç."

msgid ""
"One or more problems were detected with your XML Sitemap "
"configuration: @messages"
msgstr ""
"Un o mai de problèmas an estat detectats amb vòstra configuracion "
"del XML Sitemap : @messages"

msgid ""
"Creates an XML Sitemap conforming to the <a "
"href=\"http://sitemaps.org/\">sitemaps.org protocol</a>."
msgstr ""
"Crea una mapa XML que conéis al <a "
"href=\"http://sitemaps.org/\">protocòl sitemaps.org</a>."

msgid ""
"Configure XML Sitemap settings, select which links are included in "
"sitemap."
msgstr ""
"Configura las configuracions de XML Sitemap, selecciona quinas ligams "
"son inclúsas dins lo sitemap."

msgid "XML Sitemap entity bundle settings"
msgstr "Paramètres dels grops d'entitats XML Sitemap"

msgid "Starting XML Sitemap generation. Memory usage: @memory-peak."
msgstr ""
"Comencem la generacion del sitemap XML. Utilizacion de la memòria : "
"@memory-peak."

msgid ""
"Finished XML Sitemap generation in @elapsed. Memory usage: "
"@memory-peak."
msgstr ""
"Generacion del Sitemap XML acabada en @elapsed. Utilizacion de la "
"memòria : @memory-peak."

msgid ""
"Generated by the <a href=\"@link-xmlsitemap\">Drupal XML Sitemap "
"module</a>."
msgstr ""
"Generat pel <a href=\"@link-xmlsitemap\">module Drupal XML "
"Sitemap</a>."

msgid "Label for the XML Sitemap."
msgstr "Etiqueta per la Sitemap XML."

msgid "There are currently no XML Sitemap contexts available."
msgstr "Actualament, cap de contèxtes XML Sitemap es disponible."

msgid "@bundle XML Sitemap settings"
msgstr "<@bundle Ajustaments del Sitemap XML>"

msgid "XML Sitemap settings for the %bundle have been saved."
msgstr ""
"Las configuracions del plan del site XML pel %bundle son estat "
"enregistradas."

msgid ""
"A rebuild is not necessary. If you are just wanting to regenerate the "
"XML Sitemap files, you can <a href=\"@link-cron\">run cron "
"manually</a>."
msgstr ""
"Una reconstruccion es pas necessària. Se volètz solament regenerar "
"los regulièrs XML del plan del siti, podètz <a "
"href=\"@link-cron\">lançar lo cron manualament</a>."

msgid ""
"When enabled, this will add formatting and tables with sorting to make "
"it easier to view the XML Sitemap data instead of viewing raw XML "
"output. Search engines will ignore this."
msgstr ""
"Quan es activat, aquò apondrà de formatatge e de taulas amb "
"classament per facilitar la consulta de las donadas del plan de site "
"XML en plaça de consultar la sortida XML bruta. Los motors de "
"recèrca o ignoraràn."

msgid ""
"Subdirectory where the sitemap data will be stored. This folder "
"<strong>must not be shared</strong> with any other Drupal site or "
"install using XML Sitemap."
msgstr ""
"Sos-dorsièr onte las donadas de la mapa del site seràn estocadas. "
"Aquesta carpeta <strong>deu pas estar partatjada</strong> amb cap "
"d'autre site Drupal ni installacion que utilize XML Sitemap."

msgid "Override XML sitemap link settings"
msgstr "Substituir las configuracions del ligam de la mapa XML"

msgid "Override XML sitemap settings for individual links/entities."
msgstr ""
"Subrepassar los parameters de la mapa del site XML per los "
"ligams/entitats individualas."

